 <office:body>
  <office:text text:use-soft-page-breaks="true">
   <text:sequence-decls>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Illustration"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Table"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Text"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Drawing"/>
   </text:sequence-decls>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2"><text:bookmark text:name="_GoBack"/>Sa.; obsequio, Hor.; jure, non vi; consilio, si vires nihil juvant; trecenti conjuravimus Romani, ut adversus te hac via g-remur, L.; superbe, avare in provincia; adversum alqm superbiā et sævitiā, Su.; contra deos contemtu religionis, Js.; veneno; dolo; dum eminus g-antur barbari, inulta vulnera fuere, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grassātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grassātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kringstrykande; stråtröfweri:</text:span></text:span> nocturna g-io, Pn.; g-æ et latrocinia, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grassātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lösdrifware; stråtröfware:</text:span></text:span> si quis ad carmina se applicabat, g. vocabatur, Cato; viator spoliatus a g-e, C.; nocturnus, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gressio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gång:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gressus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(poet.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gång; steg; färd:</text:span></text:span> tendere, recipere g-um ad moenia; comprimere g-um; g-us glomerare superbos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en häst),</text:span> Vg.; celeres, Sen.; huc dirige g-um (navi), Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aggrĕdio</text:span>, ĕre: Pt., Js. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aggrĕdior</text:span> <text:line-break/>(adgrĕdior), gressus, grĕdi, (-īri, Pt.), 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå till, begifwa sig hän till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> aliquo, C.; ad aliquem l. aliquem, Pt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wända sig till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn (med ord, böner, löften o. s. w.), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">fresta, angripa:</text:span></text:span> alqm de aliqua re, Pt.; a. et commovere aliquem, C.; pecuniā alqm, Sa.; dictis, Vg.; precibus, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fiendtlig mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Angripa, -falla:</text:span></text:span> urbem; virum, Pt.; alqm, C.; Helvetios, Cs.; ferro alqm, N.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skrida till (werket), gripa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">an, företaga, taga befattning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt; med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">inf.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">begynna, företaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig -:</text:span> in omni re, priusquam a-are, adhibenda est præparatio diligens; ad historiam; ad leges singulas; ad injuriam faciendam; causam ancipitem, C.; rem, Sa.; opus opimum casibus, T.; de quibus dicere a-ar, si - - -, C.; Tydides et Ulixes a. Palladium sacrato avellere templo, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aggressio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Angrepp:</text:span></text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skridande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till en sak, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">begynnelse:</text:span></text:span> prima, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aggressūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Angrepp:</text:span></text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aggressus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span> = aggressio: Fm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Antĕgrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå förut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i rum l. tid,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">trans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">intr.</text:span>: Lucifer solem; (decorum) tum apparet, quum a-sa est honestas, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Circumgrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kringgå, -ränna:</text:span></text:span> barbari c-untur, occursant, T.; exercitum, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Circumgressus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammanträda, -träffa, gå att träffa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">möta:</text:span></text:span> in unam domum, Varr.; quo die c-si erimus, consilium capere poterimus; coram c.; in aliquo loco; cum aliquo; luna cum sole, C.; alqm, Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammandrabba, inlåta sig i kamp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">strid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngn:</text:span> armis Cs.; <text:soft-page-break/>acie, L.; cum vellet, c-retur, Cs.; c. cum hoste, N.; Achilli (<text:span text:style-name="T3">dat.</text:span>) c., Vg - cum rhetore; cum aliquo criminibus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congressio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gående</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tillsammans med någon; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">sammanträde, -träffande, -komst, -waro,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (samtal):</text:span> nemo eum aditu, c-e, sermone, convivio dignum putavit; prohibere alqm a c-e alicujus; sermo in c-bus familiarium versetur; una nostra vel jocosa vel severa c. pluris erit, quam -, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammandrabbning, drabbning:</text:span></text:span> proelii; prima c., Js.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congressus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammanträdande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till en förening); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">sammanträffande, umgänge:</text:span></text:span> bestiarum inter se, C.; non modo sermone ac disputatione, sed conspectu ipso c-uque vestro (omnia placabuntur); hominum c-us fugere; c. quotidianus, C.; c-us feminarum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äktenskapligt),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fiendtligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammandrabbande, träffning:</text:span></text:span> ante c-um multa fiunt, quæ non ad vulnus, sed ad speciem valeant, C.; in primo c-u cadere, Cs.; causæ, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēgrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå, träda, tåga, rycka, stiga ned:</text:span></text:span> de via in semitam, Pt.; monte, Sa.; ex arce; tumulis; in campum; eques ad pedes, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēgrassor</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Störta ned:</text:span></text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Anfalla:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Degressio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Digressio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dīgrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå åtskils, gå bort; skiljas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid ngn l. från hwarandra; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">aflägsna sig, afwika:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absol.,</text:span> Sa., N.; hos ego d-ens dictis solabar amicis, Vg.; priusquam d-rentur, Mettius quæsivit, L.; ab aliquo, C.; inde; a colloquio; domum; in sua castra, L. - uxor a marito d-sa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. förlupit),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Afwika</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (från det rätta, från ämnet, göra en utflygt); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">låta sig bort-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hänföras:</text:span></text:span> officio, Ter.; delectandi gratia parumper d. a causa; ad id, unde d-si sumus, revertamur, C. (alii leg. degredi).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dīgressio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skilsmässa:</text:span></text:span> congressio et d. nostra, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Afwikelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ämnet; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">utflygt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (digression):</text:span> causa - plurimos exitus dat ad d-es; a proposita ratione, a proposito, a re d., C. (alii: degressio). <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dīgressus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bortgång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">skilsmässa:</text:span></text:span> a tuo d-u Romam veni; non (credo) longinquum inter nos d-um et discessum fore, C.; supremus, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Digression:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ēgrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. och eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå, färdas, rycka ut:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T3">intr.</text:span>: domo; portā Capenā; Romā; urbe; ex urbe, C.; castris; e castris, Sa.; ad pugnam, Cs.; extra cancellos, fines, C.; extra vallum, <text:soft-page-break/>N.; e porta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(segla ut),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T3">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lemna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en ort; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">öfwerskrida:</text:span></text:span> urbem, L.; flumen, Sa.; fines, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. l. oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. navi, e navi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. absol. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Landstiga, gå i land:</text:span></text:span> navibus, Cs.; navi, N.; in hunc locum e-si Trojani, L.; in terram e., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rycka, tåga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> upp:</text:span> ad summum montis, Sa.; in tumulum, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Afwika</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (från ämnet):</text:span> a proposito ornandi causa, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerskrida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i oeg. men.):</text:span> modum, L.; historia veritatem, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ēgressio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utgång:</text:span></text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utflygt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ämnet:</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ēgressus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utgående, -gång, -färd; landstigning; afwikelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ämnet:</text:span> frequentiā suā celebrare alicujus e-um, C.; e-us obsidere, T.; remis eo contendit, qua optimum e-um esse cognoverat, Cs.; Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T3">intrans.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">in locum</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">dat.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet.) o.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå in, inträda, beträda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> in antiquum fundum, C.; intra fines suos prohibere alqm i., Cs.; domum; pontem; in viam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> viam, C.; castra, T.; tecta, cubilia, Ov.; castris (<text:span text:style-name="T3">dat.</text:span>), Vg.; loca, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inträda i, komma in på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">råka i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">beträda, tillträda, börja:</text:span></text:span> in vitam; in causam; in disputationem cum aliquo; ad hoc genus disputandi timide; in iram; spem; vitam honestam; viam vivendi; iter pedibus; i-sum scribere alqd nox oppressit, C.; tibi res antiquæ laudis et artis i-or, sanctos ausus recludere fontes, Vg.; primus ego i-or puro de fonte sacerdos Itala per Grajos orgia ferre choros, Ppt.; annum nonum, Vell.; studia; consulatum, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> incedo): quum primum posse i-i coepit -; vix; tardius; ascensu arduo i.; in hac urbe, quacunque i-imur, in aliquam historiam vestigium ponimus; i. vestigiis patriis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i sin faders spår),</text:span> C.; puerulus coepit i.; per scenam i., Pn.; curru <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fara),</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingressio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inträdande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -gång:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ab i-e fori propulsari, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inledning:</text:span></text:span> i. non ex oratoris disputationibus ducta, sed ex media philosophia repetita, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gång:</text:span></text:span> interdum cursus incitatior, interdum moderata i., C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingressus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ingång, -fall; inledning:</text:span></text:span> hostilis, T.: operis, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gång, gående:</text:span></text:span> i., cursus, accubitio; vestigia i-usque, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intrōgrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Träda in:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Praegrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå framför, förut; komma före:</text:span></text:span> Ligus, Sa.; lictor p-itur, L.; gregi equus, Varr.; alqm, C.; ad urbem; p. nuntios et famam rei, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerträffa:</text:span></text:span> Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Praegressio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förutgående:</text:span></text:span> causæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Praetergrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå, fara förbi:</text:span></text:span> castra, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerträffa:</text:span></text:span> Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōgrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå, skrida, rycka, tåga fram:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. men.:</text:span> regredi, quam p-i malle; duos pedes p.; cum exercitu ad locum, C.; tridui viam; magnis itineribus, Cs.; alicui obviam, L.; barbari longius, N. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå framåt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">widare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i framställning l. bewisning); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">gå, fortgå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sträcka sig); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">göra framsteg, winna befordran; förkofra sig, tilltaga:</text:span></text:span> ad reliqua p-amur; oratione longius p.; his non concessis digitum p. non possunt, C.; quidquid p-or, in vastam altitudinem provehor, L.; eo malitiæ; in eum locum, ut -; videamus, quatenus amor in amicitia p-di debeat; ætate p-ens sibi dissimilis factus est; ad omnia (i. e. omnes honores); in virtute; usus p-ens familiaritatem effecit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōgressio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framåtskridande, framsteg; stegring</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i rhetorisk men.):</text:span> ad virtutem; discendi, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōgressus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rummet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gående fram</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. ut; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">framåtskridande:</text:span></text:span> arcere alquem p-u; stellarum p. et regressus constantes, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i tid l. sak) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fortskridande, utweckling; framsteg, förkofran:</text:span></text:span> ætatis; causarum; facere tantos p-us in Stoicis, ut Stoicus esse videatur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕgrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå tillbaka, wika tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> ab ostio, Pt.; r-i quam progredi malle; in infinitum r., C.; hostes, Cs. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Återgå, återwända:</text:span></text:span> ad inceptum, Sa.; (Romam); in illum annum, quo alius prætor fuit, edicto r., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕgressio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Återwändande; upprepande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i rhet.):</text:span> Ap., Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕgressus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tillbakagång, -wikande; återwändande, -komst; tillflykt:</text:span></text:span> stellæ in omni æternitate conservant progressus et r-us, C.; r. in tutum; ab ira, L.; ad principem, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕtrōgrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå bakåt, tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕtrōgrădus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. går tillbaka:</text:span> Mercurius, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕtrōgressus</text:span>, us <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Suggrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå, rycka upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">inemot, på:</text:span></text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭpergrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå ofwanpå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">öfwer; öfwerskrida; stå öfwer, öfwergå, -träffa:</text:span></text:span> ruinas, Ct.; modum, Cap.; necessitates, Sen.; feminas pulcritudine, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Transgrĕdior</text:span>, gressus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå öfwer; öfwergå, -skrida,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">trans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">intr.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> in Italiam, L.; in Germaniam Galli, T.; in contrarias sedes, Pn.; Taurum montem; pomoerium, C.; amnem, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwergå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till annat parti, ämne o. s. w.:</text:span> ad alqm; in partes Vespasiani, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förbigå:</text:span></text:span> mentionem hominis, Val.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerskrida:</text:span></text:span> mensuram, Pn.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerträffa:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Transgressio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwergång:</text:span></text:span> Gallorum, C.; rationis, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Transgressus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwergång:</text:span></text:span> fluvii, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>ræcus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grekisk.</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>ræcus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grek, Hellen.</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>ræce, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På grekiskt sätt, på grekiska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (språket):</text:span> scribere, C. - <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>ræcānĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är efter grekisk sed, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grekisk:</text:span></text:span> nominatus, Varr.; color, Pn.; toga, Sa. - <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>ræcia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Grekland:</text:span> vetus; Magna G. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i Italien),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>Græciensis = Græcanicus: Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Graecisso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">græcisera, wara grekisk:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Græcor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lefwa som en Grek (med bibet. af weklighet l. öfwerflöd):</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congræco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På grekiskt wis förstöra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (rumla upp):</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pergraecor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span> = Græcor: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>ræcostăsis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett ställe på forum i Rom. (jfr. Becker, Röm. Alt.</text:span> 1.): locus est substructus, ubi nationum subsistant legati, qui sunt ad senatum missi, Varr.; C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>ræcŭlus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grekisk, Grek</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ofta med föraktlig bibet.):</text:span> loquax; homo, negotium; G,, C.; G. esuriens in caelum, jusseris, ibit, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>rajocĕli, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt folkslagsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>rajus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekisk, Grek (wanl. archaistiskt och poet.).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>rajŭgĕna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">c.</text:span>: (gigno): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af grekisk börd, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grek:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Grallæ, Grallator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gradior.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grāmen,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gräs, ört:</text:span></text:span> in remoto g-e reclinatus; redeunt jam g-a campis, arboribusque comæ, Hor.; viride g.; ignobile cerinthæ, Vg.; g-is herba pura, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grāmĭneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är af gräs; gräsbewuxen:</text:span> corona, L.; hasta, C.; campus, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grāmĭnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gräsrik:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grāmiae,</text:span> ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">war i ögat:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grāmiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A</text:span>,: Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Gramma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">linie:</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grammĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">geometrisk:</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Gramma,</text:span> ătis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wigt:</text:span> Fann.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grammătĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till skrifter</text:span> (τὰ γράμματα) i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till literaturen l. språkwetenskapen hörande:</text:span> ars, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grammătĭcus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. sysselsätter sig med literatur och språk, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Philolog:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> Su. de Gram. I): hoc literarum studium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwersättn. af</text:span> grammatica), quod profitentur ii, qui vocantur g-i; g-i poētarum <text:soft-page-break/>interpretes; absurdum sit, si quis g-um se professus barbare loquatur, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grammătĭca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grammătĭcē</text:span>, es. <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grammătĭca</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skriftkunskap, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Språk-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">literaturstudier; philologi:</text:span></text:span> rhetorica, dialectica, g-a; in g-is poētarum pertractatio, historiarum cognitio, verborum interpretatio, pronunciandi quidam sonus, C.; g-e in duas partes dividatur, recte loquendi scientiam et poētarum enarrationem; g-es elementa, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grammătĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grammatiskt:</text:span> Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grammătista</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">språklärare (i elementen):</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Grammicus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Gramma.<text:line-break/>Grampius mons <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Graupius m.<text:line-break/>Granaria, Granat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Granum.<text:line-break/>Grandævus, -desco, -diculus, -dificus, -diloquus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Grandis.<text:line-break/>Grandin . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Grando.<text:line-break/>Grandio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Grandis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grandis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stor:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i kroppslig mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stor, storwuxen, rymlig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> m. m.:</text:span> fetus; gutta; g-ia hordea mandare sulcis, Vg.; cubiculum; vas; literæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bokstäfwer);</text:span> epistola, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i andra hänseenden:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: stor = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Riklig, betydande, storartad, hög:</text:span></text:span> seges, Varr.; pecunia; fenus; vectigal; res g-ores, C.; dos; g-e munus Cecropio repetes cothurno; Orcus metit g-ia cum parvis, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wuxen; ålderstigen, gammal:</text:span></text:span> puer, C.; g-ior ætas, Ov.; g-is natu, C.; g. ævo, Ov., T.; bella gerebat, ut adolescens, quum plane g. esset, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om talare l. föredrag: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Storartad, hög, högstämd:</text:span></text:span> orator g-is sententiis, creber verbis; g. et, ut ita dicam, tragicus; g-ior et quodammodo excelsior; genus dicendi; carmen, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandævus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: (ævum): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ålderstigen:</text:span></text:span> Vg., Ov., Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bli stor, wäxa:</text:span></text:span> frumenta, Pn. - lentiscus triplici fetu, poët. ap. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingrandesco</text:span>, ĕre, id.: Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandĭcŭlus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandiusculus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Temligen stor, wuxen:</text:span></text:span> Pt.; virgo g-uscula, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">högsint:</text:span> Amm. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandĭlŏquus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. talar i hög l. storartad stil l. ton: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Högstämd; stortalig:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandio</text:span>, 4.: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wäxa:</text:span></text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/>b- = grandem facere: Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandiscāpius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: (scapus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Storstammig:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Storhet, höghet:</text:span></text:span> verborum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Comp.</text:span> -ius: Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pergrandis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mycket stor:</text:span></text:span> gemma, C.; natu p., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ganska gammal:</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Praegrandis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jättestor:</text:span> aures, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subgrandis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(suggrandis): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">temligen stor:</text:span> cubiculum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Grandiscapius, -ditas, -diter, -diusculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Grandis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grando,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hagel:</text:span></text:span> cadit, nocet; g-bus terrentur animi, C.; nigrans commixta g-e nimbus, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> saxorum, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandĭnat</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Imp.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Det haglar:</text:span></text:span> hieme ningit, non g., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēgrandĭnat</text:span>: Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandĭneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grandĭnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af hagel:</text:span> cæli qualitas, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Graneus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Granum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>rānīcus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Mysien:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Granifer <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Granum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>rānius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Granosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Granum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grānum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Korn, frö, gryn, kärna:</text:span></text:span> tritici; fici, C.; papaveris; punica; uvæ, Ov.; ciceris, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grānāria</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sädes-magasin, -loft:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grānātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kornwis, korn för korn:</text:span> legere, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grānātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">försedd med l. full af korn:</text:span> malum (= m. Punicum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">granatäpple),</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grāneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af korn, gryn:</text:span> (puls), Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grānĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bär korn l. frön:</text:span> formicæ, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grānōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af kärnor:</text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grăphĭcus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skicklig i målarekonsten; konstfärdig): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Slug, fintlig, fiffig:</text:span></text:span> servus; fur, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăphĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: id.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăphĭcē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ritkonst:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pergrăphĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mycket fiffig, fintlig:</text:span></text:span> sycophanta, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăphis</text:span>, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ritkonst:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăphĭum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skrif-stift, griffel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af jern l. ben, hwarmed man skref i wax):</text:span> Ov.; Cæsar Cassii brachium trajecit g-o, Su. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăphiārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: theca <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwari skrifstift förwaras),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăphiārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: id.: Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Grass . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gradior.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grātus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T3">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Behaglig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: (egnad att behaga) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Full af behag, täck; angenäm:</text:span></text:span> <text:soft-page-break/>protervitas Glyceræ; g-a Venus; conviva<text:span text:style-name="T3">;</text:span> quies; hora, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. är någon till behag, till nöjes; s. wäl upptages, winner, beweker): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Behaglig, omtyckt, gynnad, kär, ljuf:</text:span></text:span> hæc (spectacula) pueris et mulierculis g-a sunt (gravibus viris non item); hæc opera g-a multis et ad obstringendos homines beneficiis accommodata; beneficia mutua et g-a; officia g-a; populo g-a est tabella, quæ frontes aperit hominum, voluntates tegit; id mihi g-um fuit; facere alicui g-um, g-simum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till nöjes, ett nöje),</text:span> C.; beneficium g-um, Pt.; g. alicui, Sa.; lex in vulgus g-a, L.; g-um opus (Georgica) agricolis; g-ior est pulcro veniens in corpore virtus; tellus g-a Nereidum matri, Vg.; donec g-us eram tibi, Persarum vigui rege beatior; g-ae divitibus vices; Choerilus g. fuit Alexandro, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T3">act.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tacksam:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förbinder l. förwärfwar tacksamhet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">tacknämlig:</text:span></text:span> ea beneficia, quæ attingunt singulos, sunt etiam g-ora; dicendi facultas etiam g-ior et ornatior est, quam juris scientia, C.; Cs. b. G. VI, 16.; Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tacksam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">erkänsam:</text:span></text:span> perraro g-i homines reperiuntur; id quod tributum est viro bono et g-o, in eo quum ex ipso fructus est, tum ex ceteris; et re ipsa et animo g-simus; g. erga alqm; se præbere g-um in alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> alicui; g-o animo, g-ā memoriā prosequi aliquem, alicujus virtutem, C.; g-um memoremque cognosci, N.; g-us Camenā insigni referam, Hor.; g. adversus alqm, Ter., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tacksamt, med tacksamhet, med tacksamt sinne:</text:span></text:span> meminisse, facere alqd, C.; g-sime acceptum est, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātes</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blott i formen</text:span> grates; gratibus, T.), <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tacksägelse; tack (wedergällning):</text:span></text:span> diis g. agere, Pt., C., L., Ov.; g-bus prosequi alqm, T.; g. debere alicui, Pt.; persolvere dignas; referre, Vg.; habere, referre alicui pro aliqua re, Ct.; g. persolvere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om straff),</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Behag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i utseende l. sätt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">förmåga att behaga; skönhet, täckhet:</text:span></text:span> in adolescentulo erat magna g., N.; sermonis honos et g., Hor.; formæ, Ov., Ppt.; orationis, Qu.; villæ, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. personification: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gratie, Charit:</text:span></text:span> G. cum Nymphis geminisque sororibus, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ynnest, gunst:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. ngn hyser; concr.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ynnest-, gunstbewis</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (nåd):</text:span> g-am alicujus sibi conciliare; inire ab aliquo, colligere ex aliqua re; recipere alqm in g-am; g-am parere defensionibus; g-am fortunati et potentis hominis causæ inopis et optimi anteponere, C.; in g-am alicujus, facere alqd, L.; sequi, velle g-am alicujus, Cs.; in beneficii loco et g-æ petere; g-æ causa concedere alqd, C.; regum, Hor.; immensa, T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf:</text:span> facere alicui g-am alicujus rei = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">efterskänka ngn ngt, öfwerse med ngt hos ngn:</text:span> nullius mihi delicti g-am feci, Sa.; omnium tibi, quæ nefarie ausus es, g-am facio, L.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos</text:span> Com. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är</text:span> g-am facere alicui alcjs rei = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afråda ngn ngt,</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ynnest,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. ngn eger; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">omtyckthet, wänskap, popularitet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> personligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">inflytande:</text:span></text:span> nostrum nomen erat in g-a; ponere alqm in g-a apud aliquem; in præfectura summum gradum tenere dignitatis et g-æ; apud externos valere opibus et g-ā; ad opes augendas et ad g-am valet jurisperiti industria, C.; Dumnorix magnā apud plebem propter liberalitatem g-ā fuit; de ea, quam habebat, g-a desperabat, <text:soft-page-break/>Cs.; nec precibus nec g-ā neque pretio eum impellere potuerunt; omnis g., potentia, honos apud illos fuit, - nos vulgus fuimus, sine g-a, sine auctoritate, Sa. -; privatam g-am statim mereare, s. recipias T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ömsesidigt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Godt förhållande, wänskap, sämja:</text:span></text:span> cum bona g. hæc inter vos potius componantur, quam cum mala, Ter.; est mihi cum eo magna g.; in g-am redire <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(försonas)</text:span> cum aliquo; in g-am cum aliquo reducere, reconciliare, restituere alqm, C.; fratrum quoque g. rara est, Ov.; g. male sarta rescinditur, Hor. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tycke</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för en sak:</text:span> quae g. curruum armorumque fuit vivis, - eadem sequitur tellure repostos, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tacksamhet, tacksägelse, tack:</text:span></text:span> leve onus est beneficii g.; quid præstabilius est eloquentiā vel spe indigentium vel g-ā eorum, qui defenduntur? dissimilis est pecuniæ debitio et g-æ. Nam - qui g-am refert <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wisar i handling),</text:span> habet <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hyser),</text:span> et qui habet, in eo ipso refert; magnam g-am diis, senectuti habeo; cogitare g-am; g-as agere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hembära tack, tacka)</text:span> alicui magnas, maximas, immortales (C.), magnas, miras, mirificas, (Ter.), justissimas alicui pro re, propter rem; quod ita egit, qui ita egerit; g-rum actio; nullum officium referendā g-ā magis necessarium est; sin erunt merita, ut non ineunda, sed referenda g. sit, major opus est diligentia; pro meritis referre g-am; tribuere g-am, C.; repetere g-am ab aliquo, L.; C.; g. dis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tack ware),</text:span> Ov. (Met. VII. 511); bene apud memores nostri stat g. facti, Vg.<text:span text:style-name="T3">;</text:span> major alicui debetur g., Hor.; g-as agere, T.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">abl.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T3">sing.</text:span> alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> alicujus rei <text:span text:style-name="T3">gratia</text:span> (gratiā alicujus rei, Qu.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">För - skull:</text:span></text:span> bestiæ hominum g-ā generatæ sunt; eum honoris g-ā nomino, C.; probri g-ā motus e senatu, Sa.; hujus accusandi gratiā, N.; dolorum fugiendorum g-ā, C.; si, exempli g-ā, vir bonus - - frumenti numerum advexerit - -; verbi g-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till exempel),</text:span> C. - meā g-ā, Pt.; id eā g-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för den skull)</text:span> eveniebat, quod -, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T3">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">gratiis</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">gratis;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af gunst, godhet; göra l. få ngt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utan wedergällning; för intet:</text:span></text:span> dare alicui alquid, Pt., adjicere, Ter.; virtutes g. diligere; g. habitare in alieno, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātĭfĭcor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wisa ynnest, artighet, nåd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mot ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">göra ngn en tjenst, tjena;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bewilja, skänka, offra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt:</text:span> in suffragiis populo potestas honeste bonis g-andi datur; g-atur mihi gestu accusator; deus nihil cuiquam g-ans; de eo, quod superest, aliis g-ri; liberalis g-andi voluntas; g-ri cuipiam, quod obsit illi, cui prodesse velle videantur; cur hoc tibi non g-er, nescio, C.; potentiæ paucorum decus ac libertatem suam g-ri, Sa.; pro Romanis alqd, L.; populo alqd; inter se, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātĭfĭcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gunst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">nådesbewisning:</text:span></text:span> impudens g. cum acerba injuria conjungitur; in imbecillitate g-em et benevolentiam ponere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gratiis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gratia 4. b.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. eger, winner l. söker att winna ynnest) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Omtyckt, populär, inflytelserik; förbindlig, artig:</text:span></text:span> homines potentes, g-i, diserti; esse alicui g-um; erat ut argentarius apud omnes ordines g.; in sua civitate g-us; - g-i scribæ sunt in dando et cedendo loco, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Gratis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gratia 4. b.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lyckönska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">glädjas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngn:</text:span> g-re sorori; g-atur (sc. eos esse) reduces, Vg.; cupimus - tuum sequentes currum Jovis templum g-ntes ovantesque adire, L.; g. mihi, quod <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till att)</text:span> (Met. IX, 244); g-are et tura libens aræ pone, Ov. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på dessa 2 sista ställen enl. soml.</text:span> = gratias agere); complexus eum incolumem fore g-atur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātanter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under lyckönskan l. glädjebetygelser:</text:span> Cp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātuītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> (-ĭtus, St.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. fås l. göres för intet, s. fås till skänks, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Friwillig, fri; ointresserad; - gjord för intet, onyttig:</text:span></text:span> liberalitas; amicitia; suffragia, C.; hospitium, Pn. - g. furor multitudinis; - ne g-a præterita parricidia essent, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātuīto</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utan lön, för intet; för sakens egen skull, utan att hafwa fördel deraf:</text:span></text:span> causas defendere g., C.; g. malus et crudelis erat, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātŭlor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lyckönska, betyga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">alicui</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sin </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">glädje</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till ngt, öfwer ngns lycka,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">aliquid</text:span>): g-er tibi an timeam, nescio; te mihi g-ri, quam gratias agere malim; felicitati tuæ g-or; affinitate, de filia, in alqua re g-ri alicui; Ciceroni recuperatam libertatem g-tus est Brutus, C.; Mettus Tullo devictos hostes g-atur, L.; pro ingenio alicui g., Pn.; g-or tibi, quod abes, quod te - summa laus prosecuta est, C.; Cs. b. G. I. 30; tibi g., ingenium tuum non latuisse, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hembära tacksägelse; tacka:</text:span></text:span> diis, Enn., Ter., Cato apud C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātŭlābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lyckönskande, med lyckönskningar:</text:span></text:span> multitudo g-a se effudit, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātŭlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lyckönskan, -ning, glädjebetygelse:</text:span></text:span> sera; gratiis agendis et g-bus habendis celebrari; parenti adjumento in periculis, g-i in victoria fuit, C.; defungi mutua g-e, Ct. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tacksägelsefest:</text:span></text:span> diis ad omnia templa alicujus nomine g-em facere; decernere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om folket)</text:span> alicui reipublicæ conservatæ g-em; donare alicui unius diei g-em, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grātŭlātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: epistola, Cp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congrātŭlor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Glädjas med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">betyga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn sin </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">glädje, lyckönska:</text:span></text:span> c., quia fortiter pugnavi, Pt.; alicui libertatem restitutam, L. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förut på 3 ställen hos</text:span> C., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">der nu läses</text:span> gratulari).<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congrātŭlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lyckönskan:</text:span></text:span> Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Obehaglig, oangenäm:</text:span></text:span> mihi tarda fluunt i-aque tempora, Hor.; joci, Ov.; sapor, Col.; virus, Pn.; oratio, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Otacksam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= s. ej hyser eller wisar tacksamhet):</text:span> i-i animi crimen horreo; nihil cognovi i-ius; patria i.; i in alqm, C.; haec tulit i-os seges et feret omnibus annis, Hor.; homo i-simus, Vell.; adversus deos, Gell.; ager, Mt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Otacksam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= hwarför man ej får tack l. lön):</text:span> sin (officia) i-a esse sentiam, non committam, ut insanire videar, C.; labor, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingrāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Obehagligt, utan behag:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Otacksamt:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingrātia</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">abl. plur.</text:span> -<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingrātiis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Emot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns (sin) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wilja; motwilligt:</text:span></text:span> amborum i-is, Pt.; tuis i., Ter.; extorquendum est invito et i., C.; i. cogi ad depugnandum, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingrātĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Otacksam:</text:span></text:span> Acc. apud C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕringrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ganska otacksam:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pergrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ganska angenäm:</text:span></text:span> p-um nobis feceris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ett stort nöje),</text:span> si explicaris, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gravanter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gravo, Gravis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gravastellus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: (Pt. Epid. V. 1. 14. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl. gißning = grå</text:span> ɔ: ravastellus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> ravus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gravat . . ., Grave . . ., Gravid . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gravis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grăvis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tung:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i kroppslig mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wäger mycket:</text:span> onus, Cs., Hor.; aes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fullwigtigt);</text:span> imbre nubes, L.; pondus auri; dona auro g-ia, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tung, tryckande:</text:span></text:span> cibus; g-e est æstate aureum amiculum, hieme frigidum; anni tempus, C.; g. ætas, Cs.; aura, Ov.; cælum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(luft),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tung, förtyngd, nedtyngd:</text:span></text:span> g. ætate, vino, somno; agmen rediit prædā g-e, L.; morbo; fetæ g-es, Vg.; somno; malis, annis g., Hor., Ov.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwande:</text:span></text:span> regina sacerdos Marte <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af Mars)</text:span> g., Vg. <text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om röst och toner: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Låg:</text:span></text:span> vocem ab acutissimo sono ad g-simum recipere; vox, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Swår</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (att bära och fördraga;</text:span> difficilis = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">swår att werkställa), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">betungande, tryckande, beswärlig, widrig:</text:span></text:span> iis omnis ætas g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en börda)</text:span> est; morbus; adversarius; bellum; odor; labor; periculum; sensus (naufragii); g-es communium temporum casus; vita otiosorum minus g. est aliis, C.; fortuna; volnus; dies alicui, Cs.; mors; fatum, Ov.; g-e virus, Hor.; non est mihi g-e honorem habere regi, N.; tunc sentina g., Juv.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sträng, hård:</text:span></text:span> senatus consultum vehemens et g.; g-ore nomine appellare; inimicitiæ; metus et terror domini g-simi; judicium g-ius subire, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wigtig, maktpåliggande, betydande, gällande, giltig:</text:span></text:span> quod judicium g-ius quam de libertate?, res g-es et utiles; studia g-ora et majora; artes g-ores <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> leviores); causa g-sima, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fast, stadig, allwarlig, allwarsam, stadgad, charactersfast, grundlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (solid):</text:span> imperium g-ius et stabilius, Ter.; nulla societas g-or, nulla carior; g. homo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> puer i et mulierculæ); g-es sententiæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> ridiculæ); g-simus et severissimus; civis g., constans, severus; g-es, constantes, stabiles in amicitia; Tib. Gracchus homo prudens et g.; honores et auctoritas mea g-ius alqd requirebat, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eftertrycklig, kraftig, werkande, -sam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. gör intryck, effect), i synnerhet om föredrag och framställning:</text:span> g-bus verbis, sapientibus sententiis ornata oratio; oratio g. et ornata; g-e carmen fundere; <text:soft-page-break/>ornatus in dicendo et g.; g. et magnus orator; g. apud populum oratio; in contrarium afferre, quod sit aut g-ius aut æque g-e, C.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wärdig, aktningswärd, trowärdig, ansedd, aktad:</text:span></text:span> amicitiæ ortus a natura, quam ab imbecillitate, g-ior et verior est; studia g-ora, quam nostra; testis, civitas g.; tam g-i oratoris nomine dignus, C.; historicus, N.; vir pietate ac meritis g., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvēdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tyngd i hufwudet, snufwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (influenza):</text:span> C., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvēdĭnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har anlag för snufwa:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förorsakar snufwa:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăveŏlens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: (oleo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Starkt, illa luktande:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvesco</text:span>, ĕre:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bli tung, nedtyngas:</text:span></text:span> nemus fetu, Vg.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bli hafwande:</text:span> cameli, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förswåras, förwärras:</text:span></text:span> mala publica, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tung, full,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absol. och af ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">lastad, proppad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> ubera, C.; arista, Vg.; messes; nubes, Ov.; pharetra sagittis, Hor.; pectus curis, Luc.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwande, drägtig:</text:span></text:span> virgo fit ex aliquo, Pt., Ter.; uxor, C.; uterus, T,; pecus, Vg., Ov.; terra semine, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvĭdĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwandeskap, drägtighet:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvĭdo</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Göra</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bli) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">fruktsam:</text:span></text:span> C., Aur. V.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tyngd, tunghet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> pondere et g-e moventur atomi, C.; oneris g., Ov.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egenskap att trycka l. kännas tung; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Det tryckande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngt; = känslan af tyngd, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">matthet, förtyngdhet:</text:span></text:span> caeli, C.; odoris, Pn.; membrorum, C., Lucr.; capitis; aurium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> audiendi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tung hörsel),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om uttalet) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hårdhet, grofhet:</text:span></text:span> linguæ g. et sonus vocis agrestis, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwandeskap:</text:span></text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Swårhet, beswärlighet:</text:span></text:span> morbi, C.; belli diuturnitas et g., L.; annonæ, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Allwar, stadga, fasthet; fasthet i grundsatser, character</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sfasthet):</text:span> constantis ætatis, vultus et morum; clemens castigatio g-e adjuncta; cum g-e constantiaque vivere; Catoni natura tribuit incredibilem g-em; g-em retinere, iracundiam pellere; senatus g. unius oratione convertitur; a g-e sapientis non recedere, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eftertryck, kraft:</text:span></text:span> verborum g. acris; omni sententiarum g-e - utendum est, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wärdighet, anseende:</text:span></text:span> genus hoc sermonum plus videtur habere g-is; quanta g., quanta in oratione majestas!, C.; Suevorum amplitudo et g., Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tungt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hårdt):</text:span> cadere, C., Lucr.; g. pellere fores; fores crepant, Ter.; ferire, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om ton) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Doft, lågt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hårdt, groft:</text:span></text:span> sonare g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> acute); verba inflata et exanimata g-ius, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Swårt, hårdt, strängt, häftigt, otåligt; djupt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om sorg, förtrytelse):</text:span> ægrotare; irasci; angi suis incommodis; mortem filii g. mærere; ferre alqd g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låta det gå sig till sinnes);</text:span> queri; accusare; dissentire inter se. C.; accipere alqd g., Ter.; dolere; ferre; vindicare in alqm, statuere in alqm g., Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Med fasthet, character; grundligt:</text:span></text:span> utrumque egit g.; g. et cum constantia vivere; multa non tam g. dixit, quam facete, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Med kraft, eftertryck:</text:span></text:span> g-sime et copiosissime dicere; Thucydides res gestas narrat g. et probe, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gravitudo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gravedo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăviuscŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">något djup:</text:span> sonus, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedtynga, trycka, falla ngn tung; beswära; förswåra:</text:span></text:span> poma ramos, Ov.; g-atus vino somnoque, L.; mens ebrietate g-atur, Ct.; subibo humeris neque me labor iste g-bit, Vg.; nihil moror officium, quod me g-at, Hor.; invidiam matris, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(finna ngt tungt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Göra swårigheter; icke lida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">tåla, förargas öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. på:</text:span> ego non g-rer, si mihi ipse confiderem; ne g-eris exædificare id opus, quod instituisti, C.; Cs. b. G. I. 33; Pegasus terrenum equitem g-tus, Hor.; civium aspectum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sky),</text:span> T.; matrem, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvanter</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvāte</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăvātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nödigt, med swårighet:</text:span></text:span> g-te ille (vendidit hortos); non g-te <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(willigt)</text:span> monstrare viam, C.; haud g-tim arma Rutulis junxit; haud g-ter ad Poenum venerunt (XXI. 24. 5.), L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aggrăvesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bli tyngre, förwärras:</text:span></text:span> morbus, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aggrăvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förtynga, nedtynga, trycka, beswära, förswåra:</text:span></text:span> pondus a-atur; odor capita a-at, Pn.; morbus eum, Su.; argumenta reum, Qu.; (si) res bello a-atæ (essent ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ställningen ytterligare förswårad),</text:span> L.; dolor a-atur, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēgrăvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tynga, trycka ned; beswära:</text:span></text:span> vitis ulmum, Ov.; partem navis ii d-ant, Pn.; opere laboris d-ri, Col.; illatis signis d-ant prope circumventum cornu; lassitudo et vulnera et pavor nantes d-at; vulnus consulem d-bat, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingrăvesco</text:span>, ĕre:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bli tung; bli matt:</text:span></text:span> id pondere, Pn., corpora defatigatione i-unt, animi se exercendo levantur; ætas i-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(årens tyngd ökas),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bli hafwande:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ökas:</text:span></text:span> studium, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förswåras, -wärras:</text:span></text:span> morbus; ardet furore et in dies i-it; annona, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingrăvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedtynga; förwärra, -swåra:</text:span></text:span> puppem, St.; hæc (verbis), Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pergrăvis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mycket betydande, kraftig, eftertrycklig:</text:span></text:span> testis, oratio, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pergrăvĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Swårt; eftertryckligt:</text:span></text:span> offensus; reprehendere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Praegrăvis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mycket tung, swår, beswärlig:</text:span></text:span> onus, Ov.; vino p., T.; caput; servitium, Pn.; imperium, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prægrăvĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mycket tung:</text:span></text:span> moles, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Praegrăvo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedtrycka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med öfwerwägande tyngd), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">betunga:</text:span></text:span> scuta telis p-ta; exonerare regnum p-ante multitudine, L.; corpus onustum animum p-at, Hor.; caput p-tum, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa öfwerwigt; öfwerwäga, -glänsa:</text:span></text:span> urit enim fulgore suo, qui p-at artes infra se positas, Hor.; pars deterior civitatis p-at, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subgrăvis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">något swår:</text:span> odor, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>răviscæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Etrurien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gravit . . ., Graviusculus, Gravo, -vor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gravis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>raupius mons, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Caledonien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Greg . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Grex.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grĕmium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sköte, (knä):</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> in g-o alqm ponere, Ter.; in g-o matris sedere, educari, C.; g-o accipere, fovere alqm, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttr.:</text:span> terra g-o mollito ac subacto semen excipit; e sinu g-oque patriæ abstrahi; Aetolia medio fere Græciæ g-o continetur, C.; Padus g-o montis - profluit, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gress . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">s</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">e</text:span> Gradior.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grex,</text:span> grĕgis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hjord, flock:</text:span></text:span> g-es armentorum, pecudum, equarum, C.; taurorum, Varr.; hædorum, Vg.; pecorum, Ov., Epicuri de g-e porcus; avium Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sluten </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Trupp, skara, sällskap</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af mskor, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">krets</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (parti, skola); någons </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">följe:</text:span></text:span> g-e facto cum telis irrumpere, Sa.; Epicurus una in domo magnos tenuit amicorum g-es; philosophorum g-es; sæpe exsistunt excellentiæ quædam, ut erat Scipio - in nostro g-e, C.; recipere alqm in suum g-em; ancillarum, Ter.; Chrysippi porticus et g., Hor.; Niobe extulit g-es natorum, Juv.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skådespelaretrupp:</text:span></text:span> Pt. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(prologen till</text:span> Asinaria), Ter.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hopen, massan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till anföraren l. framstående medlemmar):</text:span> in g-e patronorum annumerari, C.; pars melior indocili g-e, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grĕgālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: s. hör till hjorden:</text:span> equus, Varr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. hör till samma sällskap;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Subst.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kamrat:</text:span></text:span> Clodii g-es, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sådan som hopen l. hopens) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Simpel, wanlig, (gemen):</text:span></text:span> sagulum, L.; poma, Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grĕgārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af l. wid hjorden:</text:span> bos, L.; pastor, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är en ur hopen, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Simpel, gemen:</text:span></text:span> miles, C.; militia, Js.; poēta, Sid.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grĕgātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hjord-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">flockwis; hoptals:</text:span></text:span> elephanti g. ingrediuntur, Pn.; graculi g. volant, Qu.; cives Romani g. conjecti in lautumias, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aggrĕgo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(adgrĕgo), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sälla, sluta, samla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngn l. ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">upptaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ett samfund, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">räkna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till en klaß:</text:span> se ad amicitiam alicujus, Cs.; alqm in numerum amicorum a.; naufragos undique collectos eodem a.; ego te semper in nostrum numerum a. soleo; voluntatem suam ad dignitatem alicujus (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">söka bidraga till - -),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congrex</text:span>, ĕgis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. hör till samma hjord s. flock, samfund:</text:span> Ap., Sol.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congrĕgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammanföra till en hjord</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ett samfund;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">sluta sig tillsammans, bilda förening</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">samfund;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">samla, förena:</text:span></text:span> feræ se, Pn.; apium examina c-antur, quia naturā congregabilia sunt; homines naturā c-ti; dispersos homines in unum locum c.; pares cum paribus facillime c-antur; homines cum æqualibus se libenter; multitudo ex servis c-ta, C.; verba idem significantia c., Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congrĕgābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har anlag l. drift till att bilda samfund:</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congrĕgātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammanslutning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till samfund); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hopsamlande:</text:span></text:span> hominum, C.; criminum, Qn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ēgrĕgius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utwald ur hopen), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utmärkt, utomordentlig, förträfflig; - ärofull:</text:span></text:span> forma; facies, Ter.; color; indoles ad discendum; opus; e. in laude bellica; civis; poēta, C.; facinus, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i ironisk men.:</text:span> testes, C.; laus, Vg.; - mihi e-um erat Pompeji subolem in meos penates adsciscere, T. -<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ēgrĕgie</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utmärkt wäl, förträffligt, utomordentligt:</text:span></text:span> loqui Græce; placere; pingere; fidelis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sēgrex</text:span>, ĕgis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sēgrĕgus</text:span> (Aus.), <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Enslig, ensam:</text:span></text:span> vita, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sēgrĕgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afsöndra, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Afskilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (från en hjord l. ett samfund), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">skilja, utmönstra, utesluta, söndra:</text:span></text:span> oves, Phdr.; e senatu alqm, Pt.; a se aliqum, Pac., Ter.; e numero civium; a communi tamquam humanitatis corpore; virtutem a summo bono; comitatu, C.; culpam a se <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(aflägsna),</text:span> Pt.; pugnam Curiatiorum Horatius, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grīphus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nät), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gåta:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grōma</text:span> <text:line-break/>(gruma), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Landtmätarestång:</text:span></text:span> Fs.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grōmātĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: disciplina <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Subst.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Grōmātĭca, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>), Hyg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grossus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Omoget fikon:</text:span></text:span> cocti, Cato; crudæ, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grossŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>rudii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt folkslag.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gruma <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Groma.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grūmus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tufwa, jordhög:</text:span></text:span> Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grūmŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>rūnĭum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ort i Phrygien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grunnio,</text:span> 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grymta:</text:span></text:span> porcus, Varr., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grunnītus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grymt, -ande:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Degrunnio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grymta:</text:span></text:span> Phdr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">(Gruo,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obr. stamverb., identiskt med</text:span> ruo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss.</text:span> gnosco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> nosco?)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congruo</text:span>, ui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sammanfalla):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammanträffa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i tid, rum, sak):</text:span> centra, Pn.; menses diesque cum solis ratione, C.; forte c-rat, ut - cædes nuntiarentur, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammanstämma, stämma öfwerens, förlikas med:</text:span></text:span> sensus nostri c-unt; de ceteris inter se; ejus sermo cum tuis literis; hæc inter se c-unt; cum alicujus moribus et natura; cum virtute semper c.; lex cum judicio; principiis c-re debent ea, quæ sequuntur, C.; mulier mulieri magis, Ter.; sermo inter omnes c-bat; expositos jussu regis infantes sciebat et tempus, quo eos sustulisset, ad id c-bat, L.; oratio sententiæ, N.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Passa för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> non omni causæ c-it unum orationis genus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congruens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerensstämmande, enlig; passande; samstämmig, wäl proportionerad, symmetrisk:</text:span></text:span> gestus cum verbis; oratio sententiis c-ns; vita cum disciplina; genus dicendi aptum et c. C.; c-ia ad consulem deferre; c. clamor a Romanis, dissonæ illis, ut discrepantibus linguis, voces, L.; membris c., Su. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congruenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Enligt; i öfwerensstämmelse med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> dicere ad id, quod agitur, apte et c.; c. naturæ vivere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congruentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerensstämmelse, proportion:</text:span></text:span> morum, Su.; membrorum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incongruens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Opassande, orimlig:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congruus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerensstämmande:</text:span></text:span> sermo cum aliquo, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incongruus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Opassande:</text:span></text:span> Val. Max. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incongrue</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingruo</text:span>, ui 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Falla, störta, komma in på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">öfwer; nalkas, påkomma, träffa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer:</text:span> Aeneas Italis, Vg.; hostis, T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker:</text:span> clades in alqm; morbi in remiges i-runt; i-ens periculum; i-entis vis fortunæ, L.; horror armorum i-it; imber, Vg.; radii solis; morbi iis; senium, Pn.; frigus; æstas, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grūs</text:span> <text:line-break/>(gruis, Phdr.), gruis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f. m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Trana:</text:span></text:span> una g.; grues volantes trianguli efficiunt formam, C., membra gruis sparsi sale multo, Hor.; mansuefactæ, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gry̆</text:span> (γρῦ): ne g. quidem = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">icke det ringaste:</text:span></text:span> Pt. (Most. 595 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ritschl.).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gryllus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gräshoppa:</text:span></text:span> Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">comisk målning, l. figur:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gryllo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om gräshoppornas läte):</text:span> Carm. Phil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>rȳnēa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Grȳnēum, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ställe i Mysien.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grȳnēus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">binamn till Apollo.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gryps,</text:span> grȳphis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grȳphus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grip,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fabeldjur, lejon och örn i ett):</text:span> Vg., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gŭbernum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Styre</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på fartyg, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">roder:</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">plur.</text:span>), Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gŭbernio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gŭbernius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Styrman:</text:span></text:span> Isid.; Laberius ap. Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gŭberno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Styra:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: fartyg:</text:span> nautæ inter se certant, quis potissimum g-et, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Styra, leda, bestämma:</text:span></text:span> equum, Mt.; orbem terrarum Sulla; nobis rem publicam g-antibus togæ arma cesserunt; hæc fortuna viderit, quoniam ratio non g-at; alqm suis consiliis; fortunæ motum ratione; alqd prudentiā suā; hæc in casu sita temporibus g-antur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:bookmark-start text:name="_Hlk144223412"/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gŭbernācŭlum</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Gŭbernāclum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Styre, roder:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> naufragus exceptus accessit ad g-um, C.; ipse g-clo subit, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttr.:</text:span> ad g-a reipublicæ sedere; g. reip. tractare; civitatum regendarum g-a oratori tradere; a g-is civitatum repellere oratorem; a g-is recedere, C.; vitæ, Pn. <text:bookmark-end text:name="_Hlk144223412"/><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gŭbernātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Styrande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. om fartyg:</text:span> nec g-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(konsten att styra)</text:span> nec medicinæ sapientia similis est, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Styrelse, ledning:</text:span></text:span> summi imperii g-e districtus; tanturum rerum g. vix humani consilii est; cupiditas consilii g-e regatur, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gŭbernātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Styrman, styresman, styrare:</text:span></text:span> g. tenens clavum in puppi sedet; custodes g-esque reipublicæ, C.; equorum, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gŭbernātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">styrarinna, ledarinna:</text:span> præclara g. civitatum eloquentia, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Adgŭberno</text:span> <text:line-break/>(aggŭberno), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Styra:</text:span></text:span> Fl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōgŭbernātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Understyrman:</text:span></text:span> Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>ugerni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">germaniskt folkslag.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gŭla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Strupe:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> obtortā g-ā in vincula abripi; g-am digitulis oblidere, C.; <text:soft-page-break/>laqueo g-am frangere, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. ss. smakens läckerhetens, fråsseriets organ: sw. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gom, läckergom, swalg;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> meton. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">fråsseri, swalg och dryckenskap:</text:span></text:span> o insulsam g-am!, C.; eamus, quo ducit g., Hor.; subtilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fin),</text:span> Col.; quanta g., quæ totos sibi ponat apros!, Juv.; g-æ irritamenta; Vitellius ventre et g-ā sibi inhonestus; T.; explere profundam g-am, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gŭlo</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Läckergom, -mun:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gŭlōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Glupsk, fråssande:</text:span></text:span> Juv.; lector, Mt.,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gŭlōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kräsligt, läckert:</text:span></text:span> condire, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēgŭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fråssa upp:</text:span> Char. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēgŭlātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gumen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gummi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gŭmia,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fråssare:</text:span></text:span> Lucil. ap. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gummi,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">def. n.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gummis</text:span> <text:line-break/>(cummis), is <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span> <text:line-break/>(gūmen, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: Pall.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gummi, harts, kåda:</text:span></text:span> optimum; liquida, crassa, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gummātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hartsig:</text:span></text:span> Pall.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gummeus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: id.: Aus.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gummĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gifwa från sig gummi:</text:span> Pall.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gummītio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hartsning:</text:span></text:span> Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gummōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kådig:</text:span></text:span> folia, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gumnasium, Gunæceum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gymnasium, Gynæceum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gurdus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tölpig, dum:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gurges,</text:span> ĭtis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wattenhwirfwel, afgrund;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> poet.: i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">upprördt haf, watten, wågor:</text:span></text:span> turbidus; altus Vg.; imus, Pn.; flumineus, Mt.; quæ Charybdis tantos potest exhaurire g-tes?, C.; apparent rari nantes in g-e vasto, Vg.; qui g. aut quæ flumina lugubris ignara belli?, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Afgrund, djup; slukare:</text:span></text:span> vitiorum; g. et vorago; ille g. et helluo; g. et vorago patrimonii, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ēgurgĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fråssa upp:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingurgĭto</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Indoppa, sänka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i -:</text:span> se in merum, Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerlasta, berusa:</text:span></text:span> se, C.; alqm poculis, Ap. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Dränka, sänka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">fördjupa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">se i. in rem,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berusa sig med fråssa i njutningen af -:</text:span> in flagitia se; in copias Pompeji se, C.; ingenium ingentibus poculis, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gurgŭlio,</text:span> ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Luftrör, -strupe:</text:span></text:span> g. est exercitor, Pt. Trin. 1016; Varr. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.</text:span> = cauda: Ps.<text:line-break/>b. = curculio, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kornmask:</text:span></text:span> Pall.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gurgustium</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gurgustiŏlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Koja, kyffe:</text:span></text:span> Su., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gustum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förrätt, smakrätt:</text:span></text:span> (Apic.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gustus,</text:span> us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Smak:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. sinne:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> hoc non magis arte <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medelst theori)</text:span> traditur, quam g. aut odor, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> facinorosi veræ laudis g-um non habent, C.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Smakande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> panis bonitatem g-u explorare, Col.; minister epulas g-u explorare solitus, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">concret: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förrätt- appetitsrätt:</text:span></text:span> hæc satis sunt in g-u, Mt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Försmak; prof:</text:span></text:span> g-um tibi dare volui, Sen.; versificationis nostræ g-um tibi negare nolui, Col.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Smak,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som en sak eger:</text:span> acutus et odoratus; salsus, Pn.; vilis; nobilis Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gusto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Smaka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt l. på ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> leporem g. fas non putant, Cs.; biduum ne aquam quidem g-veram; uva peracerba g-tu, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Äta en bit</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. mellanmål, före den egentliga måltiden:</text:span> post lavationem dormiebat, deinde g-bat, Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Smaka, pröfwa; få smak på:</text:span></text:span> nondum g-verat vitæ suavitatem; philosophiam, physiologiam primis labris; sanguinem civilem, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gustātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: = gustum: Petr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gustātōrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bricka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarpå förrätten framsättes; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">förrätt,</text:span></text:span> Pn. Ep. VI. 2. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gustātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Smak:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. sinne:</text:span> g. est ex omnibus sensibus maxime voluptarius, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Smak</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos en sak:</text:span> pomorum jucundus non g. solum, sed etiam odoratus et aspectus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēgusto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Smaka af, läppja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt: </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> vinum, Cato; novas fruges, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lätt beröra, öfwerfara, snudda wid:</text:span></text:span> ignis alqd, Lucr.; volnere corpus, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngt litet </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Pröfwa, göra bekantskap med, röna:</text:span></text:span> vitam meam; convivam; mentes sensusque alicujus; exercitationem; ex ejus sermone paulum speculæ d-arat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hemtat);</text:span> pauca licet ex altercatione nostra d-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(höra),</text:span> C.; etiam tu, Galba, quandoque imperium d-bis, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingustābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Som ej kan smakas, ätas:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingustātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ej smakad:</text:span></text:span> ilia rhombi, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Praegusto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förut smaka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på:</text:span> cibos, Pn.; pocula, Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Praegustātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Munskänk:</text:span></text:span> Su. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> libidinum tuarum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕgusto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Smaka (äta) om igen, ideligen, (idisla):</text:span></text:span> bilem suam, Sen.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: ständigt njuta ånyo:</text:span> laudationem alicujus; crebro literas, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gutta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Droppe, stänk:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> g-am haud habeo sanguinis (exanimatus); vini, Pt.; g-æ imbrium; in cadentibus g-is numerum notare possumus, C.; g. cavat Iapidem, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fläck:</text:span></text:span> paribus lita corpora g-is, Vg.; cærulea, Ov. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ett grand, något litet:</text:span></text:span> consilii, Pt.; dulcedinis g. stillat in cor, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Guttātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fläckig:</text:span></text:span> gallicæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(perlhöns):</text:span> Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Guttātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Droppwis:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Guttŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Liten droppe:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Guttur,</text:span> ŭris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span> Pt.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Strupe, (hals); kräfwa:</text:span></text:span> thermopotasti g-em; vinum nimis calidum erat, amburebat g-em, Pt.; vitium ventris et g-is (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fråsseri o. dryckenskap),</text:span> C.; frangere senile patris g. Hor.; rarum magni g-is exemplum; quis tumidum g. miratur in Alpibus?, Juv.; tentare g. avis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gutturnium,</text:span> ”vas, ex quo aqua in manus datur”, Paul. Diac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Guttus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Flaska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med trång hals:</text:span> quī vinum dabant, ut minutatim funderent, a guttis g-um appellarunt: in hujusce locum in conviviis - successit epichysis; in sacrificiis remansit g., Varr.; cum patera g., Campana supellex, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>y̆ăros, i, <text:line-break/>(Gy̆ăra, æ Juv.), <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö i Archipelagen:</text:span> Vg. – </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>y̆as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>y̆es, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en rese:</text:span> centimanus, Hor. Od. III. 3.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en Trojan:</text:span> Vg. - <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>y̆ges, is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> æ, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lydisk kung:</text:span> C., Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gymnas,</text:span> ădis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppsöfning:</text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gymnăsĭum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gymnasium,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> offentlig anläggning egentl. för kroppsöfningar enligt grekiskt sätt: wanligen en park med portiker, öppna platser</text:span> (areæ), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gångar</text:span> (spatia), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prydda af berömda minnesstoder, grafmonument m. m.:</text:span> nobilissimum orbis terrarum g. Academiæ, C.; Timoleon sepultus est in g-o, N. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">I dessa g. började snart philosopher och andre lärdomsidkare hålla föredrag och underwisa:</text:span> hoc tempore omnia g-a philosophi tenent; clamabunt omnia g-a et philosophorum scholæ, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos Romarne war för motswarande anläggningar ordet</text:span> g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">aldrig nationelt</text:span> (horti, thermæ), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ej heller förekommer det någonsin i betydelsen af läro- l. underwisningsanstalt i allm., utan deß bruk förblifwer inskränkt till de </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">grekiska</text:span></text:span> gymnasia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i deras trefaldiga bestämmelse af palæstror, skolor och offentliga promenader l. förlustelseställen), och sådana directa efterbildningar (i miniature) af dessa, som t. ex. Ciceros</text:span> g. superius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> inferius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på hans</text:span> Tusculanum.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gymnnăsiarchus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gymnnăsiarcha</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">föreståndare för ett gymnasium:</text:span> C., Val. M.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gymnastĭcus</text:span> (Pt.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gymnĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till kroppsöfningar hörande, i kroppsöfningar bestående (gymnisk):</text:span> ludi g-nici, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gymnŏsŏphista</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">indisk wis:</text:span> Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gy̆naecēum</text:span> <text:line-break/>(gunæceum, Pt.), ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gy̆næcōnītis</text:span>, ĭdis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Frustuga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (den inre, af qwinnorna bebodde delen af ett grekiskt hus):</text:span> g-um, Pt. Most., C.; g-tis, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gypsum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gips:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gypso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gipsa; belägga med gips:</text:span></text:span> vasa, Col.; manus g-tæ (histrionis, qui Medeam agebat, candoris causā), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gȳrus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Krets, ring,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ringbana):</text:span> g-um trahit draco; ingenti g-o volat avis, Vg.; cogere equum in g-um; miluus per aëra ducit g-os, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttr.:</text:span> in exiguum g-um compellere oratorem; homines sibi præfidentes debent in g-um rationis et doctrinæ duci, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gȳrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rundad:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gȳrīnus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grod-rom:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕgȳro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kretsa, göra en swäng tillbaka:</text:span> bellum in Hispaniam r-vit, Fl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">G</text:span>y̆thēum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gy̆thīum, i. <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hamn i Laconien:</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>Gy̆theātes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ha,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hahe</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hahæ</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hahahe</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Interj.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för skratt:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hăbēna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> habeo? = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det, hwari l. hwarmed något hålles?):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rem:</text:span></text:span> fundæ, St.; soleæ, Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tygel, töm:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttryck:</text:span> læva, Hor.; laxas dare h-as; flectere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(styra, länka),</text:span> Vg., Ov.; non audit currus h-as, Ov.; laxare, Ct.; adducere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(draga åt),</text:span> Vfl.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bilder:</text:span> commodum est quam laxissimas habere h-as amicitiæ, quas vel adducas, quum velis, vel remittas; legum validæ h-æ te repriment; regendi sui potestatem quasi quasdam h-as tradere alicui, C.; rerum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(statens),</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hăbeo,</text:span> ui, ĭtum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa; hålla:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ega, innehafwa, hafwa i sin ego, besitta, rå om:</text:span></text:span> societas hominum divellitur, si suum cuique h-re non licet; non sunt duo milia civium, qui rem h-ant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ega ngt, hafwa förmögenhet),</text:span> C.; agrum, Ter; fines proprios, Cs.; amor sceleratus h-di, Vg., Ov.; vectigalia, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på sig, hos sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i händerna o. s. w.:</text:span> fenum h-et in <text:soft-page-break/>cornu, Hor.; equus h-et apes in juba; terra ad digitos lentescit h-do; h-do aptat ensem; arma h. humeris, Vg.; anulus in digito subter tenuatur h-do, Lucr.; ignes h-ent in pectore equi, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bebo, innehafwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett hus, ett land o. s. w.; (arch.) absol. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bo:</text:span></text:span> ubi nunc h-et adolescens?; Syracusis h-et; Pt.; urbem Romam a principio Trojani h-uere; Gætuli Africam h-ent; scelesti (apud inferos) loca tætra, inculta, foeda h-ent, Sa.; Capuam, L.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa i sitt wåld, hålla besatt, beherrska:</text:span></text:span> arcem h-ent Sabini scelere emptam, L.; urbem Romam a principio reges h-uere; Hispaniæ tribus legionibus h-bantur, T.; muros; moenia, Vg.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hålla, sköta:</text:span></text:span> quid faciat lætas segetes, qui cultus h-do sit pecori, expediam, Vg. Georg. I. 1.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ett ställe:</text:span> castris; in custodia, Sa.; castris æstivis tres simul legiones h-bantur, T.<text:line-break/>7. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sakliga subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa, hysa, omsluta, innefatta:</text:span></text:span> te, pater, pontus h-et Libyæ, Vg.; quidquid h-et dives, circumspice, mundus; cæruleos h-et unda deos, Ov.; barbiton hic paries h-bit; nulla taberna h-et meos libellos, Hor.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i inre och allmännare mening: <text:line-break/>1. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa i sitt wåld, beherrska, ega:</text:span></text:span> animus agit atque h-et cuncta, ipse non h-etur, Sa.; nos Amaryllis h-et; somnus animalia h-bat, Vg.; h-et mortalia casus, Luc.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwerhufwud om concreta l. abstracta object, hwilka på något sätt tillhöra l. äro till för subjectet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa, få, ega:</text:span></text:span> quando h-o multos cognatos, quid mihi opus est liberis?, Pt.; h-es a patre munus; h-es epilogum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(här har du l. se här epilogen);</text:span> ratione nihil a diis melius h-emus; secum h. alqm; nomen aliquod h.; in manibus h-emus virtutem Scipionis; sibi h-ant talos, sibi tesseras; h. aditum ad rem, tempus; commercium cum aliquo; multa et varia spectacula in cælestibus locis animus h-turus est; h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(någon),</text:span> cui narret, a quo accipiat alqd, C.; h-ent legibus sanctum, si quid quis de rep. acceperit, uti ad magistratus deferat; non h-ent <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(någre),</text:span> quibus vendant, Cs.; quid Jove majus h-emus?, Ov.; partem in opere; non, quod speraret <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ngt hopp),</text:span> h-bat, Vg.; nil h-o, quod agam, Hor. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">weta, kunna:</text:span></text:span> non h-o, quid agam, Ter.; si ad intelligendum non omnia h-o, quæ vellem, tamen utar his, quæ h-o; quid respondeam, non h-o; nihil (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">intet skäl)</text:span> h-o, quod vobis succenseam; ultra quo progrediar, quam ut veri similia videam, non habeo; de rep. nihil h-o ad te scribere, C.; incipe, si quid h-es, Vg.; h. melius suadere, Hor. Epod. 16. 23.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med object af egenskaper, werkningar o. s. w. hos</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personliga subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa:</text:span></text:span> qui unam h-et, omnes h-et virtutes; propinquitas ad animos jungendos minus h-et firmitatis; videat, non solum quam res honesta sit, sed etiam ut h-at efficiendi facultatem; h. comitatem sermonis, benevolentiam; libidinem procreandi; notitiam dei; infinitam memoriam, C.; bonum animum, L.; nullane h-es vitia?; Sardus h-bat ille Tigellius hoc, Hor.; virtus clara atque æterna h-etur (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är en herrlig och ewig besittning),</text:span> Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakliga object = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">föra med sig, medföra, skänka, fordra</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det ligger i);</text:span> h-et opportunitates maximas amicitia; res h-et multum utilitatis; severitas h-et gravitatem; ea agamus, quæ h-ent levationem ægritudinum; res h-et invidiam, lætitiam, infamiam, <text:soft-page-break/>molestiam, delectationem, utilitatem; res nihil vitii h-et, C.; ea res h-uit deformitatem, N.; non h-et victoria laudem, Vg.; creditur, ex medio quia res arcessit, h-re sudoris minimum, sed h-et comoedia tanto plus oneris, quanto veniæ minus, Hor.; pacem vultus h-et, Ov.; bella geri placuit nullos h-tura triumphos, Luc.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med object, som utmärka en inre l. yttre handling: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hålla, hysa, förehafwa, göra:</text:span></text:span> viam h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(styra)</text:span> ad aliquem, Pt.; orationem, disputationem, delectum, quæstionem, rationem; fidem h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hysa, sätta till)</text:span> alicui, Cs.; h. spem de aliquo; opinionem; gratiam alicui; sensum h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa)</text:span> rei; delectum rerum; rationem hominum; censum; deliberationem; sermonem; h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla)</text:span> senatum, C.; frequens senatus jam poterit haberier, Pt.; spem in armis h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bygga);</text:span> concilium Vg.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med object, hwilka utmärka ngt, för hwilket subjectet är föremål: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa; få, träffas af:</text:span></text:span> febrim; res h-uit malum eventum; h. querelam, timorem, odium; h. judicium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ligga under -),</text:span> C.; res h-uit suspicionem, N.; poenam, L.; (hoc) h-et = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">han har fått det (eg. om en sårad gladiator), han är träffad,</text:span> Ter., Vg.<text:line-break/>7. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bestämning för den egenskap l. det sätt l. det tillstånd, hwari objectet (i passiv construction subjectet) eges, hafwes, hålles:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med substantivum ss. prædicatsnomen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hafwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt i ngn l. ngt:</text:span> Crassum h-o generum, ne rhetoricoteros tu sis, Lucil. ap. C.; h-es somnum imaginem mortis; - tum intellexisse, quos h-isset amicos fidos, quos infidos, C.; h. alqm præceptorem, collegam, obtrectatorem; Agesilaus h-rat naturam fautricem in fingendis animi virtutibus, N.; hanc h-o sedem, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med prædicatsbestämning af adj. l. partic.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa, hålla;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">part. præt. pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ofta blott uttryckande den fulländade handlingen ss. ett ännu </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">warande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tillstånd:</text:span> h. animum alienum ab aliquo; h. laxas habenas; res eum sollicitum h-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(håller honom i oro);</text:span> h. rem perspectam, cognitam, spectatam, expertam, absolutam, compertam; Sullam mortuum h-emus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(S. äro wi af med);</text:span> domitas h. libidines (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hålla i styr),</text:span> C.; compertum h. alqd, Cs.; notum, Ov.; carum h. alqm, N.; periculum non occultum h-bat, Sa.; res me h-et anxium, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stundom i pass. hos</text:span> Sa. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Vg. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">föga mera än ett</text:span> esse: Cato clarus et magnus h-etur, Sa.; mons, qui nunc Albanus h-etur, Vg. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med prædicatsnomen = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hålla, anse, akta, taga för, räkna för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sällan hos de bäste prosaister i activum):</text:span> natura nobis insculpsit in animis, ut deos æternos et beatos h-remus; illa prima et summa h-emus, utilitatis nomen non tam splendidum, quam necessarium ducimus; eum nos ut perveterem h-emus (Brut. § 61); Themistocles quum recusaret lyram, h-tus est indoctior, C.; Atticus bonus pater familias h-batur, N.; humanis hostiis litare fas h-ent Germani, T.; h-et hos numeratque poētas, Hor. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt märkes:</text:span> satis habere = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Anse för nog, nöja sig med; wara nöjd:</text:span></text:span> Cs. I. 15; Epaminondas Lacedæmonios satis h-re coēgit, si sua tutari possent, N.; - necesse habere = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">twingas, wara twungen;</text:span></text:span> non h-o n. scribere, C.; h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">gerundivum</text:span>: h-o faciendum = mihi est faciendum, T. (Dial.); Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>8. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bestämning af</text:span> casus obl. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med præpositionala l. adverbiala bestämningar:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">gen. pretii</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Akta, skatta:</text:span></text:span> magni, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">dativus finalis</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>aa. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> ludibrio alqd, Ter.; h-re remp. quæstui turpe est, C.<text:line-break/>bb. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Räkna till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">för; låta werka till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> non religioni h-dum est interdum nocentem defendere, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt i ett tillstånd; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">behandla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (person); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bära</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ett öde), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">föra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett lif så l. så:</text:span> se habere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> haberi = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">förhålla, bete sig:</text:span></text:span> in loco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> loco filii h. alqm; liberalissime h. alqm, C.; ea res eos in magno diuturnoque bello h-uit; h. vitam in obscuro; exercitum sine imperio luxuriose h.; benigne h. alqm; egestas facile h-etur (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom fattig kan man lefwa)</text:span> sine damno, Sa.; servorum loco; in numero hostium h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= nedhugga);</text:span> eodem loco, Cs. ea Tiberius civiliter h-uit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(upptog liberalt),</text:span> T.; - res se meā sententiā sic h-et; res se male, præclare, bene, melius h-et; bene h-emus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wi hafwa det wäl, det är wäl för oß),</text:span> C.; ita plerumque h-entur mortalia (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så går det till i werlden),</text:span> Sa.; palam h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wisa),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="T3">intrans.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förhålla sig, wara:</text:span></text:span> bene h-et, Hor.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="T3">sic h.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa det så</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för sig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">så bedöma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">betrakta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en sak; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">öfwertyga sig, döma om</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> omnes homines sic h-ent, a diis se omnia h-re; illud velim sic h-as; de me sic habetote, C.<text:line-break/>f. habere <text:span text:style-name="T3">aliquid pro alquo</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hålla, anse, räkna, taga för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> incerta pro certis, C.; alqm pro indigno, pro hoste, L.; pro re comperta, pro explorato, Cs.<text:line-break/>g. habere in rebus, in numero = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Räkna bland:</text:span></text:span> in bonis, in malis, in bonorum numero h., C.; in rebus turpissimis, Cs.; uno ordine omnes Achivos h., Vg.; in amicorum numero, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">(wäl hållen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">skött): Wälmående, fet, hullig:</text:span></text:span> virgo h-ior, Ter.; eques h-simus; equus, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. lätt att hafwa, ”handterlig”):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Beqwäm, passande, tjenlig, anwändbar; skicklig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (habil):</text:span> calcei ad pedem; figuram corporis h-em et aptam ingenio natura homini dedit, C.; gladius ad pugnam, L.; venatrix h-em arcum humeris suspenderat, Vg.; locus retibus pandendis h., Pn.; terra frumentis, Col.; sunt quidam in iisdem rebus ita h-es (oratores), ita naturæ muneribus ornati, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. låter sig anwända, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Willig, böjlig:</text:span></text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Beqwämlighet, ändamålsenlighet:</text:span></text:span> omitto reliqui corporis opportunitates et h-es, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Beqwämt:</text:span></text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhăbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Otjenlig, obeqwäm, obruklig, oskicklig:</text:span></text:span> fetibus progenerandis, Col.; telum ad remittendum; magnitudo navis, L.; omnibus rebus; ad parendum, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: debitio gratiæ, non h., Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭto</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Pläga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att hafwa, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bruka:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bo; bebo:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentliga uttryck:</text:span> apud alqm; cum patre filia; in ædiculis; in gurgustio; in via <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid wägen);</text:span> sub terra; laxe et magnifice; gratis in alieno; tot numis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för så hög hyra),</text:span> C.; bene, N.; ad occasum; tanti, Pn.; sub tegulis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på winden),</text:span> Su.; centum pagis, T. - casas, Vg.; terras, Ov.; agellus h-tus quinque focis, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildliga uttryck: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bo</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ständigt wistas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ett ställe, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ideligen sysselsätta sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> in foro; in rostris; in una ratione tractanda; in libris, C., muta quies h-at, Ov.; tecum habita ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stick handen i din egen barm,</text:span> Ps. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭtābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Beboelig:</text:span></text:span> C., Hor., Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭtācŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bo, boning:</text:span></text:span> leonis, Gell.; agreste, Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Boning, bostad:</text:span></text:span> hæc mihi est h., Pt.; sumptus h-is, C.; mercedes h-um annuæ, Cs.; fit ei h. juxta januam, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hyra:</text:span></text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭtātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inwånare; hyresgäst:</text:span></text:span> mundus: in cælesti domo, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭtātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inhăbĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bo, bebo:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Ap., Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inhăbĭtābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omöjlig att bebo:</text:span> regio, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utseende,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kroppslig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">beskaffenhet:</text:span></text:span> corporis, Ter.; bona h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hull),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭtŭrio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Önska att ega:</text:span></text:span> Pt. (d. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăbĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Beskaffenhet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">yttre:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Beskaffenhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (constitution), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">utseende</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ofta mindre om kroppens perpetuella byggnad l. skapnad, än med afs. på motsatsen af smärthet l. fyllighet); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hållning, skick:</text:span></text:span> h-us corporis opimi (<text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span>); summa gracilitas et infirmitas, qui h. - non procul abesse putatur a vitæ periculo; integerrima ætas, optimus h.; oris h. ad vitæ firmitatem nihil pertinet; virginalis h., C.; virginis os h-umque gerens, Vg.; obsita squalore vestis, fœdior corporis h. macie et pallore perempti, L.; connubiis mixtis in h-um Sarmatarum fœdantur, T.; h. corporis quiescenti, quam defuncto similior, Pn. ep.; diversus ascendentium h. et descendentium, Sen.; motus, h., incessus, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utstyrsel; drägt, klädedrägt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. en persons yttre </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppträdande:</text:span></text:span> (crinem barbamque summittunt -) h. votivus oris, T.; sollennis, L.; patrius, Su.; lugubris, Pn.; Romulus quum cetero h-u se augustiorem tum maxime lictoribus sumptis fecit, L.; Tiberium cultum h-mque Germanici leniter perstrinxit (quod sine milite, pedibus intectis et pari cum Græcis amictu per Aegyptum incesserat), T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utseende</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af döda ting, orter o. s. w.:</text:span> vestis; locorum, Vg.; domicilii, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inre:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Beskaffenhet, läge, art, skick:</text:span></text:span> format enim natura prius nos intus ad omnem fortunarum h-um, Hor.; naturæ, fortunæ h., Ct.; suo h-u vitam degere, Phdr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">själens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Beskaffenhet, tillstånd, sinnesart; stämning, sinnesstämning, beteende, hållning:</text:span></text:span> justitia is h. animi est, qui - -; divinus naturæ h., C.; non admodum simplex inter Achæos animorum h. fuit, L.; et hic quidem Romæ animorum h. fuit, T.; eos ex præsenti potius, quam ex præterito æstimat h-u, L.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">föredragets allmänna </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ton, stil, character</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i motsats till de serskilda egenskaperna af ordställning, periodbyggnad o. s. w.):</text:span> si h-um etiam orationis et quasi colorem requiritis, est et plena quædam - - et tenuis - et mediocris, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i philosophisk stil = fulländad och stadgad utbildning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Character</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gr.</text:span> ἕξις): h. in perfecta et constanti animi aut corporis absolutione consistet, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhĭbeo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafwa, hålla, (föra,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sätta wända, lägga) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">till:</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">syn.</text:span> admoveo, addo): huc a-e aures, Pt.; huc a. vultus, Ov.; manum ad vulnera, Vg.; animos a.; alicui calcaria, frenos; melius est ægrotis non a-re vinum; ad deos odores, honores, preces <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(komma till gudarne med);</text:span> quintum genus a. vacans nomine; his a-itis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(då dessa ting kommit till)</text:span> ad primum motum animi et amorem - -, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Medhafwa, kalla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (åkalla, citera), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bjuda, taga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt:</text:span> matresfamilias ad convivium; sibi in consilium XV principes a-uit; ad deliberationem a., in collegium alqm; testem alqm; auctor est a-dus Themistocles; advocatum a.; ad eligendum doctos homines a.; medicum, C.; a-iti ad ministerium dapemque Potitii et Pinarii, L.; te deum alteris mensis a-emus; deus aut heros a-etur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framföres på scenen),</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Anwända</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">på -, egna åt, bruka i, på, wisa i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt (företag); absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">anwända, iakttaga, wisa:</text:span></text:span> ad res considerandas tempus et diligentiam; ad alqd prudentiam; alqm ad res majores; auctoritatem ad monendum; iis rebus (<text:span text:style-name="T3">dat.</text:span>), quæ tractantur in vita, modum et ordinem a.; solatium alicui; vim alicui; fidem, dolum in aliqua re; in omni re præparationem diligentem; memoria custos rebus inventis a-atur; severitas a-atur, contumelia repellatur; correctione a-ta; magnitudinem animi; tranquillitatem; securitatem; modum; liberam contumaciam; sævitiam; pietatem; sollertiam; officium erga alqm; reverentiam adversus deos, C.; disciplinam alicui a.; belli necessitatibus non eam patientiam a-bimus, quam lusus elicere solet?, L.; quum peterent (ab eo) opem, nullam a-uit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wisade)</text:span> memoriam contumeliæ, N.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Behandla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> severe, liberaliter alqm, C.; se a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bete sig:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Antĕhăbeo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Föredraga:</text:span></text:span> incredibilia veris, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhĭbeo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammanhålla; inne-, omsluta, fasthålla, fästa:</text:span></text:span> terra semen; universa natura omnes naturas c-et, C.; grandinem nubes, Lucr.; Scyllam spelunca, Vg.; callosa ova vitellum marem; nec Stygiā c-bor undā, Hor.; deos parietibus c., T.; alqm intra castra, in vinculis, Ct.; te, Archyta, pulveris exigui munera; nodo crinem, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stäfja, hämma, tillbakahålla:</text:span></text:span> motus animi turbatos; conatus; impetus furentis; libidines suas ab aliqua re; oculos; manus; animum ab auro; vocem a ploratu; assensionem a rebus incertis, C.; hostem a prædandi licentia, L.; altitudinem ædificiorum, T.; filium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla i styr),</text:span> Pt.; necessitas non cum diis pugnare c-et, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhĭbĭtus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: genus dicendi, oratio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tuktad, sammanträngd; jfr.</text:span> astrictus), Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭncŏhĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Okuflig:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĭrĭbeo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 2.: (dis-hibeo; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> dirimo):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fördela, sortera</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (röster wid walförsamling):</text:span> tabellas, C.; suffragia, Varr. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förfoga öfwer, hafwa i sin hand:</text:span></text:span> pop. Rom. totius domitor orbis, qui gentes et regna di-et, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĭrĭbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sortering</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af röster):</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĭrĭbĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. tabellarum, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som skär för mat wid bordet:</text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĭrĭbĭtōrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ställe, der röstsorteringen försiggår:</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhĭbeo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framhafwa, -lemna; utlemna, förete, wisa:</text:span></text:span> e-e librarium illud legum; pupillum e-o, C.; deæ se nudas Paridi, Ov.; quadringentos senatores ad necem, Su.; spectaculum, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wisa, öfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en handling mot ngn; absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">öfwa, utöfwa:</text:span></text:span> fidem et benevolentiam domino, Col.; imperium, Pt.; liberalitatem, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wisa, låta se</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = bringa till ngns kännedom:</text:span> professus sum, me philosophiam populo nostro e-turum, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förorsaka, wålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt:</text:span> negotium, molestiam alicui, C.; laborem alicui, Col.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Underhålla:</text:span></text:span> vitam aliqua re, Js., Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhĭbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">företeende:</text:span> Gell. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">underhåll:</text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhĭbeo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hålla inne, hålla igen, hämma, förhindra:</text:span></text:span> frenos, L.; alqm i., quominus, quin -, Ct.; fletum, Ov.; alvum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afföringen);</text:span> dolores; venerem; aviditatem, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. sjömansterm:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hålla upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med roendet:</text:span> C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som sjelf på annat ställe erkänner denna anwändning ej enlig med bruket).</text:span><text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hålla inåt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> land, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ro</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bakut:</text:span> nautæ, quum i-ent, non sustinent, sed alio modo remigant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> inhibitio), C.; navem retro, L.; remis Js. - vela contrahit, remos i-et, Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Anwända, werkställa, utöfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngn:</text:span> supplicia alicui, C.; potestatem; imperium in alqm, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhĭbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: i. remigum motum habet et vehementiorem quidem remigationis navem convertentis ad puppim, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrhĭbeo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framhafwa, -ställa, -skaffa, förete, wisa:</text:span></text:span> patronum (causæ), C.; testimonium rei, Varr.; honorem alicui, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förtälja, berätta, föregifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om rykten); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">nämna, gifwa namn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af (i ryktet):</text:span> verba; non ego te novi, Menæchme, Moscho prognatum patre, qui Syracusis p-eris natus esse in Sicilia?, Pt.; is p-etur fuisse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> esse, Ter., C.; prohibiti estis, ut p-etis, pedem ponere in Africa, C.; <text:soft-page-break/>ut p-ent <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som man förtäljer),</text:span> Vg.; (sidus) Ophiuchum Graji nomine p-ent; vatem aliquem p-re optimnm, C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(poēt.).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Posthăbeo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tillbaka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">åsidosätta, låta stå tillbaka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngn l. ngt:</text:span> res omnes, Ter.; rebus omnibus p-itis, C.; mea seria illorum ludo, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præhĭbeo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(arch.), wanl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præbeo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framhålla, -räcka, -ställa; öfwerlemna, prisgifwa; wisa:</text:span></text:span> os ad male audiendum, C.; mammas alicui; aures conviciis; os ad contumeliam, L.; corpora plagis, Ov.; Pœnorum crudelitati Reguli corpus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(prisgifwa);</text:span> se victimam reipublicæ, C.; se ictibus, Ov. - se oculis universorum, Su.; terga, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gifwa, skänka, bestå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngn till hans underhåll l. undfägnad):</text:span> servis (<text:span text:style-name="T3">dat.</text:span>) justa p-da; sponsalia genero p.; aër spiritum animantibus, C.; sumptum; domum (hospitibus), Hor.; ea urbs Themistocli panem p-ret <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skulle bestå honom, förse honom med),</text:span> N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om abstracta obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gifwa, egna, bereda, erbjuda:</text:span></text:span> perfugium et solatium alicui, C.; speciem rei; causam; operam reipublicæ; accessum alicui; ratio initur, cui fortuna ipsa p-uit materiam, L.; auxilium, usum alicui, Pn.; iter, Col.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förorsaka, wäcka, uppwäcka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absol. l. hos ngn:</text:span> tumultum; terrorem; alicui spem, metum, L.; suspicionem p-uit, quasi -, T.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bewisa, wisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wisa, bewisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig ss. -:</text:span> fidem alicui, N.; honorem alicui, Pn.; se virum, se misericordem, in testimonio religiosum, placabilem alicui, superbum in fortuna, credulum, æquum alicui, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præbenda</text:span>, ōrum <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwad s. måste bestås), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Underhåll</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt en till provins afgående tjensteman:</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præbia</text:span>, ōrum <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Amulet:</text:span></text:span> p. dicuntur a præbendo, ut sit tutus, quod sint remedia in collo pueris, Varr. l. l. VII, 107.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bestående, traktering:</text:span></text:span> Varr. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">leverans:</text:span></text:span> Js.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præbĭtor</text:span>, ōris <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skaffare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (leverantör):</text:span> minister et p., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prŏhĭbeo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla borta, undan):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fördrifwa, afwända, afwärja; afhålla, hindra:</text:span></text:span> dii p-ant, Ter.; ira p-atur in puniendo, C.; dolores dentium, Pn.; conatus alicujus, C.; vim ab aliquo, Cs.; dii, p-ete nefas !; p-be infandos a classibus ignes, Vg.; p. aliquem domo, cibo, exitu, usu urbis, opere, a congressione alicujus, C.; hospitio p-emur arenæ, Vg.; p. alqm mori, uti urbe, pedem ponere, C.; agros coli p., L.; p., ne <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> quominus fiat; dii p-ant, ut hoc præsidium sectorum existimetur (pro Rosc. Am. §. 151), C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wärja, hålla fri för -, wärna:</text:span></text:span> rempublicam a periculo; injuriā p. tenuiores, C.; Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prŏhĭbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förhindrande:</text:span></text:span> sceleris, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prŏhĭbĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prŏhĭbĭtōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hindrande, förbjudande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕdhĭbeo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Återlemna,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynn. köpt wara, ss. ej motswarande aftalet:</text:span> vasa (commodata), Pt.; mancipium (vitiorum <text:soft-page-break/>causa) jure civili, C.; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">taga igen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sådan såld wara,</text:span> Pt. Merc. 449.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕdhĭbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">återlemnande af köpt wara, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Köps återgång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">:</text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hac, Hactenus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ădria <text:line-break/>(Adria), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Adriatiska hafwet.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hădriăcus, <text:line-break/>Hădriātĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>adria <text:line-break/>(Adria), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Picenum.</text:span> <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Venetia.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hadriānus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> – </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>adrūmētum <text:line-break/>(Adrūmētum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Africa.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hadrūmētīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Haedus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(hoedus) i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kid, killing</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ung get):</text:span> Varr.; villa abundat porco, h-o, agno; seu poscat agnā sive malit h-o (fieri), Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Haedŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Haedŭlea</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Haedillus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: Pt., <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Haedīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är af killing:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>æduus <text:line-break/>(Aeduus), <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag i mellersta Frankrike:</text:span> Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Haemătĭnus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Blodröd:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hæmătītes</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Blodsten:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hæmorrhăgĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Näsblod:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hæmorrhŏis</text:span>, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blodflöde, hæmorrhoider:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags orm:</text:span> Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>æmŏnĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Thessalien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hæmŏnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">thessalisk:</text:span> arcus H-i (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Centaurens),</text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/>Hæmŏnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span> – </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>æmus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hæmos i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg mellan Thracien och Moesien;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">acc.</text:span> Hæmon, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Haereo,</text:span> hæsi, hæsum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hänga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> fast, wid (mots.</text:span> pendeo = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hänga, swäfwa fri), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">låda wid, sitta fast, wara fästad, bli sittande</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">in re</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T3">rei</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">dat.</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="T3">re</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> ad radices linguæ h-et stomachus; videamus, utrum terra radicibus suis h-at an media pendeat; in equo h.; scalarum gradus male h-entes; aqua h-et (in tubo), C.; tela in scuto, L.; lateri letalis arundo, Vg.; equo; navis litore, Hor.; viscere; telæ, Ov., (Met. IV. 35).<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sitta fast, wara fästad; wara qwar, wara orubblig:</text:span></text:span> id in <text:soft-page-break/>mentibus, in memoria, in medullis ac visceribus alicujus h-et; dolor animo h-et; turpitudo reipublicæ; molestiæ h-entes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> sedatæ), C.; in animo, Sa. - is terminus h-et, Vg., Lucr.; chorus nil canat, quod non proposito conducat et h-at apte, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wara fast; ej gå för sig; ej komma ur stället; wara i förlägenhet, willrådighet, ej kunna röra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">reda sig, stå häpen:</text:span></text:span> h-et hæc res, si quidem sum apsens, quam præsens, longior; negotium, Pt.; pugna, Vfl.; h-bat nebulo: quo se verteret, non habebat; h-rem, nisi tu expedisses; in hoc etiam Democritus hæsit; in scribendo; in nominibus; in media stultitia, C.; dic alqm, sodes, dic, Quintiliane, colorem: h-emus, Juv. <text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ständigt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppehålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig hos ngn, på ett ställe, med ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wara oskiljaktig från, hålla sig wid, till:</text:span></text:span> alicui, Su.; lateri alicujus, Js.; diu circa muros unius urbis; in obsidione, Ct.; in urbe, Pn.; in jure ac prætorum tribunalibus; in libris; h-et in causa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla sig till saken);</text:span> in una eademque sententia, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om brott, oförrätter, beskyllningar o. d.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Få insteg hos</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gerningsmannen); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">träffa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (föremålet):</text:span> peccatum alicui; injuria in bonis civibus; crimen alicui; facete dictum ante h-re debet quam cogitari potuisse videatur, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hänga följa med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wara i hack och häl efter; följa med på släpet:</text:span></text:span> h. in tergis hostium, T., Ct.; in terga; ne in turba quidem h-re potuit unus plebejus (tribunus mil.), L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hæresco</text:span>, hæsi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bli sittande, bli qwar, fast; fastna; häpna, komma i förlägenhet, staka sig:</text:span></text:span> aspera (humoris pars) in terra, Lucr., Jugurthæ h-rat in animo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(den öfwertygelsen hade stadgat sig hos honom),</text:span> Romæ omnia venalia esse, Sa.; vox faucibus hæsit; aspectu conterritus hæsit, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hæsĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hänga, wara fast, bli sittande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> in luto, Ter.; in vadis, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stamma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på målet); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wara osäker, wara i förlägenhet, willrådig; tweka; komma af sig:</text:span></text:span> linguā h-ans; verba h-antia, C.; h-ans in majorum institutis; dubitant, h-ant; h-ans nostra vehitur oratio; quum h-ret, quum teneretur, quæsivi ab eo, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hæsĭtābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Brydd:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hæsĭtantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: linguæ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stammande:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hæsĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Osäkerhet, förlägenhet:</text:span></text:span> quanta h. tractusque verborum!; noli ignoscere h-i meæ, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hæsĭtātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">s. twekar, är willrådig:</text:span></text:span> in edendo libro, Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhæreo</text:span>, hæsi, hæsum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hänga fast, blifwa hängande wid:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> tela in visceribus, C.; Galli saxis, L.; naves ancoris, T.; bitumen ad contactum, Pn. - a-et dormitorium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sluter sig derintill, ligger intill),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wara fästad wid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn l. ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ständigt uppehålla sig hos</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> illi canis cognomen, Hor.; lateri a-et gravis dominus, L.; comes perpetuus philosopho a-bat, Pn.: castris, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hänga med, följa med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. ett bihang, på tåget, släpet):</text:span> quum ille quæstor factus est, tum tu vix extremus a-isti, C.; parti alicujus fortunæ, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhæresco</text:span>, hæsi, hæsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bli hängande, fastna wid, få tag i:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ad saxum; fæx in lateribus; in tantam materiam fax, C.; ad turrim tragula, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bli qwar, få fast fot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någorstädes:</text:span> in his locis, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Haka sig fast, stöta på, träffa:</text:span></text:span> argumentum simul atque emissum est, a-it; fastidiis (<text:span text:style-name="T3">dat.</text:span>); ad alicujus studium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(träffa = öfwerensstämma med),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hålla sig wid, hålla fast wid:</text:span></text:span> justitiæ et honestati, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om föredraget) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hacka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> stundtals </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">afbrytas:</text:span></text:span> oratio ita libere fluebat, ut nunquam a-ret, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhæse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: loqui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hackande),</text:span> Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhæsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fastnande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid -:</text:span> atomorum inter se, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhæsus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: id.: Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhæreo</text:span>, hæsi, hæsum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hänga samman, sammanhänga; wara sammansatt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af: </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> mundus apte; membrum cum corpore, C.; turris muris hostium, Ct.; connexa et c-entia ædificia, T.; ceteræ partes, quibus homines c-ent, C. - cohæsus, Gell. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">relativt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammanhänga, stå i sammanhang</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt l. inbördes:</text:span> verba inter se c-ent; verba cum causa; res naturā c-entes disputatione separare; Sullæ legibus resp. ita c-et, ut iis solutis stare non possit, C.; gentes moribus et commercio linguæ c-entes, Ct.; statui non ultra attingere externa, nisi qua Romanis rebus c-erent, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ega sammanhang</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> inom sig; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hänga samman; sammanhållas, bestå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> consto): non modo crimen non hærebat, sed vix c-bat oratio; C.; non c-ent <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det hänger ej ihop = är orimligt),</text:span> Ter.; sine virtute beata vita c. non potest; non posse c. propter magnitudinem ægritudinis, C. <text:line-break/>c. c-ens oratio = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wäl sammanfogad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med afs. på ordställningen),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhærenter</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Oafbrutet:</text:span></text:span> Fl.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerensstämmande, conseqvent:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhærentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sammanhang:</text:span></text:span> mundi, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhæresco</text:span>, ĕre, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Komma att sammanhänga:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhæreo</text:span>, hæsi, hæsum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hänga, sitta fast, fästad i, wid:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> sidera sedibus suis; beluarum genus ad saxa; quorum linguæ sic i-ent, ut loqui non possint, scalpello resectæ liberantur, C.; patris cervicibus, Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wara fästad; sitta, ligga i:</text:span></text:span> in mentibus i-et augurium sæculorum futurorum; in visceribus i-et (cupiditas pecuniæ); ea argumenta quæ i-ent in rei natura, C.; studiis, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhæresco</text:span>, hæsi, hæsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fastna i, infästas, fästa sig i:</text:span></text:span> bestiolæ in visco; poētæ leguntur, ediscuntur, i-unt in mentibus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ŏbhæreo</text:span>, hæsi, hæsum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hänga, sitta fast</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i wägen för ngt):</text:span> navis vado, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ŏbhæresco</text:span>, hæsi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Haka sig fast, fastna:</text:span></text:span> lacinia ei resurgenti, Su.; equus in medio flumine, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭbhæreo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sitta fast:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oeg.:</text:span> in suspicione, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hæres <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Heres.<text:line-break/>Hæresco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hæreo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Haerĕsis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wal) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sect</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (philosophisk):</text:span> Cato est in ea h-i, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skämtsamt:</text:span> Vestoriana <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en bankirs),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hæsit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hæreo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ălæsa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Sicilien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hălæsīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ălæsus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mythiskt personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Halcedo, Halcyon <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Alcedo.<text:line-break/>Halec <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Alec.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ales, ētis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Lucanien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Halex <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Alec.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ălĭacmon, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Macedonien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hălĭæĕtus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hafsörn:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ălĭartus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Boeotien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hălĭartii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inw. i H.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Halica <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Alica.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ălĭcarnassus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Carien, Herodoti födelseort.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hălĭcarnassēus, <text:line-break/>Hălĭcarnassĭus, <text:line-break/>Hălĭcarnassensis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ălĭcy̆æ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Sicilien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hălĭcyensis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hălĭeutĭcus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till fiske hörande:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hălĭeutĭca</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poem af Ovidius om fiske.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Halitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Halo.<text:line-break/>Hallucinatio, -cinor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Alucinor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hālo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fläkta, dunsta, dofta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T3">intr.</text:span>: auræ de vallibus, Ov.; ture calent aræ sertisque recentibus h-ant; horti floribus h-antes, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T3">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utdunsta, sprida doft</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af:</text:span> croci flos nectar naribus; sulfur h-re, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hālĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fläkt, pust, andedrägt; ånga, dunst:</text:span></text:span> leo extremum efflavit h-um, C. poēt.; h-us graveolentia, Pn.; Averni, Vg.; oris, Juv.; terræ, Qu.; solis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhālo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Flåsa, fläkta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ănhēlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Flåsa, flämta, fnysa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T3">intr.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om lefwande subj.:</text:span> spiritus a-ans ducebatur, C.; acer, a-anti similis; equus; Vg.; boves, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om döda subj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ånga:</text:span></text:span> amnis vapore, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T3">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framflåsa, -flämta, utandas:</text:span></text:span> nolo verba inflata et gravius a-ta exire, C.; Capricornus a-at frigus, C. poēt.; Aetna ignes, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> Catilina scelus a-ans; crudelitatem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(liks. flämta fram det, hwaraf hans inre war öfwerfullt och som wille ha luft),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ănhēlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Flämtande, andtäppa:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ănhēlātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som lider af andtäppa:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ănhēlĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tung </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Andedrägt; andtrutenhet, flämtande, flåsande:</text:span></text:span> a-um reddere ac per vices recipere, Pn.; nimis festinantibus movetur, C.; quatit æger a. artus; creber a., Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Dunst, doft, stank:</text:span></text:span> vini; terræ, C.; tristis, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ănhēlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Flämtande, flåsande, kiknande, andtruten:</text:span></text:span> senex; equus; pectus; tussis, Vg.; sitis, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subtĕrănhēlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Flåsa under</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en börda:</text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhālo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Dunsta ut; sprida dunst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ånga, utandas:</text:span></text:span> vinum; crapulam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sofwa af sig),</text:span> C.; Albunea (fons) e-at sævam mephitin, Vg.; terra nebulas, Pn.; animam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppgifwa),</text:span> Ov., Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhālātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utdunstning:</text:span></text:span> terræ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhālo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Andas på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> teterrimam popinam (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stank från),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕdhālo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Åter utdunsta:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ălŏnēsus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö wid macedoniska kusten:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hălŏphanta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">saltangifware, skämtsam efterbildning af</text:span> sycophanta: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hālōs,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ring kring solen:</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hălōsis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eröfring:</text:span></text:span> Trojæ, Petr., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Halter,</text:span> ēris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. hoppare): blymassor, s. athleter balancerade:</text:span> h-es facili rotat lacerto, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ăluntium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Sicilien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hăluntīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>alus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Assyrien.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ălys, y̆os, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i mindre Asien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hăma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hămŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wattenspann,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Brandämbar:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Col.; Juv.; Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hămādry̆as,</text:span> ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Träd-, skogsnymf:</text:span></text:span> Ov.; <text:span text:style-name="T3">dat. pl.</text:span> hamadryasin, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hamatilis, -matus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hamus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hămaxa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wagn:</text:span></text:span> Cap., Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hămaxăgōga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Forman:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ămilcar, ăris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">carthaginiensiskt namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hamiota <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hamus.<text:line-break/>Hammon <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ammon.<text:line-break/>Hamula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hama.<text:line-break/>Hamulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hamus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hāmus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hake, krok, hulling:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> taleæ ferreæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fotanglar)</text:span> h-is infixis, Cs.; ferrei h-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(häkta),</text:span> Pn.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om örnens klo, om törntaggar,</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ring</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i pansar:</text:span> lorica h-is conserta, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Metkrok</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i eg. och bildliga uttryck):</text:span> capere pisces h-o, C.; piscarius; non ego illi extemplo h-um ostendam: sensim mittam lineam; ubi demisi rete atque h-um, quidquid hæsit, extraho, Pt.; piscis præroso h-o fugit insidias; occultum decurrere ad h-um, Hor.; aduncus; fallax, Ov.; piscari aureo h-o, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hāmātĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: piscatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. sker med krok),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hāmātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Försedd med krok, hulling, tagg:</text:span></text:span> arundo; sagitta; unguis, Ov.; rubus, Tib. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> munera <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(försåtliga),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hāmiōta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fiskare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med metspö), skämtsamt bildadt ord af</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hāmŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: piscarius, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>annĭbal, ălis, (-ālis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.)</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>anno, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">carthaginiensiska namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hăpălus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Löskokt:</text:span></text:span> ovum, Apic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hăphē,</text:span> es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sand,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarmed athleter beströdde sin oljade kropp:</text:span> flavescit h-e, Mt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">stoft</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Happalopsis,</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">krydda:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hăra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stiga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (swin-, gås-):</text:span> C., Varr., Pt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom skällsord till person:</text:span> h. suis, germana illuvies, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Harena <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Arena.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hăriŏlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Spåman, signare:</text:span></text:span> imprudentes h-i aut inertes aut insani aut quibus egestas imperat, poēt. ap. C.; interdixit h., Ter. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">titel på comoedi af Nævius,</text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăriŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Spåkäring:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăriŏlor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Spå:</text:span></text:span> Venus eam fecit h., Pt.; quæstus causa, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">prata</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som en förryckt:</text:span> non mihi credis? - h-are (ɔ: fabulæ!, somnia!), Ter.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăriŏlātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Spående:</text:span></text:span> Acc. ap. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Harmămaxa</text:span> (arm.), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">persisk täckt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Reswagn:</text:span></text:span> Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>armŏdĭus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">attiskt namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Harmŏnĭa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Samljud, -klang, harmoni:</text:span></text:span> h-am novimus ex intervallis sonorum, C.; caeli, Mcb. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen myth. personnamn:</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Harmŏnĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: ratio, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Harpăgo,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Båts-, brunns-, stormhake:</text:span></text:span> L., Pn., C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">röfware:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Harpăgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Röfwa:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Harpax</text:span>, ăgis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rofgirig:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>arpăgus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mediskt namn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>arpălus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>arpăly̆cē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekiska namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Harpē,</text:span> es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lie) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Krokigt swärd:</text:span></text:span> Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en falk-art:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>arpŏcrătes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ægyptisk gudomlighet, s. föreställes med fingret på munnen; derför ansedd ss. symbol af tystnaden:</text:span> Catl. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekiskt namn (äfwen</text:span> Harpocras). </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>arpyia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mythologiskt wäsende, fågel med qwinnoansigte:</text:span> Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rofgirig, girig qwinna:</text:span></text:span> Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Harundo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Arundo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hăruspex,</text:span> spĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Fs. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> haruga (aruga, arviga) = hostia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> specio): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. etrurisk) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tecknatydare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. spår af djurs inelfwor, af blixt o. s. w.; i allm. s. förklarar järtecken och råder bot derför):</text:span> prodigia, portenta ad Etruscos h-es deferunto: quibus divis jusserint, procuranto: iidemque fulgura et obstita pianto; quum in Capitolio res complures essent percussæ - - h-es ex tota Etruria convenerunt -; mirabatur Cato, quod non rideret h., h-em quum videret, C.; prodigia multa nunciari - - (sed) hostibus Etruscis, per quos ea procurarent, h-es non erant, L.; Corinthius, N.; o proceres, censore opus est an h-e nobis?, Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăruspĭca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăruspĭcīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.:</text:span> libri, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăruspĭcīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tecknatydarekonsten,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">-läran:</text:span></text:span> facere; colere, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hăruspĭcium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tecknatydning:</text:span></text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>asdrŭbal, ălis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">carthaginiensiskt namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hasta,</text:span> ae. <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stång,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> lång </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">staf:</text:span></text:span> gramineæ h-æ, in quibus nihil erat manu factum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ett slags rör),</text:span> C.; pampinea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(thyrsus-staf),</text:span> Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stång,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. uppsattes ss. tecken till att auction hölls; deraf meton: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">auction:</text:span></text:span> in foro h-ā positā civium bona vendere, C.; sub h-a vendere, L.; a sceleratiore h-a non recessit; Cæsaris h. refrixit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(intresset för - har kallnat),</text:span> C.; ad publicam h-am nunquam accessit Atticus, N. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lans, pik,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (längre och smalare än</text:span> pilum): eminus h-is, cominus gladiis uti; vibrant ante pugnam h-as, quibus in pugnando nihil utuntur; jactare h-am, C.; h. pura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utan jern, ss. heders- l. helgeskänk);</text:span> brevi uti, N.; transfigere, perfodere alqm h-ā, Ct.; h-as (frameas) gerunt Germani angusto et brevi ferro, T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildliga uttryck:</text:span> h-as abjicere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwa tappt),</text:span> C.; jureconsultus oratoribus h-as ministrat; orator quum a jureconsulto h-as amentatas acceperit, ipse eas oratoris viribus torquebit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hastātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lansbewäpnad,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. om den första linien i en romersk acies:</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hastīle</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Qwist, gren:</text:span></text:span> densis h-bus horrida myrtus, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lansskaft, lans:</text:span></text:span> N., Juv., Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hastŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten staf l. lans:</text:span> Fr., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>aterius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Hau,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Interj.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Aj, ah:</text:span></text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Hau</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr Ritschl,</text:span> Prolegomena in Trinumm. p. 99), <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Haud, <text:line-break/>Haut,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Icke just, wißt icke,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> negation i förening med bekräftelse l. i allm. uttryck för subjectets mening; derför</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oftast förenad med grad- och egenskapsord (adjectiva och adv.):</text:span> haud magna res; h. idem, C.; h. pœnitendus, L.; h. facile; h. dubie; h. quaquam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ingalunda);</text:span> h. mediocriter; h. sane, C.; h. diu, Ter.; h. amplius; h. ita multo post<text:span text:style-name="T3">;</text:span> h. dum; h. cunctanter, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mera sällan med verba: isynn. i uttr.:</text:span> haud scio an <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= jag skulle tro),</text:span> C., L.; h. assentior, C.; h. ambigam, L.; quod Tiberio haud probatum, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Haudquaquam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Quisquam, Qui. <text:line-break/>Haveo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Aveo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Haurio,</text:span> hausi, haustum (hausurum, Vg. Aen. IV, 382 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ribb.;</text:span> haurii, -ītum, Varr., Ap.), 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ösa; tömma, dricka; utgjuta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> aquam de puteo; de dolio vinum, C.; poculum L.; impiger h-sit spumantem pateram, Vg.; potionem, Pn., Su.; sanguinem; L., Luc.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttr.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ösa, uttaga, hemta; inhemta:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> libo): ceterarum artium studia e reconditis fontibus h-untur; sumptus h-it ex ærario; animos ex divinitate h-tos habemus; legem a natura; cogitatione aliquid, C.; animo aliquid, Vg.; auribus, Ov.; præcepta vitæ, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om lefwande och döda subject) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sluka, förtära, bortrycka:</text:span></text:span> sua h., T.; serpens cervos solidos, Pn.; cibos, Col.; mare naves; flamma multos; incendium opes, L.; lacus servos, T.; quos, ni mea cura resistat, jam flammæ tulerint inimicus et h-serit ensis, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utgräfwa, genomborra:</text:span></text:span> fossam, L.; humum, Hor.; lumina <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ögonen),</text:span> Ov.; pectus ictu, L.; latus gladio, Luc.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utstå; njuta:</text:span></text:span> luctum et dolorem; incredibiles calamitates, C.; supplicium, Vg.; libertatem, L.; voluptates, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Haustor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tömmer, dricker:</text:span> Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Haustrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ösmachin, kran:</text:span></text:span> fluvios videmus versare rotas et h-a (austra), Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Haustus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ösning, wattenhemtning; upphemtning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">; (concr. handfull); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">drickande; dryck:</text:span></text:span> aquæ ductus, h., iter, actus, C.; arenæ, Ov.; fontium; auræ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inandning),</text:span> Ct.; Pindarici fontis, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕhaurio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ösa ur:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhaurio</text:span>, si, stum, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utösa; uttömma, -dricka, utgjuta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> sentinam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utpumpa),</text:span> C.; fontem, Cs.; tantum vini; poculum mortis, C.; poculum, L.; spiritum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utandas, uppgifwa),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uttömma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (så wäl = tömma ut, som = göra tom), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">förslösa, medtaga, utarma, utblotta:</text:span></text:span> copias; pecunias ex ærario; ærarium; domos; alqm bellis; civitatem bonis; sermo hominum e-stus est; actio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gesticulation, mimik)</text:span> superiori motu e-sta erat, C.; plebem impensis, L.; patriam sumptibus; facultates alicujus, N.; vires, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Borttaga, betaga, beröfwa:</text:span></text:span> ex alicujus laudibus alqd; alicui dolorem; sibi vitam, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utstå:</text:span></text:span> labores, L., Pn.; dura et aspera belli, Vg.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utföra:</text:span></text:span> mandata, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnexhaustus</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Outtömd; outtömlig:</text:span></text:span> pubertas juvenum; litus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ej utplundrad),</text:span> T.; aviditas legendi, C.; metalla, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hauscio = Haud scio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Haust . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Haurio.<text:line-break/>Haut <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Hau.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĕautontīmōrūmĕnos <text:line-break/>(Hautontīmōrūmĕnos), i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: ”ipse se poeniens” (C.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Sjelfplågaren, titel på en comoedi af</text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hebdŏmas,</text:span> ădis (acc. h-a, C.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hebdŏmăda</text:span>, ae, (Gell.) <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tid, period af sju dagar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wecka): (i fråga om frossa, om critiske dagar i sjukdom o. s. w.),</text:span> C. Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ēbē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hebe,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ungdomens gudinna</text:span> (lat. Juventas): Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hebenum, Hebenus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ebenus.<text:line-break/>Hebeo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hebes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hĕbes,</text:span> ĕtis, (<text:span text:style-name="T3">Acc.</text:span> hebem, Næv.) <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Slö:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mechanisk men. = ej hwaß:</text:span> tela h-iora, C.; mucro, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sinnen, färger o. s. w.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Slö, matt, långsam:</text:span></text:span> oculi, Pn.; aures; sensus; spondēus h-ior et tardior, C.; color, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fattningsförmåga, förstånd, känsla: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Slö, slapp, förslappad, dum:</text:span></text:span> h. æque ac pecus; h. ingenium; h. ad intelligendum, h. in vita communi; me molestiæ h-em reddiderunt, C.; exercitus, Sa.; h. et indocilis, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕbeo</text:span>, ēre, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wara slö, matt; gå fåfäng:</text:span></text:span> ferrum, L.; sidus, Luc.; sanguis, Vg.; ipsi h-ent (proceres Germanorum), T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕbesco</text:span>, ĕre, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förslöas, mattas:</text:span></text:span> acies mentis; in otio homo, C.; sidera, T.; virtus, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕbĕto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Göra slö, förslöa, förslappa, förswaga:</text:span></text:span> hastas aut perfregerant aut h-verant, L.; nubes mortales visus tuos h-at, Vg.; h-at allium oculos; cura vino h-atur, Js.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕbĕtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: oculorum, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕbĕtātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. förslöar, -swagar:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕbĕtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Slöhet:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĕbræus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">judisk:</text:span> terra, T. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĕbrus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Thracien:</text:span> nivali compede <text:span text:style-name="T6">v</text:span>inctus, Hor.; celer, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĕcătæus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn (historieskrifwares).</text:span> </text:p>
