   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hĕdĕra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span> <text:line-break/>(edera): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Murgrön:</text:span></text:span> Baccho gratissima, Ov.; h-ā ornare poētam; h-ā formosior albā; nigra; errans, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕdĕrāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Af murgrön:</text:span></text:span> corona, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕdĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prydd med murgrön:</text:span> Treb. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕdĕrĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bär, är bekransad med murgrön:</text:span> Mænades, Catl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕdĕrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full, öfwertäckt af murgrön:</text:span> antrum, Ppt.</text:p>
