   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Helcĭum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Silja, bogträd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på häst:</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Helciārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som drager fartyg:</text:span> clamor h-orum, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĕlĕna ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hĕlĕnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn (Menelai gemål,</text:span> causa belli Trojani).</text:p>
