   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĕlĭcon, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Musernas berg i Boeotien:</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>Hĕlĭcōnĭădes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Muserna:</text:span> Lucr. <text:line-break/>Hĕlĭcōnis, ĭdis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f. A.</text:span>: silva, St. <text:line-break/>Hĕlĭcōnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
