   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hellĕbŏrus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(ellĕbŏrus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hellĕbŏrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Prustrot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (oftast omtalad ss. ett renande och kylande medel mot kropps- och sinnessjukdomar):</text:span> danda est h-i longe pars maxima avaris, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hellĕbŏrītes</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med prustrot kryddadt win:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hellĕbŏrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Som behöfwer mycken</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> pr.</text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ej rätt klok):</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hellespont . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Helle.<text:line-break/>Helluo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med härledn. se</text:span> Heluo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ēlōtes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Hilotes, <text:line-break/>Ilotæ): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Lacedæmoniernes lifegne (eg. inwånare i staden Helos):</text:span> N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Heluatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Heluo.</text:p>
