   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ērāclēus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hērāclīus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillhör Heracles (Hercules).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ērāclēa, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hērāclīa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stadsnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hērācleensis, <text:line-break/>Hērāclēus, <text:line-break/>Hērācleōtes, ae, <text:line-break/>Hērācleōtĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ērāclīdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ättling af Heracles (Hercules).</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ērāclītus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ēræa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Arcadien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Herba,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wäxt, ört; gräs; brodd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (grönska):</text:span> corona ex h-is asperis et agrestibus; fructus apparet ut in h-is non fallacibus, C.; florens; suavis; mollis, Vg.; h-æ, quas edunt homines, Pt.; graminis <text:soft-page-break/>h. pura, L.; in h-a recumbere, abjicere se, C.; - frumenta sunt in h-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på rot),</text:span> Cs.; adhuc tua messis in h-a, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herbāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af gräs; gräsgrön:</text:span> corona; color, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herbans</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grönskande:</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herbāria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herbārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">örtkunskap, örtkännare (botanicus):</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herbesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utweckla sig till gräs, gro:</text:span></text:span> viriditas, C.; semen, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herbeus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gräsgrön:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herbĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ört-, blomster- gräsrik; grön:</text:span></text:span> campus, L.; color, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herbĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: id.: mons, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herbĭgrădus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: (gradior): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. går i gräs:</text:span> C. poēt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herbōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gräsrik:</text:span> cæspes, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herbŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ört:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exherbo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rensa från gräs, luka:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>erbessus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Sicilien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Herbessensis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>erbĭta, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Sicilien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Herbĭtensis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hercisco</text:span> <text:line-break/>(ercisco), ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skifta bo</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">arf:</text:span></text:span> familiæ h-undæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herctum</text:span> <text:line-break/>(erctum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bo, arf:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ercŭles, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Hercules, styrkans gud - i bedyranden: (wid H., i sanning):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. H-es, me H-es (sc. juvet): C.<text:line-break/>b. Hercule, mehercule, Hercle, mehercle: ego mehercule; sed mehercule; minime hercle; dii hercle, C.; pulcre mehercle, Ter. <text:line-break/>Hercŭleus, <text:line-break/>Hercŭlāneus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Herculis, herculisk:</text:span> labor, Hor. - <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ercŭlāneum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hercŭlānium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Campanien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hercŭlānensis, <text:line-break/>Hercŭlāneus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> – </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ercy̆nia <text:line-break/>(Orcynia) silva: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">allmänt namn på de bergssträckor, s. genomskära Tyskland.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Here <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Heri.<text:line-break/>Hered . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Heres.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>erennius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på en romersk</text:span> gens.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hēres</text:span> <text:line-break/>(hæres), ēdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T3">comm.,</text:span> Prisc.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Arfwinge, arftagare, -erska:</text:span></text:span> is mihi h. esto; h-em relinquere, facere, scribere, instituere alqm testamento, C.; h-em nuncupare, Su.; h. secundus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i survivance),</text:span> C.; <text:soft-page-break/>h. ex asse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till det hela),</text:span> Qu.; ex parte, T.; ex dodrante <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till</text:span> ¾), N.; indignus; avidus; quartæ partis h., Hor. - monumentum h-em ne sequatur, Hor.; paterni odii h., T.; arboris h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(telning),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Egare, egarinna; delegare, -rinna:</text:span></text:span> abstuli hanc (pallam), quojus h. (illa) nunquam erit post hunc diem; fecisti funus med absente prandio. Cur ausus facere, quoi ego æque h. eram, Pt. (Men. III. 2. v. 12. 28.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hērēdĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Arftägt, arf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i abstract och concret men.), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">arfwedel:</text:span></text:span> h. paterna; hoc mihi h-e venit; h-e possidere alqd; multa h-bus, multa dotibus tenebantur sine injuria, C.; h-e relinquere alicui alqd; ex h-e accipere alqd, N.; h-em capere; h-is loco tradere alqd alicui; ad alqm venit, pervenit, redit h.; h-em cernere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bestämma sig för att tillträda),</text:span> adire, obire <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillträda),</text:span> C.; h-es multas consequi, N. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttr.:</text:span> optima h. liberis traditur gloria; ad te h. hujus gloriæ pertinet, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hērēdĭtārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ärftlig, ärfd;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som angår arf; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">arfs-:</text:span></text:span> regnum, Pn.; agri, Pn. ep.; imperium, Ct.; actio; controversia, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hērēdium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Arfgods:</text:span></text:span> N., Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hērēdiŏlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hērēdĭpĕta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: (pcto): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Arfjägare:</text:span></text:span> Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhēres</text:span>, ēdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">comm.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Medarfwinge:</text:span></text:span> c. meus; c-em esse alicui, C.; solus multisne c.?, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhēres</text:span>, ēdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">comm.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Arflös, urarfwa:</text:span></text:span> quærebatur, possetne paternorum bonorum e. esse filius, quem neque heredem neque e-em nominatim scripsisset pater, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = förlustig:</text:span> vitæ, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhērēdo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Göra arflös:</text:span></text:span> filium, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fråntaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (arf):</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhērēdātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hĕri</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕre</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I går:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Ter., C., Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hesternus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gårdags-:</text:span></text:span> h. sermo, dies, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Herifuga, Herilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Herus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ērillus i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn (philosoph). </text:span><text:s/><text:line-break/>Hērillii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lärjungar af H.:</text:span> C. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ermæum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ort i Boeotien.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ermăgŏras, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hermes</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Herma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Hermesstod (pelare med (Hermes-)hufwud):</text:span> C., N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hermăphrŏdītus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tweköning:</text:span></text:span> Ov., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hermăthēna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">pelare med dubbelansigte af Hermes och Athena:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hermērācles</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dubbelstod af Hermes och Hercules:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hermĕros</text:span>, ōtis <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dubbelstod af Hermes och Eros:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ermēsiănax, actis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>erminius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Portugal.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ermĭŏnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">qwinno- och stadsnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hermĭŏnĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ermiŏnes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Herminŏnes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">germanisk folkstam:</text:span> Pn., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ermŏdōrus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ermŏgĕnes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ermŏtīmus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ermundŭri, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">germanisk folkstam.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ermus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Lydien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hernia,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bråck:</text:span></text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Herniōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ernĭci, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i Latium.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ēro, ūs, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hērōus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ērōdes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span> – </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ērŏdŏtus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hēros,</text:span> ōis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Heros,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">sagohjelte, urtidshjelte, halfgud:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> quem virum aut heroa? quem deum?, Hor.; divis mixti h-es; magnanimi h-es nati melioribus annis; Acestes, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> h. ille Cato, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hērōĭcus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hērōus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Heroisk:</text:span></text:span> tempora, ætas h-ca; versus h-ci; pes h-ous (= dactylus), C.; versus h-oi, Qu. - facinora h-ca, C.; sensus h-oos (alii heroas) exprimere, Ps. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hērōīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: Ppt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hērōis</text:span>, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hērōum</text:span>, ōi, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tempel åt</text:span> heros: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ersĭlia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Romuli drottning.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ertha, ae <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">germanisk gudinna, som dyrkades på en ö i Oceanen (Rügen):</text:span> T. Germ. 40.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hĕrus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(erus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Husbonde, husmoder; herre, fru:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> h-i adhibent sævitiam in famulos, C.; o here salve; h-o servire; h. major, minor (pater, filius familias); h-a major et minor (mater et filia familias), Pt.; fundi, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Herre, herrskare, -inna:</text:span></text:span> cælestes h-i (= dii), Catl.; h-a Fors, Enn. ap. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕrĭfŭga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förlupen tjenare:</text:span></text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕrīlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">husbonde tillhörig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Husbondes, husbonde-:</text:span></text:span> filius, Ter.; imperium; filia; amica; negotium h-e curare, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ēsĭŏdus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekisk skald.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hēsĭŏdēus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ēsĭŏnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hēsĭŏna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>espĕrus <text:line-break/>(Hespĕros), i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lat.</text:span> vesper): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Aftonstjernan:</text:span></text:span> C., Vg. <text:line-break/>Hespĕrĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Westlig, westerländsk:</text:span></text:span> Gallus et H-is et Gallus notus Eois, Ppt. <text:line-break/>Hespĕrĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">westerlandet, western:</text:span> Graji (Italiam) cognomine H-am dicunt, Vg. <text:line-break/>Hespĕris, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Westlig:</text:span></text:span> aquæ, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. Hespĕrĭdes, um: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Hesperiderna, myth. wäsenden i yttersta western:</text:span> māla H-um, Vg. <text:line-break/>Hespĕrūgo, ĭnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span> = Hesperus: Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hesternus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Heri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>estĭæōtis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">thessaliskt landskap.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hĕtærĭa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Samfund, gille:</text:span></text:span> Pn. ep.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĕtærĭcē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: altera equitum (Macedonum) ala h. appellabatur, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hetruria, Hetruscus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Etruria.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Heu,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Interj.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">nom.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">acc.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ack! O ! Ah!:</text:span></text:span> h. prisca fides; h. me miserum, Ter.; h. cæcæ vatum mentes!, Vg.; h. me; ferebar ad non amicos h. mihi postes et h. limina dura, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Heurĕtes</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Heurĕta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uppfinnare:</text:span> Pt. (d. l.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Heus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Interj.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hör! hör hit!:</text:span></text:span> h. tu, h. Syre, Ter.; h. evocate, C.; h., juvenes, monstrate - -!, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hexăchordos,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sexsträngad, -stämmig:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hexăclīnon</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">säte för sex:</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hexăgōnum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sexhörning:</text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hexămĕter</text:span>, tri, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">vers med sex (dactyliske) fötter: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hexameter:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hexăphŏrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stol, som bäres af sex:</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hexăpy̆lon</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Port med sex genomgångar:</text:span></text:span> L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hexăstĭchus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sexradig:</text:span> hordeum: Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hexăstȳlos</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sex colonner i fronten:</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hexēris</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fartyg med 6 roddarerader:</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hiatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ibernia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Irland:</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hibern . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för öfrigt</text:span> Hiems.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hĭbiscus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. </text:span><text:s/><text:line-break/>Hĭbiscum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m. n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wäxt:</text:span> Vg., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hibrĭda</text:span> <text:line-break/>(hybrĭda), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är af blandad race, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bastard,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (blandföding):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om djur:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om mskor:</text:span> h. Persius, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hic</text:span> (hīc, hĭc), hæc, hōc (hice, hæce, hoce), <text:span text:style-name="T3">gen.</text:span> hujus (hujusce), <text:span text:style-name="T3">dat</text:span> huic (huice), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Pron. demonstrativum</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(archaistiska former:</text:span> hisce, <text:span text:style-name="T3">nom. plur. masc.,</text:span> Pt. Mil. 374. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Fl.;</text:span> hæc, <text:span text:style-name="T3">nom. plur. fem.,</text:span> ap. Com. sæpe): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Denne; den här; den nu warande; den sednare; den ifrågawarande:</text:span></text:span> quis hic est?; non possunt mihi minis tuis hisce (= hi-ce) oculi ecfodiri; hic mihi id dixit; certumst hoc observare ostium, Pt.; hæ sunt meræ nugæ; hic dies <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(denne dagen);</text:span> hicine (i. e. hice, hic <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med enclitiskt frågeord)</text:span> est Simo?; hocine <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(är wäl detta)</text:span> credibile aut memorabile?; accede ad ignem hunc, jam calesces plus satis!, Ter.; hæc porticus, in qua ambulamus; ex his tenebris ad illam lucem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från mörkret här till ljuset der);</text:span> hæc tempora, hæc ætas (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wår tid);</text:span> hæc ætas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(generation)</text:span> oratorum; hæc lex in amicitia sanciatur; hujus (Catonis) facta, illius (Socratis) dicta laudantur; hoc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(desto)</text:span> magis, C.; hoc est illud <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det omtalade)</text:span> in rerum cognitione frugiferum, omnis te exempli documenta in illustri monumento posita intueri, L.; hæcine parva meum funus arena teget?, Ppt. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> talis, tantus).<text:line-break/>2. hic - hic = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Den ene - den andre:</text:span></text:span> hi summo in fluctu pendent, his unda dehiscens terram inter fluctus aperit, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sådan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som den ifrågawarande):</text:span> putabam, eum oratorem fore hoc populo (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sådant wårt folk är)</text:span> probabiliorem, qui nihil artificii afferret; hæc opera sunt magni et excelsi animi; hujus generis, hujusmodi res = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sådana ting,</text:span> C.; hic meret æra liber Sosiis; ne fueris hic tu, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hāc</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">abl. sing. fem.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> hic), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På denne wäg; här</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fram), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">häråt, på detta sätt:</text:span></text:span> h. non successit, Ter.; h. copias traduxit, N.; h. sit iter: manifesta rotæ vestigia cernis, Ov.; h. rabiosa canis fugit, hac lutulenta ruit sus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hactĕnus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(se præp.</text:span> tenus), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Härtill, hittills, härintill, till denne punkt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i rum, tid, framställning:</text:span> h. vivo Attico hæc a nobis edita sunt, N.; h. arvorum cultus et sidera cæli (scripsi), Vg.; hæc h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nog härom):</text:span> redeo ad urbana sed hæc h.: redeo ad augurem, C.; h. in Occidentem Germaniam novimus, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Så widt; blott så till wida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">för så widt:</text:span></text:span> hæc artem et præcepta h. requirunt, ut certis dicendi luminibus ornentur; h. requiro eorum tarditatem, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Antĕhāc</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(arch.</text:span> <text:line-break/>antĭdhāc), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (före denna tiden):</text:span> a. sperare licebat: nunc etiam id ereptum est, C. - a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(twåstafw.)</text:span> nefas depromere Cæcubum, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Posthāc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hädanefter, framdeles, sedermera:</text:span></text:span> decrevi ad te scribere alqd hoc tempore, multa p.; - ut ipse ne quid tale p., et ceteri <text:soft-page-break/>sint ad injuriam tardiores, C.; p. non simili poena commissa luetis, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prætĕrhāc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utöfwer detta; widare, mera:</text:span></text:span> p. si mihi tale faxis, faxo vidua visas patrem, Pt. Men. I. 2. 3.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hīc</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(arch.</text:span> <text:line-break/>heic, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uttaladt</text:span> = hic), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Här:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. = härstädes, på detta ställe:</text:span> fenus illic, fenus hic: nescit quidem nisi fenus fabularier, Pt.; h. ante ostium, Ter.; h. omnes tui valent; h. piscari nulli solent, C.; serus in cælum redeas - h. ames potius triumphos, h. ames dici pater atque princeps, Hor.; h. optime manebimus, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Härwid, wid denne punkt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i framställningen, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">härutinnan, i denna fråga, i denna sak:</text:span></text:span> hic tu miraris!, C.; h. mihi quisquam mansuetudinem nominat!, Sa.; h. se bene gerebat, N.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wid detta tillfälle; då:</text:span></text:span> h. omnes tacite assensi inter se significare coeperunt, C.; h. regina gravem auro pateram poposcit, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hinc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Härifrån, hädan:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. local mening:</text:span> h. euntem Scævolam conveni, C.; abi h. ad sponsum!, L.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Från,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">på denna sida:</text:span></text:span> h. pietas est, illinc scelus: h. fides, illinc fraudatio, C.; h. atque h. glomerantur Oreades, Vg.; h. vos, vos h. mutatis discedite partibus, Hor.; h. atque inde patens, Juv.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hädanefter, sedan:</text:span></text:span> T., Su.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Härifrån, häraf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i fråga om utgång, ursprung, orsak, källa, område, hwarifrån ngt hemtas); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">med anledning häraf:</text:span></text:span> h. canere incipiam, Vg.; h. illæ lacrimæ, Ter.; h. rhetorum campus de Marathone; h. sicæ, h. venena, h. falsa testamenta nascuntur; h. ille Gyges inducitur a Platone, C.; h. mihi prima mali labes, Vg.; quid facient comites, quibus h. toga, calceus h. est?, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ăbhinc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Härifrån:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i local mening:</text:span> aufer a. lacrimas, balatro, et compesce querellas, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fråga om tid = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">För detta, för - sedan,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">præp.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">abl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">acc.</text:span>: a. XXII annos; a. annis XV mortuus est, C., Hor.; a. triennium, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕhinc</text:span> (poet. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen enstafw.),</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fråga om rum: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Derifrån:</text:span></text:span> T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fråga om tid: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hädanefter; derefter:</text:span></text:span> d. deleo ex animo omnes mulieres, Ter.; Eurum ad se Zephyrumque vocat, d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(twåstafw.)</text:span> talia fatur; dona d. - ad naves ferri imperat, Vg.; d. - oppida condere coeperunt, Hor. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Derefter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ordningen:</text:span> arduum videtur res gestas scribere; primum quod -, d. quia -, Sa.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Häraf; derför:</text:span></text:span> d. conjicito, Pt.; d. postulo, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhinc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Derefter:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏdiē</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> ho die <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> hod die = hoc die; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Ritschl., Neue Plautinische Excurse</text:span> p. 89.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos</text:span> Pt. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förekommer ock</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>hocedie, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ritschl.</text:span> l. c.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Bergk, Beiträge</text:span> et cet. p. 85):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I dag:</text:span></text:span> h. me ante omnes comicos stultos senes versaris atque emunxeris lautissime, Cæcil. ap. C.; Ter.; C., Hor., Vg.<text:line-break/>2. hodie <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>hodieque = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nu för tiden; ännu i dag:</text:span></text:span> C., N.; h-eque, L. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Någonsin:</text:span></text:span> non h. dices, quorsum hæc tam putida tendant, Hor.; nunquam h. moriemur inulti, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏdiernus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Denne dagens; innewarande, den i dag warande:</text:span></text:span> dies, C.; consultatio, L.; quis scit, an adjiciant h-æ tempora summæ crastina di superi?, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hit:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. local men.:</text:span> quum h. veni, nil agere delectat, C.; h. propius me, dum doceo vos insanire, adite, Hor.; h. usque, Pn.; h. viciniæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hit i grannskapet),</text:span> Ter.; nunc h., nunc illuc versat Daretem, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hit</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">härtill, derhän:</text:span></text:span> adde h., si placet, unguentarios -; h. accedit summus timor, quem mihi natura tribuit; h. rem deduxi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bragt härtill, derhän);</text:span> hucine omnia reciderunt?; appetitus hominem h. et illuc rapit, C.; h. arrogantiæ venerat?, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhūc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. temporale: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tills nu; hittills; - ännu:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om närwarande tid med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">perf.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">præsens</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(conditionalt</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">impf.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">plusqpf.</text:span>):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hittills; tills nu:</text:span></text:span> dum tale facies, quale a., continuo edes; a. locorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(allt tills nu);</text:span> a. omnia constant, Pt.; eloquar id, quod a. semper tacui et tacendum putavi; hic mos usque a. est retentus; nihil a. scimus; id quidem nemini videor a. contigisse, C.; dixit a. alqd?, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ännu,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om ett ännu warande tillstånd:</text:span> a. de consuetudine loquor; a. tardior est ad te liberandum, C.; hanc, si quis a. precibus locus, exue mentem, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med tempora för förfluten tid:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">impf.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ett just nu upphördt tillstånd:</text:span> a. hæc erant, C. de Div. II. 1.; tempus, quod a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förut)</text:span> aut auferebatur aut surripiebatur, colligo, Sen. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i beroende satser</text:span> (oratio obliqua; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Mdvg</text:span> de Fin.): scripsi in quodam libello, disertos me cognosse nonnullos, eloquentem neminem a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ännu ingen),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i brefstil:</text:span> unam a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tills nu)</text:span> epistolam acceperam, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i wanligt och direct tal: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ännu</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (då):</text:span> bellicosiores ea tempestate erant Gallogræci, Gallicos a. servantes animos, L.; incolumi a. Augustā perfugium erat; Oriens a. immotus; multos spes acciverat occupandi principem a. immotum, T.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos silfweråldrens författare från den temporala betydelsen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ännu alltjemt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwergående till bet. af tillökning i antal, grad m. m.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ännu,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ytterligare:</text:span> a. est genus tertium, Sen.; pauculis a. diebus in Tusculano commorabor, Pn. ep.; a. difficilior, Qu.; melius a. eæ civitates, in quibus tantum virgines nubunt; si prohibuerunt sortes, nulla de eadem re in eundem diem consultatio: sin permissum, auspiciorum a. fides exigitur; si quis - vita superaverit, trahi a. in diversas terras, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭcĕtāon, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭcētas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekiska personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hiemalis, Hiematio, Hiemo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hiems.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>iempsal, ălis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">numidiskt personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hiems,</text:span> ĕmis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Winter, -tid:</text:span></text:span> erat h. summa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(midwinter),</text:span> tempestas frigida, imber maximus; non eum h-is vis, non nives deterrebant; h-e et æstate, C.; matura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tidig);</text:span> h. præcipitat; h-e confectā, Cs.; gelida et nivosa h., L.; humida solstitia atque h-es orate serenas, agricolæ, Vg.; h. informis, iniqua; solvitur acris h.; est, ubi plus tepeant h-es?; post certas h-es, Hor.; h. serotina, glacialis, Ov.; instat h., Ct.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Owäder, storm:</text:span></text:span> maritimos cursus præcludebat h-is magnitudo (mense Aprili), C.; servare navem ex h-e et mari scopuloso, N.; Neptunus sensit emissam h-em; imber noctem h-emque ferens, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Köld; storm:</text:span></text:span> letalis h. paulatim in pectora venit; pessima mutati coepit amoris h., Ov.; ferrea, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hībernus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Winter-,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (winterlig, wintrig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">kall,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> stormande (s. bär winterdrägt (om orter), frusen):</text:span> tunica, Pt.; soles; ventus; nox, Vg.; ignis h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(winterbrasa);</text:span> cubiculum; tempus; legio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. ligger i winterläger),</text:span> C.; annus; flumen; mare h-um turbat Orion; nive h-a turgidi fluvii; Jupiter h-as cana nive conspuit Alpes, Hor.; Alpes. T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hībernum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Winterrum:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hīberna</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Winter, wintertid:</text:span></text:span> ternaque transierint Rutulis h-a subactis, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Winterläger</text:span></text:span> (h-a castra): exercitum in h-is collocare, Cs.; componere, Sa.; in h-a dimittere exercitum, C.; h-a sumere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(taga),</text:span> N.; in h-a proficisci, concedere, L.; ex h-is educere, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hīberno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerwintra; ligga i winterqwarter:</text:span></text:span> pecus in tecta reducere h-tum, Varr.; milites h-ant; scire velim, ubi sis h-turus, C.<text:line-break/>b. mare h-at (”sævit vel a navigiis vacat, sicut naves h-re dicimus, quum non navigatur”, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Schol.),</text:span> Ps. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hībernācŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Winter-rum:</text:span></text:span> Pn. ep., Vitr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Winterläger</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span>): ædificare; munire; lignea h., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hiĕmālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Winter-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wintrig), wintrens, s. sker om wintren:</text:span> tempus, C., N.; vis; navigatio, C.; aquæ h-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(winterregn),</text:span> Sa.; nimbi, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hiĕmo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T3">intr.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wara wintrig, kall; storma:</text:span></text:span> dies, Pn.; auster, Col.; mare h-at defendens pisces suos, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="T3">impers.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det är winter, kallt:</text:span> Col., Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerwintra; ligga i winterqwarter:</text:span></text:span> h-at mercator mediis in undis, Hor.; ibi piratæ h-re solent; cupio scire, ubi sis h-turus, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T3">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Komma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bringa att frysa:</text:span></text:span> aquas frigus; lacu h-to, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hiĕmātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerwintrande:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrhiĕmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerwintra:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭĕra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">önamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hieracium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hierax.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭĕrāpŏlis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stadsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hĭĕrātĭcus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: charta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bestämdt till religiöst bruk),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭĕrax, ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hök:</text:span> (n. pr.) Js.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭĕrācĭum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ögonsalfwa (eg. höksalfwa):</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭĕrĭcho, ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">staden Iericho:</text:span> Pn. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭĕro, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hĭĕrōnĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭĕrŏcæsărēa <text:line-break/>(Hĭĕrŏcæsăria), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Lydien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hĭĕrŏcæsăriensis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭĕrŏcles, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭĕrŏcly̆tus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭĕrŏgly̆phĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: literæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(helig bildl. figurskrift),</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭĕrŏnīca</text:span>, ae <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">s</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egrare i heliga spel:</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭĕrōny̆mus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭĕrŏphantes</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭĕrŏphanta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som förewisar det heliga) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerste prest:</text:span></text:span> N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭĕrŏsŏly̆ma ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Hĭĕrŏsŏly̆ma, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Soly̆ma, Mt.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ierusalem:</text:span> C., T. <text:line-break/>Hĭĕrŏsŏly̆mārius, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hieto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭlăīra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn:</text:span> Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hĭlăris</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭlărus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Upprymd, gladlynt, munter, glädtig:</text:span></text:span> h-is vultus, animus; h-i convivæ; h-a vita; h-ores literæ, oculi, C.; oderunt h-em tristes, tristemque jocosi, Hor.; homo h-simus, Pt.; diem h-em sumere; h-em se facere, Ter. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭlăria</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fröjdefest:</text:span> Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭlăre</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Upprymdt, glädtigt:</text:span></text:span> vivere; accipi; esse apud alqm; loqui h-ius, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭlăresco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Blifwa upprymd:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭlărĭcŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Temligen glädtig:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭlărĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gladlynthet, gladt lynne, upprymdhet, munterhet:</text:span></text:span> in Lælio erat multa h., in Druso singularis severitas; tristitiam temporum h-e condire; h. mihi omnis erepta est; h-em in perpetuum amisi; librum h-e conspergere, C.; risus cum h-e, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭlărĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: modo acriter, modo h., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭlărĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span> = hilaritas: oculorum, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭlăro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Försätta i godt lynne, fägna, förnöja, göra glad, lifwa, muntra:</text:span></text:span> jucundus motus, quo sensus h-atur, voluptas appellatur; Periclis suavitate maxime h-tæ sunt Athenæ; terra cum cælo h-ta videtur, C.; convivia, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhĭlăro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Muntra, fägna, försätta i munter stämning, gifwa ett gladt utseende, uppfriska:</text:span></text:span> miraris, tam e-tam esse nostram servitutem?, C.; pecus pabulo e-atur, Col.; arbor flore, color e-atur, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭlărŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Temligen gladlynt:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hilla <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hira.<text:line-break/>Hilotes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Helotes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hīlum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: (id quod fabæ grano adhæret, Fs.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Litet; det minsta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ringaste:</text:span> Sisyphus saxum trudit sudando neque proficit h-um, poēt. ap. C.; videsne consulatum illum nostrum, - si hic factus erit, fabæ hilum futurum, C. (Ep. Att. I. 16. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Hoffm.);</text:span> de summa h. detrahere, Lucr. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Häraf troligtwis</text:span> nihĭlum, nihil).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrhīlum</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mycket litet, obetydligt:</text:span> ima vacillant p., Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ĭmella, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bäck i Sabinarnes land.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>īmĕra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod och stad på Sicilien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hinc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hinnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hinna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mulåsne, -a,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af häst och åsna:</text:span> ex equa et asino fit mulus, ex equo et asina h., Varr., Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hinnio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gnägga, wrinskas:</text:span></text:span> Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hinnībĭlis</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hinnībundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gnäggande:</text:span></text:span> Ap., Non.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hinnienter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: Non.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hinnītus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gnäggande, gnäggning:</text:span></text:span> equorum, L.; acutus, Vg.; tollere, Hor.; edere h-us, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhinnio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gnägga, wrinskas emot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, wid ngt:</text:span> equus equæ, Ov.; admissarius ad orationem alicujus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hinnŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mulåsne:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hinnŭleus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hjortkalf, ungt rå:</text:span></text:span> vitas h-o me similis, Chloë, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hio,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gapa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hafwa munnen öppen, uppspärrad:</text:span> lupus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gädda),</text:span> Hor.; inceptus clamor frustratur hiantes (umbras); leo immane hians, Vg.; canis ad spem futuri, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wara remnad, sprucken:</text:span></text:span> terra, semina æstibus, Col.; ligna ariditate, Pn.; flos, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om talet och den talande = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bilda hiatus</text:span></text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">låta vocaler sammanstöta, (om poeter) ej iakttaga synaloephe):</text:span> antiqui poētæ, ut versus facerent, sæpe h-bant, C.; sermo vocalibus hiat, Qu. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">isynn. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">part. præs.</text:span>: oratio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gapande, illa hopfogadt),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gapa = wara lysten, glupsk, gapa efter ngt:</text:span> avaritia hians; h. et poscere alqd, C.; emptorem hiantem inducere, Hor.; cupiditates amicorum hiantes intendere, T.; fraudes, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hiātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gap, gapande, öppning, swalg, remna:</text:span></text:span> cibum oris h-u capessere; terræ; quum terra discessisset imbribus, Gyges in h-um descendit, C.; spelunca alta fuit vastoque immanis h-u, Vg.; quid tanto h-u feret dignum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en, som tager munnen full)?,</text:span> Hor.; profundus, Pn.; exspirantis, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">vocalers sammanstötning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hiatus:</text:span></text:span> habet ille tanquam h. concursu vocalium molle quiddam, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr om</text:span> hiatus C. Or. 52.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ritschl</text:span> Prolegg. ad Plauti Trinummum 200 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.).</text:span><text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gapande = snålt fikande efter ngt:</text:span> præmiorum, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hiĕto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stå och gapa; förgapa sig på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> ibi dum hieto, ille mihi se subterduxit, Pt. Men. III. 1. 4.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hisco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gapa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öppna munnen; prægn.: = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tala;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">knysta, mucka:</text:span></text:span> diu h. non poterat, L.; raris turbatus vocibus h-o, Vg.; respondebisne ad hæc aut omnino h-re audebis?, C.; ne h-re quidem audet, L.; si h-re quidquam ausit, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öppna sig, remna:</text:span></text:span> ædes, Pt.; terra alicui, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕhisco</text:span>, hīvi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gapa, öppna sig, springa upp, remna, utspricka:</text:span></text:span> his unda d-ens terram inter fluctus aperit; attonitæ magna ora domus; tellus mihi d-at, antequam -, Vg.; terram dehisse ajunt, Varr.; acies hostium, L.; arbor, Cato; cælum, Ov.; rosa; mons; rictus; uterus, Pn.; ratis resoluto robore labens pressa d-scit, (Sen.) Oct. 320.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hiulcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gapande; remnande, -ig, klufwen:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> (Sirius) findit siti h-a arva, Vg.; fulmen, St.; nubes, Cd.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om talet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gapande, ojemn, löst hopfogad:</text:span></text:span> componere verba sic, ut neque asper eorum concursus neque h-us sit, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Snål, glupsk:</text:span></text:span> gens, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hiulce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: aspere, vaste, h. loqui, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hiulco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Komma att remna,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spricka:</text:span> æstus agros, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gapa emot, efter, öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttr.:</text:span> puer uberibus lupæ, C.; tenuit i-ns tria Cerberus ora, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gapa efter, på = med förwåning, lystnad, ängslan, nyfiken wäntan betrakta; förgapa sig uti = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fika, wara lysten efter:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">acc.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">dat.</text:span>): turba miratur euntem, attonitis i-ns animis; (hostiarum) pectoribus i-ns spirantia consulit exta, Vg.; i-ns congestis saccis indormit (avarus), Hor.; i-re aurum, Pt.; varios pulcra testudine postes, Vg.; omnia, quibus vulgus i-at, ultro citroque fluunt, Sen.; hortis alicujus Messalina, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hippăcē,</text:span> es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ost af stomjölk:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippăgus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippăgōgus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: L. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippagĭnes</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span> Gell.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Färja,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarpå hästar öfwerföras.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ipparchus, <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippărīnus, <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippăsus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippĭas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippo, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stadsnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hippōnensis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippŏcămēlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hästkamel):</text:span> Aus. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippŏcampus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sjöhäst):</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippŏcentaurus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: C.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fabeldjur.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippŏcŏon, ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippŏcrătes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippŏcrēnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Musernas källa på Helicon.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippŏdămas, antis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippŏdămē, es, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hippŏdămīa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mythiska personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippŏdrŏmus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kappkörningsbana, -rännarebana:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippŏly̆tus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hippŏly̆tē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippŏmănes</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Slem</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af sto l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">utwäxt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ett föls panna, begagnade till kärleksdrycker:</text:span> h. lentum destillat ab inguine (equæ) virus, - quod sæpe malæ legere novercæ, Vg.; Juv. VI. 133.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippŏmĕdon, ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippŏmĕnes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hippŏmĕnēĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hippŏmĕnēis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippōnax, actis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hippōnactēus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippŏnīcus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippŏpēra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kappsäck:</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippŏpŏdes</text:span>, um, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fabelmenniskor, med hästfötter:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippŏpŏtămus</text:span>, i <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Flodhäst:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippŏsĕlīnum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wild persilja:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippŏtes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Hippŏtădes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ippŏthŏus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Hippŏthŏē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hippŏtoxŏta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Beriden bågskytt:</text:span></text:span> Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hir,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">indecl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hand:</text:span></text:span> Lucil. ap. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hīra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tarm, fjelster:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hilla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tarm, korf:</text:span></text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hircus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(ircus, <text:line-break/>fircus, Varr.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bock, getabock:</text:span></text:span> stabit sacer h. ad aras; tondere barbam h-i; jungere vulpes et mulgere h-os <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ordspråk om orimligheter),</text:span> Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om osnygga, otuktiga mskor:</text:span> Pt., Su. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">swett, armswett:</text:span> gravis h. cubat in alis; olere h-um, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hircīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är af l. tillhör bock, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bock-:</text:span></text:span> barba, Pt.; pellis, Pn.; alæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stinkande),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hirco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skrika s. en lo:</text:span> Philom.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hircōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stinkande, frän:</text:span></text:span> osculum, Mt.; gens h-a centurionum, Ps.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hircŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hirnea</text:span> <text:line-break/>(hernea, <text:line-break/>irnea), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags kärl:</text:span> fictilis, Cato; implere vini h-am, Pt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton.</text:span> = potor, Vg. Cat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>irpīni <text:line-break/>(Irpīni), ōrum <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">samnitiskt folk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hirpīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hirsūtus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Raggig, ruggig, lurfwig, luden, taggig:</text:span></text:span> barba; comæ; genæ; fera, Ov.; capella, Juv.; aliæ animantes villis vestitæ, aliæ spinis h-æ, C.; castaneæ h-æ; supercilium; capellæ h.; cristā h-us equinā, Vg.; Ennius h-ā (querna?) cingat sua scripta coronā, me folia ex hedera porrige, Bacche, tua, Ppt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = obildad:</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>irtius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hirtīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hirtus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Raggig, tofwig, lurfwig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (okammad); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">grof; obildad:</text:span></text:span> oves, Varr.; pecus, Col.; capellæ, Ov.; ora; comæ, Ct.; tunica, N.; ingenium, Hor.; melius est oratorem vel h-ā togā induere, quam fucatis et meretriciis vestibus insignire, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hĭrūdo,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Igel:</text:span></text:span> non missura cutem, nisi plena cruoris, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. (utsugare);</text:span> ærarii, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hĭrundo,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Swala:</text:span></text:span> arguta, Vg.; prænuntia veris, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hĭrundĭnīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hisco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ispălis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Spanien (Sevilla).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hispălensis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hispăliensis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hispălienses, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inw. i H.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ispānus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spansk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hispāni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Spanerne.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hispānia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hispānĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hispāniensis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är l. sker i Sp.:</text:span> bellum, Js.; exercitus, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hispĭdus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Borstig, lurfwig, ruskig; upprifwen,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> härjad:</text:span> sus, Phdr.; setis h. aper, Ap.; aspectu h., Pn.; facies; agri, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ispo, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ispulla, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. Hister <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ister.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Hister</text:span>, v. etrusca: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skådespelare:</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Histrĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har afseende på skådespelare, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Theater-:</text:span></text:span> imperator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(directör),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Histrio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skådespelare, actör:</text:span></text:span> h-um levis ars; ergo hoc h. videbit in scena, non videbit sapiens vir in vita?; clarus h.; actio h-is, C.; h. comoediarum, tragoediarum; h-um personæ, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Histriōnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skådespelare-, theater-:</text:span></text:span> studium, modi, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Histriōnĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: id.: Cap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Histriōnĭca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Histriōnia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skådespelarekonst:</text:span></text:span> Lpd., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Histon,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wäfkammare:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Histŏrĭa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Historia</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = (häfdeforskning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">häfdateckning; historieskrifning; historiskt werk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">berättelse:</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">historiska werk, arbeten; historien:</text:span></text:span> prima lex h-æ est, ne quid falsi dicere audeat, deinde ne quid veri dicere non audeat; Herodotus pater h-æ; h-am scribere; ad h-am scribendam se applicare; h-am distinguere locorum varietate, verborum collocatione; abest h. literis nostris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(saknas i wår literatur);</text:span> a te flagitatur h.; laudationibus funebribus h. nostra est facta mendosior; h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i mots. till</text:span> fabula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> argamentum) est gesta res a nostræ ætatis memoria remota; Cyrus ille Xenophonteus non ad fidem h-æ scriptus; talibus exemplis non modo fabulæ, verum etiam h-æ refertæ sunt; cognoscendæ h-æ sunt; a perpetuis suis h-is ea bella, quæ dixi, separaverunt, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om skilnaden mellan</text:span> annales <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> h-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gell. V. 18.; quidquid Græcia mendax audet in h-ā -, Juv.; h-am componere, Js.; magna, viri, merces: Crassum clademque piate. Ite et Romanæ consulite h-æ, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Erfarenhet, berättelse,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ur menniskowerlden l. naturens företeelser:</text:span> Chrysippus est in omni h-a curiosus, C.; h-am (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">minnen, erfarenhetsrön)</text:span> veterem atque antiquam hæc mea ætas sustinet; quin nos domum redimus, nisi si h-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(resebeskrifning)</text:span> scripturi sumus?, Pt.; ad hanc rem h. opus est, Varr.; naturalis h., Pn.; - fieres nobilis h-ā, Ppt.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Myther, fabler, mythologiska berättelser</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> historice): satis h-arumst, Pt. Bacch. 158.; in grammaticis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till philologien hörer)</text:span> poētarum pertractatio, h-arum cognitio, verborum interpretatio, C.; peccare docentes fallax h-as docet, Hor.; hactenus h-æ: nunc ad tua devehor astra, Ppt. (V. 1. 119.); fabulosæ h-æ, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Histŏrĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Historisk:</text:span></text:span> historiam oratorio, non h-o genere perscribere, C.; fides, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Histŏrĭcus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Historieskrifware, häfdatecknare:</text:span></text:span> philosophi, poētæ, h-i; quot h-os nominavit!, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Histŏrĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på historiskt sätt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I historisk stil:</text:span></text:span> Pn. ep.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Histŏrĭcē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den historiske (saklige) delen af grammatiken (philologien) i motsats till den språklige</text:span> (enarratio poētarum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mots. till</text:span> ratio loquendi), Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Histŏriŏgrăphus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Häfdatecknare:</text:span></text:span> Capit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Histr . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Hister.<text:line-break/>Hiulc . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hio.<text:line-break/>Hodie, -diernus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hic.<text:line-break/>Hoedus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med härledn. se</text:span> Hædus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hŏlŏporphy̆rus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">helt och hållet af purpur:</text:span> stola, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏlŏsērĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">helsiden:</text:span> vestis, Lpd.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏlŏsphȳrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: æs <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(massiv),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Holus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Olus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ŏmērus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den episka diktens fader, Iliadens och Odysséens författare, till sin nationalitet en Ionier från mindre Asien (Smyrna).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hŏmērĭăcus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Hŏmērĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: senex <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hos Homerus),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>Hŏmērĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏmērista</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. declamerar Homeri sånger.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏmērŏmastix</text:span>, īgis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som kritiserar Homerus, i allm. tadlare:</text:span> Vitr., Pn. <text:line-break/>Hŏmērōnĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. efterliknar Homerus:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hŏmo,</text:span> ĭnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">m., f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(archaist,</text:span> hemo; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> nemo; homōnis, Liv. Andr., Enn.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Menniska:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. (menniska, person):</text:span> inter h-em et beluam hoc maxime interest; natura h-em conciliat h-i; h-es h-um causa generati sunt; quid interest, animi motu sublato, non dico inter h-em et pecudem, sed inter h-em et truncum et saxum?; ratione utentium duo genera ponunt, deorum et h-um, C.; h-um sator atque deorum; vox h-em sonat, Vg.; h. nihili, bonæ frugis; omnis generis, sexūs h-es, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Man:</text:span></text:span> h. magnus, clarissimus, severus, gravis, facetus, abjectus, Græcus, nobilis, novus, consularis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">m. m.;</text:span> h. servus, C.; h. durus, Sa.; h. maximi corporis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stor karl),</text:span> N. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">menniskor = lefwande l. tillsammans lefwande mskor (menskligt umgänge; folk):</text:span> inter h-es esse desierat; inter h-es esse; ab h-bus relegare alqm, C.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Menniskor i allmänhet; allmänheten; folk;</text:span></text:span> alcujus h-es = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngns landsmän:</text:span> hoc majus est, quam h-es opinantur; ea artificia improbantur, quæ in odia h-um incurrunt; nostri h-es minus student literis, quam Latini, C. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prægnant: menniska = förnuftig warelse; warelse med menskliga känslor; dödlig, swag, ofullkomlig warelse:</text:span> sunt quidam homines non re, sed nomine, C.; si h. esses, Ter.; est h. et nos diligit; ea stultitia est, ut nemo eam h-em appellare possit, C.; h. sum: nihil humani a me alienum puto, Ter.; quid cum eo disseras, qui h-em ex h-e tollat?, C.; censen me h-em esse?, Ter.; h. nata fuerat (Tullia tua), Sulp. ap. C.; Demosthenes et Homerus summi sunt, sed h-es tamen, Qu.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tilltal: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Karl;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om en förutnämnd person: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">mannen, karlen, </text:span></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">personen:</text:span></text:span> quid h-is es?; persuasit h-i, Ter.; aut insanit h. aut versus facit, Hor.<text:line-break/>f. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngns </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tjenare;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">folk, karlar:</text:span></text:span> certum h-em mittere ad alqm, N.; alere filiam et ejus h-es, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏmĭcīda</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">c.</text:span>: (cædo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mandråpare, mördare, -erska:</text:span></text:span> C.; L.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om qwinna),</text:span> Pn. - h. Hector <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(”den mannamördande”),</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏmĭcīdium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mandråp, dråp:</text:span></text:span> C.; luitur h. certo pecorum numero, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏmuncio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egentl.</text:span> ampliativum: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Karl;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oftast = swag menniska:</text:span> h. lepidissimus, Su.; nos h-es sumus: omnia nobis negare non possumus, Sen.; (quod deus fecisset), ego h. non facerem?, Ter. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏmuncŭlus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏmullus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arm, swag, usel menniska; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Usling:</text:span></text:span> deus ille -, h-ulus hic, C.; brevis hic est fructus h-ullis, Lucr.; quid cessat hic h-ullus?, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmānus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(hominanus), <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mensklig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. o. eg.: som tillhör menniskor, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">mensklig, mennisko-:</text:span></text:span> genus h-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> h-um genus; species et figura h-a, C.; gens h-a; ut ridentibus arrident, ita flentibus adsunt vultus h-i, Hor.; h. animi, corpora, societas, condicio, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. och oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mots. till gudomlig l. fullkomlig = mensklig, allmänt mensklig; menskligt swag l. ofullkomlig:</text:span> res divinæ et h.; Homerus h-a ad deos transferebat; totum cælum h-o genere completum reperiemus, C.; h-a vitia; possum falli ut h-us; est h-um, quod ita existimas, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mensklig, i mots. till djurisk, (djefwulsk):</text:span> in bestiis apparet similitudo amoris h-i; a fera agrestique vita ad cultum h-um et civilem deducere; utinam posses hæc aliqua ratione, quamvis falsa, tamen h-a et usitata defendere, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Timlig, förgänglig;</text:span></text:span> res h-æ = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det timliga, timligheten, werlden:</text:span> una est res in rebus h-is, de cujus utilitate omnes consentiant; omnibus rebus h-is amicitiam anteponere; h-a contemnere; res h-as despicere; res h-æ fragiles sunt; rerum h-arum imbecillitas, C. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tålig, undergifwen:</text:span></text:span> sensus moderatissimus et h-simus, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mensklig, menniskowänlig, artig, human, hygglig:</text:span></text:span> ingenium; hocine est h-um factum?, Ter.; comis erga Lysandrum et h. fuit; homo facillimus et h-simus, C.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bildad:</text:span></text:span> gens h-a et docta; homo doctissimus et h-simus, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmāne</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som en menniska:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Undergifwet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med resignation):</text:span> pati, Ter.; humana h. ferre; morbos toleranter atque h. ferre; h-ius facere alqd, C. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wänligt, humant, ädelt:</text:span></text:span> fecit h.: tu etiam h-ius; h-sime et diligentissime loqui C.; juvare alqm, Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hyggligt, trefligt:</text:span></text:span> intervalla vides h. commoda <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ironi),</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŭmānĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mensklighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = menskligt wäsende, mensklig art:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Menniskonaturen, menskliga naturen:</text:span></text:span> vim omnem h-is perspexisse debet orator; magna vis est h-is et naturæ; ista feritas ex communi tanquam h-is corpore segreganda est; quid magis proprium est h-is, quam sermo facetus et in nulla re rudis?, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mensklighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i känslor; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">menskliga känslor; ädelt, warmt hjerta;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> godhet emot ngn:</text:span> communis; h. et misericordia; h-is mollitudo; non modo id virtutis non est, sed etiam immanitatis omnem h-em repellentis; exuere, abjicere omnem h-em; vult hoc multitudo, patitur consuetudo, fert etiam h.; cadit in sapientem animi dolor, nisi omnem h-em ex ejus animo exstirpatam putamus; respondeo, te non potuisse non commoveri neque id fuisse h-is tuæ; omisit et pietatem et h-em; h-e duci; h. erga alqm, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Humanitet liberalitet:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i sätt och beteende):</text:span> video, Philippum Alexandro facilitate et h-e superiorem fuisse; h-is responsio est, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Folkwett, lefnadswett, hygglighet, artighet, trefligt sätt, umgängesgåfwor, finhet, smak,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i tal, sätt o. s. w.:</text:span> ea, quæ multum discrepant ab h-te (ut si quis in foro saltet), C.; contumeliosa etiam h., Sen.; tanta fuit in Crasso h., ut omnis tristitia - tolleretur, C.; summa erat in viro h.; capere alqm sua h-e, N.; Socrates in hac ironia longe lepore et h-e omnibus præstitit; sermone, literis, h-e alicujus delectari, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bildning:</text:span></text:span> in omni h-is genere orator perfectus esse debet; expers politioris h-is; vir h-e politus; disputare de studiis h-is; omnes partes h-is; inops h-is; eæ artes, quibus puerorum mentes ad h-em et virtutem finguntur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmānĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som en menniska; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Undergifwet; artigt:</text:span></text:span> te docebo, quid sit h. vivere (si occupationibus me relaxaro); sin aliter acciderit, h. feremus; h. fecit, quod ad me venit, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmānĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på menskligt wis, enligt menniskors lott:</text:span> si quid mihi h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ngt menskligt)</text:span> accidisset (i. e. ut morerer), C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Med wänlighet, godhet:</text:span></text:span> coepi juvenem non h., sed vi tractare, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhūmānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">En menniska owärdig; hjertlös, omensklig, menniskofiendtlig:</text:span></text:span> nihil est tam i-um, quam eloquentiam ad bonorum pestem convertere; vox i-a; i-um est peregrinos urbe prohibere; non est i-a virtus neque immunis neque superba; Chremes non i.; vir asperior et i., C.; libido; crudelitas, L.; barbaria, Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ohyfsad, obildad, s. saknar folkwett, osällskaplig:</text:span></text:span> ingenium; miles, Ter.; agrestis et i-a negligentia, C.; (si quid secum meditetur) in convivio, i-us videatur inscitiā temporis, C.; surge et i-æ senium depone Camenæ, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwermensklig:</text:span></text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhūmāne</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hjertlöst, omenskligt:</text:span></text:span> nimis cruciat adolescentem, Ter.; facere; i-ius dicere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhūmānĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Omensklighet:</text:span></text:span> mansuetudo nostri imperii in i-em conversa est, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Brist på folkwett; osällskaplighet, wrånghet, otreflighet:</text:span></text:span> sit hoc i-is tuæ; morositas et i. omni ætati molesta est; hoc non i-e neque superbiā faciebam; sordes et i-em populus non amat, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhūmānĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ohöfligt:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrhūmānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mycket human, höflig:</text:span></text:span> sermonem habere cum aliquo, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrhūmānĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: scribere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hŏmœŏmĕrīa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">likhet mellan delarne:</text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ŏmŏlē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Thessalien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏmōny̆mus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har lika namn, är till namnet lika:</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏmōny̆mĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namnlikhet:</text:span> Fronto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏmŏtŏnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lika spänd:</text:span> nervus, Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Homullus, Homunc . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Homo. <text:line-break/>Honest . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Honor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hŏnor</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hŏnos,</text:span> ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Varr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stamslägtadt med</text:span> onus)<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Heder,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som wisas och njutes:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Heder, hedersbewisning, -betygelse; anseende:</text:span></text:span> h-em alicui tribuere, habere; h-e afficere alqm; habere alqm in h-e; esse in h-e apud alqm; res est alicui honori; tantus eos h. prosequitur amicorum, C.; nullus h. ei defuit, N.; semper h. nomenque tuum laudesque manebunt; multo h-e compellare alqm; multa viri virtus animo multusque recursat gentis h-os, Vg.; numero plures, virtute et h-e minores, Hor.; h-is causa nominare alqm, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rang, hedersställe, wärdighet, embete:</text:span></text:span> certamen h-is et gloriæ; in h-bus versari; h-bus inservire; h-es et imperia, h-es et potestates; ad h-es amplissimos perduci, ascendere; h-es adipisci; h-bus fungi, perfungi, defungi; cursus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bana)</text:span> h-um; decursu h-um, C.; h-bus operam dare; h-es petere, capere, gerere; contendere de h-e cum aliquo; ad h-es pervenire, N.; rapti Ganymedis h-es, Vg.; - dat census h-es, Ov.; quid pure tranquillat, h. an dulce lucellum, an -?; tollere alqm tergeminis h-bus, Hor.; summus h. (= magistratus), Juv.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hedersgärd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt gudarne l. åt manerna, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">offer;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt: förstlingsoffer af ngt:</text:span> Bacchoque suum dicemus h-em; supplex aris imponit h-em; divom templis indicit h-em; in mensam laticum libavit h-em; Jovi Lenæum libare h-em; Anchisæ meritos inferre h-es (inferias), Vg.; est h. et tumulis: animas placate paternas, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hedersgärd, -skänk, belöning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt mskor</text:span> (honorarium); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">kamp-, täflingspris:</text:span></text:span> quod viris fortibus h. habitus est, laudo; h-es alicui decernere, constituere; medico h-em habere, C.; populi Romani h-es quondam fuerunt rari et tenues ob eamque causam gloriosi, nunc autem effusi atque obsoleti, N.; ipsis præcipuos ductoribus (navium) addit h-es; geminum pugnæ proponit h-em, Vg.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Artighet, compliment:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> alter alterius sermone meros audiret h-es, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span> h-em præfari, C., dicere, Pn., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bedja om ursäkt, säga ”med förlof”, då man tillåter sig grofwa l. stötande yttranden.</text:span><text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skönhet, fägring, behag:</text:span></text:span> lætos oculis afflarat h-es (Venus Aeneæ), Vg.; nedum sermonis stet h-os et gratia vivax; non semper idem floribus est h-os vernis, Hor.; ne armentis quidem suus h. et gloria frontis, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnestus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: (: honoratus = modestus: moderatus = onustus: oneratus):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hederlig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hedrad, aktad, ansedd; förnäm:</text:span></text:span> qui honorem sententiis, qui suffragiis adeptus est, is mihi h. et honoratus videtur; civitas; equites; homo, C.; viri clari magis quam h-i; non ideo tuti aut magis h-i sunt, Sa.; h-o genere, loco natus, N.; rusticus urbano confusus, turpis h-o, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hederlig, anständig; hedrande:</text:span></text:span> hæ artes sunt iis, quorum ordini conveniunt, h-æ, C.; utinam mors mearum fortunarum h-us exitus esset!; omnium rerum h-arum egens, Sa.; non eadem omnibus h-a, N.; scortum proponere h-o officio, Hor.; prima sequentem h-um est in secundis tertiisve consistere; dies alicui h-simus, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i och för sig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hederlig, ärbar, hederwärd; ädel; sedlig, dygdig; moraliskt riktig, god:</text:span></text:span> cives optimi et h-simi, C.; libertinus; soror, Hor.; ea fit inter eos h-a certatio; eorum vita in rebus h-is perspecta est; doctrina rerum h-arum, C.; rem actionemve h-am deponere; amicorum causā h-a faciamus, ab amicis h-a petamus; nisi h-um et rectum nihil postulare; consultare, utrum quid h-um factu an turpe sit, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnestum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det hederliga = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Det sedliga, moraliskt rätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. ngt sedligt o. s. w.:</text:span> primum est de h-o, tum de utili disserendum; quæritur duobus propositis h-is, utrum h-ius; decorum et h-um per se placet, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till utseendet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ädel, skön:</text:span></text:span> formam nostram reliquamque figuram, in qua esset h-a species, natura posuit in promptu, C.; esse formā h-ā et liberali, Ter.; os, caput, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnestas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hederlighet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wärdighet, heder:</text:span></text:span> in officio colendo omnis vitæ h. sita est et in eo negligendo turpitudo; alqm h-is gratiā nominare; privare, spoliare alqm h-e; amittere h-em; si est h. in rebus, exsistit ex rei natura quidam splendor in verbis; ceteræ ante partæ h-es, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sedlighet, dygd:</text:span></text:span> omnis h. manat e partibus quattuor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(de 4 cardinaldygderna);</text:span> h. aut sola aut maxime expetenda est; omnia commodis suis, non h-e metiri; - pars h-is confecta est, quam cupio tibi esse notissimam; h-em cum voluptate copulare, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skönhet:</text:span></text:span> h. testudinis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(cupolens),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏneste</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hederligt:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. natus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af hederlig, aktad slägt),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ärbart, dygdigt, sedligt, rätt:</text:span></text:span> vivere, Ter., C.; se gerere; hæc in nostris rebus non satis h-e, in amicorum h-sime fiunt, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skönt, sirligt:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnestĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span> = honestas: Acc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnesto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hedra, utmärka; pryda:</text:span></text:span> non domo dominus, sed domino domus h-da est; sanguine alicujus non modo non se contaminare, sed etiam h-re; elocutionem, C.; pudor formam, ætas <text:soft-page-break/>opera h-at, Ct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnestāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: virtus non eget h-o, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhŏnesto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bidraga till att hedra; hedra:</text:span></text:span> funus; exsequias, C.; victoriam, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕhŏnestus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Simpel, ful:</text:span></text:span> verbum, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕhŏnesto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wanhedra, -pryda; utskämma, göra skam åt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> famam maculari et d-ri, L.; Claudium vel remisse vel serio agentem alqd multa d-bant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i det yttre),</text:span> Su.; proavum infami opera, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕhŏnestāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skam, skamfläck; wanprydnad:</text:span></text:span> his amicitiarum d-is (scurris et c.) Vitellius valde gaudebat; oris, T.; originis, Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhŏnestus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skamlig, neslig; låg, simpel:</text:span></text:span> cupiditas, C.; vita, Sa.; mors, Ppt.; homo turpissimus et i-simus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ful:</text:span></text:span> homo, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhŏneste</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På wanhederligt, gement sätt:</text:span></text:span> parare divitias, Ter.; accusare alqm, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhŏnesto</text:span>, 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utskämma, göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">skam:</text:span></text:span> palmas adeptas, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhŏnestāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōrārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tilldelas, eges, är för hedrens skull; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Heders-:</text:span></text:span> arbitrium; arbiter; frumentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. friwilligt betalas åt en provinsföreståndare),</text:span> C.; ludi h-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. gåfwos för erhållet embete l. hörde till embetet),</text:span> Su. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōrārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hedersskänk,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">honorarium:</text:span></text:span> Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōrĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hedrande, hederlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för föremålet):</text:span> oratio; nunquam ab eo mentio facta est de me, nisi h-a; res h-entior; verba; senatus consultum h-simum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōrĭfĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På hedrande sätt, med aktning:</text:span></text:span> tractare; dicere in alqm; non potuit fieri h-ius; appellare alqm h-sime, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōrĭfĭcentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Heder, prakt:</text:span></text:span> Vop.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhŏnōrĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förnärmande:</text:span></text:span> dictum, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrhŏnōrĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mycket hedrande, aktningsfull:</text:span></text:span> consalutatio in alqm p-a, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrhŏnōrĭfĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōrĭpĕta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: (peto): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som fikar efter ära, wärdighet:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hedra, utmärka, förherrliga:</text:span></text:span> h-ri ab h-ato viro, poēt. ap. C.; laudibus alqm, C.; virtutem; diem, L.; donis alqm, Ct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hedrad, aktad, ansedd:</text:span></text:span> beati, qui h-i sunt, videntur, miseri autem, qui inhonorati; militia h-ior; apud plebem h-ior, L.<text:line-break/>b. = honoribus præditus: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förnäm, högt uppsatt, i högt stånd:</text:span></text:span> vir clarus et h.; h. et princeps; h. et nobilis; Metello erant quattuor h-i filii; habet senectus, præsertim h-a, tantum auctoritatis, ut -, C.; vir imaginis h-simæ, L.; Achilles h., Hor.; locus h-simus, Val.; familia vetus et h-a, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōrābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hedrande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. bringar ngn heder:</text:span> hæc ipsa sunt h-a, <text:soft-page-break/>quæ videntur esse levia, assurgi et c., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōrābĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med heder, hedersbewisning:</text:span> Cap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōrāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På ett</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för föremålet) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hedrande sätt; med aktning; hederligt:</text:span></text:span> custodire alqm, T.; revocare, Js.; excipere, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhŏnōrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ej hedrad; utan hedersbewisning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">belöning:</text:span></text:span> dea, Ov.; post victoriam i-simi, L.; alqm mortuum i-um transmittere, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ej förnäm; af ringa ställning; utan utwärtes anseende, oansenlig:</text:span></text:span> vita i-a et ingloria; multi i-i et propter id ipsum beatiores, C.; triumphus (in monte Albano) i-or, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏnōrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hedrande:</text:span></text:span> oratio; facere, disserere h-a in alqm, T.; fama, Ov.; nomen, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhŏnōrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ej hedrad, wanärad, ej ansedd:</text:span></text:span> deus; civitas, Pn.; signa, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hoplītes,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tungt bewäpnad fotknekt:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hoplŏmăchus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags gladiator:</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hōra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Timme;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ofta i allm. = (en kortare tid,) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">stund:</text:span></text:span> prima, tertia etc. h. (diurna), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kl.</text:span> 6, 8 etc., C.; decem h-is nocturnis sex et quinquaginta millia passuum pervolavit; ab h-a tertia bibebatur; uti suis h-is; legitimæ h-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(de åt en sakförare medgifna);</text:span> in h-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för stunden)</text:span> vivere, C.; matutina; meridiana; vespertina, Pn.; quota est h.? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwilken timme på dagen är det?);</text:span> grata superveniet, quæ non sperabitur h.; mutari in h-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för hwarje timme),</text:span> Hor.; crescere in h-as, Vg.; homo omnium h-arum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(alltid färdig,</text:span> ”toujours”), Qu. - <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span> h-æ = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ur,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> watten- l. solur:</text:span> quum machinatione quadam moveri alqd videmus, ut sphæram, ut h-as -; mittere ad h-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för att se på uret),</text:span> C.; h-as quærere, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Årstid; wäderlek:</text:span></text:span> Juppiter mundum temperat variis h-is, Hor. - h. anni, Pn. (?); nunquam te fallet crastina h., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ōræ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Horerna,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> årstiderna personificerade:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hōrārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ur:</text:span></text:span> Cens.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hornus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hornōtĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som tillhör årstiden, som är årets wäxt, skörd, producter; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Årets:</text:span></text:span> vina, fruges hornæ, Hor.; agni horni, Ppt.; frumentum h-tinum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horno</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I år:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hōrŏlŏgĭum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Timwisare, ur:</text:span></text:span> C.; h. solarium, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hōroscŏpus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwarpå man ser timmarne:</text:span> vasa, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hōroscŏpus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nativitetsställning:</text:span> Man.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hōroscŏpo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utforska denna:</text:span> Man.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trĭhōrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tre timmars tid:</text:span></text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ŏra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på Hersilia såsom gudinna:</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hōræum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fisklake:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Horarium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hōra.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ŏrātius, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span> (Q. Hor. Flaccus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. skald,</text:span> † 746 a. u. c.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Horda <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fordus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hordeum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen</text:span> <text:line-break/>ordeum): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Korn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. sädesslag; wanl. ej brukadt till bröd af Romarne):</text:span> Cato, Pn., Col.; h-o pascere milites <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ss. straff),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hordeāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är af korn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Korn-:</text:span></text:span> panis, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hordeārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. lefwer på kornbröd:</text:span> Pn., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hordus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fordus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hordicālia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slagt af</text:span> forda: Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hŏria,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŏriŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fiskarebåt:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hŏrior,</text:span> 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Pådrifwa:</text:span></text:span> Enn. ap. Diom. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stamverb till</text:span> hortor, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se detta.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hŏrizon,</text:span> ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Horizont, synkrets</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lat.</text:span> finiens, Cic.): Man.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Horn . . ., Horologium, Horoscop . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hōra.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Horreo,</text:span> ui, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Stå styf):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i massa) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stå upp, stå styf, skjuta upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från en yta:</text:span> comæ; setæ, Ov.; h-ent per totum corpus villi, Pn.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ofta om en massa (”skog”) af lyftade wapen:</text:span> hastæ h-entes; h-entia (= infesta) Martis arma, Vg. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> c.).<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ytan (kroppen, fältet) sjelf:</text:span> h. aliqua re = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wara besatt, öfwertäckt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med styfwa, uppstående ting, ss.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wara borstig, wara raggig; wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">stå ruggig:</text:span></text:span> casa Romuli h-bat culmo; squamis serpens; Rutulus thoraca indutus ahenis h-bat squamis, Vg.; hastis campus h-et, Enn.; galeis densisque virûm hastis h-uit seges; ager late hastis h-et; h-entia suum terga; h-ens leo, rubus, Vg. - non potest eodem tempore terra florere et h-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bära blommor och bära stubb),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bibetydelse: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stå orörlig, bister, dyster, hemsk:</text:span></text:span> non toto anno h-et tempestas; verba h-entia minis, Ov.; umbræ h-entes, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skälfwa, darra, rysa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> segetes aquilonibus, Ov.; totus tremo et h-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af fruktan),</text:span> Ter.; reddere tunicam servo h-enti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af köld),</text:span> Juv.; frigoribus, Col. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rysa, bäfwa, fasa, bli skygg, frukta för:</text:span></text:span> pericula; minas; conspectum alicujus; deorum conscientiam; ingrati animi crimen; h-o, quorsus hæc dominatio eruptura sit; ea nemo vir non adspicere h-et, C.; equus varios strepitus h-et; animus meminisse h-et luctuque refugit, Vg.; h-o, ne illæ res magis nos ceperint, quam nos illas; h-bant veram justamque mox in se versuram potestatem, L.; pauperiem, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrendus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ryslig, förfärlig, hemsk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (äfwen om det, som wäcker en helig fasa, rädd wördnad):</text:span> monstrum h-um, informe, ingens; vox <text:soft-page-break/>h-a; h-us visu; virgo; Sibylla, Vg.; lex erat h-i carminis, L.; nox; sonus, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrendum</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rysligt:</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horresco</text:span>, rui, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Resa sig, skjuta upp; resa borst; bli borstig, besatt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> mare coepit h-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppröras),</text:span> C.; seges ensibus, Vg.; tempestas, nimbus, Sil.; sætis, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Börja skälfwa, rysa; bäfwa:</text:span></text:span> segetes flabris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bölja),</text:span> Vg.; h-o referens; h-re visu, Vg.; etiam feræ sibi injecto terrore mortis h-unt; crimen h., C.; procellas, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ryslig, hemsk, förfärlig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (dæmonisk):</text:span> h. fremitus armorum; formidines; irati animi h-esque impetus; h-es miserique casus; bellum; reipublicæ pestis h.; h-e dictu; hoc τέρας (Cæsar) h-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dæmonisk)</text:span> vigilantiā, celeritate, diligentiā, est, C.; fera; visus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrĭdus</text:span>, -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ruggig, borstig, sträf, lurfwig; besatt med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt: <text:line-break/>1. eg.:</text:span> jecur; barba, C.; sus; glacie riget h-a barba; myrtus h-a hastilibus; silva dumis et ilice nigra, Vg.; mare h-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(upprördt),</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sträf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till smaken; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wild</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bister, barsk, hård, grym</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (att se l. röna), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">gräslig:</text:span></text:span> sapor, Pn.; h-us in jaculis et pelle Libystidis ursæ; h-a bella; jussa Jovis h-a; bruma, Vg.; hiems; arma, Ov.; h-a tempestas, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wild, sträf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">owårdad, hård, grof, ruskig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. om formen af framställning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">grof, sträf, rå, oprydlig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mots.</text:span> lēvis, politus): ager <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> cultus); vita h-a et arida, C.; gens, Vg.; verba paulo h-ora; oratio aspera, tristis, h-a; scripta h-a et inculta neque perfecta neque conclusa; in antiquis tabulis ipso illo h-o obsoletoque delectamur, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sträft, oprydligt; hårdt:</text:span></text:span> dicere; vivere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrĭdŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Något styf, hård; ruskig, grof, oprydlig, owårdad:</text:span></text:span> papillæ; comes, Ps.; oratio; scripta h-a et incompta, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrhorrĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: stagna situ p-a = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Aldeles wilda, obanade:</text:span></text:span> L. XXII. 16.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭbhorrĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Något ruskig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">osnygg:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bringar rysning (af köld l. fasa):</text:span> aquilo; prodigia, poēt. ap. C.; auræ aquilonis, C.; ægis, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ryslig, fasawäckande, hemsk:</text:span></text:span> bellum, C.; lapsus Harpyiarum, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrĭfĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrĭfĭco</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppröra:</text:span></text:span> mare, Catl.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fylla med fasa, förskräcka:</text:span></text:span> vatum prædicta Dido h-ant, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrĭpĭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wara besatt med hår:</text:span> aures, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horrĭsŏnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förfärligt dånande:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horror</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Upprättstående; styfhet:</text:span></text:span> comarum, Vfl.; ferri, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skälfwa, rysning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af sjukdom, köld, förskräckelse); i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">fasa, bäfwan:</text:span></text:span> Attica (ægra) sine h-e est; me perfudit h., C.; mihi frigidus h. membra quatit; comæ h-e arrectæ, Vg.; eos perstringit h.; h-e perfusus (aspectu Romuli), L.; Scipiadæ, Carthaginis h., Lucr.; Acron, Roma, tuis moenibus h. erat, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ăbhorreo</text:span>, ui, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rysa ifrån):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sky; wara obenägen för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wara främmande för</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">ab aliquo</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T3">a re</text:span>): ei animus a nuptiis, Ter.; a nuptiis; ab uxore ducenda; animus a scribendo, a pugnando; deorum aures et animus a nobis; voluntas ejus a me; omnes eum aspernabantur atque a-bant; homo a juris studio non a-ens, C.; is a consiliis illius, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efterclassiskt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Afsky</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">aliquid</text:span>): Augustus pumilos atque distortos a-bat, Su.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Afwika, skilja sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ifrån -; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">strida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ej öfwerensstämma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ej passa för; ej rimma sig med, wara otjenlig</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">a re</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T3">rei</text:span>): a-re a veritate longe; ab opinione alicujus; a vulgari orationis genere et consuetudine communis sensus; ratio tua a consiliis nostris; oratio a causa, a sensibus nostris, ab auribus vulgi a-bat; nostra ætas a castris; sin plane a-bit (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">otjenlig till talare) -;</text:span> nos fugiamus ab omni, quod ab approbatione oculorum a-eat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ej kan tillwinna sig);</text:span> a-et a suspicione (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">träffas ej af);</text:span> id facinus ab eo viro (ɔ: non cadit in), C.; orationes inter se; huic tam pacatæ profectioni a-ens mos bona Porsennæ vendendi; id a fide a-et, L.; vitæ cultu a gente; cultus a privato; aqua a colore maris, Ct.; res vero a-et, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhorresco</text:span>, rui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Få rysningar; rysa till, blifwa förskräckt:</text:span></text:span> ex quo sudore quum c-isset, cum febri domum rediit; quem ut agnovi, c-ui, C.; c-it corpus meum, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhorreo</text:span>, 2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhorresco</text:span>, rui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rysa upp, till; fasa för; blifwa hänförd:</text:span></text:span> siccos æstus e-ēre, Col.; - metu; in oratore, C.; vultūs alcjs, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhorreo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stå (upp); stå styf:</text:span></text:span> rictum, Lucr.; acies i-et velut vallo sæpta, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhorresco</text:span>, rui, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Resa sig, häfwas, uppröras</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om hafwet):</text:span> i-it mare, poēt. ap. C.; i-uit unda tenebris; spicea messis campis i-uit, Vg.; pili mihi, Petr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skälfwa, rysa till, rysa; betagas af fasa, fruktan:</text:span></text:span> vepris ventis i-uit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(praßlat),</text:span> Hor.; aper i-it armos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skakas i = ruskar),</text:span> Vg.; domus principis; temptat clausa, i-it vacuis, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ŏbhorreo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wara besatt med:</text:span> punctis sanguineis, Pn. (l. d.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrhorresco</text:span>, rui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Häftigt rysa, fasa wid, för:</text:span></text:span> toto corpore; in periculo alicujus; recordatione consulatus vestri; dissolutionem naturæ; memoriam diei; fugam, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Horreolum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Horreum<text:line-break/>Horresco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Horreo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Horreum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förrådshus, lada, bod, magasin, källare:</text:span></text:span> privata (frumenti), C.; condere (frumentum) proprio h-o, Hor.; h-a ponere, <text:soft-page-break/>L.; (vini), Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horreŏlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Horri . . ., Horror <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Horreo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Horsum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Horsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: (= huc (hui, hoi) vorsum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liks.</text:span> rursum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> v.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hitåt, hit, härtill;</text:span></text:span> h. pergunt; h. adigent te somnia, Ter.; insidias dabo, quam mox h. ad stabulum junix recipiat se a pabulo, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>orta, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Etrurien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hortīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ortălus, i <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hortam . . ., Hortat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hortor. <text:line-break/>Hortensis, -tensius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hortus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ortensius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hortensius, <text:line-break/>Hortensiānus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hortinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Horta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hortor</text:span> <text:line-break/>(hŏrĭtor, Enn.), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af ett lika betydande</text:span> horior, 3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos</text:span> Enn. Ann. 409. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Vahl.; arch.</text:span> horto): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Drifwa på; uppmana, råda, intala mod</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">lust; styrka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt; absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">uppmuntra:</text:span></text:span> currentem h-ri, C.; te et moneo et h., Ter.; magnopere te h-or, ut legas, C.; is eos h-batur, ne - -, N.; alqm ad laudem, ad dicendum, de iisdem rebus, C.; in amicitiam jungendam, L.; in proelia, Vg.; quid ego hæc te h-or?; pacem h-ri non desino, C.; h. accipere, N.; socios h. amare focos, Vg.; h-atur Thymoetes, (equum Troj.) duci intra muros; h-antur socii, Cretam proavosque petamus, Vg. -; milites, Sa., N.; canes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hetsa),</text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppmuntringsmedel; uppmaning:</text:span></text:span> ingens ad omnia audenda, L.; feminæ cibos et h-a pugnantibus gestant, T.; uti h-e longo, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: id.: h-o esse alicui, Sa.; magna animi h-a, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppmaning, tillstyrkan:</text:span></text:span> non h-e, sed precibus fraternis tecum ago, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortātīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uppmanande:</text:span> genus dicendi, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Pådrifware, uppmanare, tillstyrkare:</text:span></text:span> assiduus; isto h-e, auctore, intercessore Sullam adierunt; ejus studii tibi erat h. et magister domi; cædis h.; h-es ad me restituendum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tillstyrkan, uppmaning:</text:span></text:span> vox hujus h-u confirmata, C.; N.; blandi, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhortor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppmana till -, lifwa för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">uppmuntra:</text:span></text:span> locus ipse ad bellum faciendum; alqm ad rempublicam defendendam; a-or, ut; milites, C.; in bellum, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhortāmen</text:span>, ĭnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhortātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppmaning, -muntran:</text:span></text:span> missa nostra a-e ad illorum disputationem veniamus, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ădhortātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Pådrifware, uppmuntrare:</text:span></text:span> operis; suus cuique animus, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhortor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppmana, uppfordra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> alla samfäldt till gemensam handling; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">uppmuntrande tilltala;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">uppmana, -muntra:</text:span></text:span> Cæsar milites c-tus proelium commisit, Cs.; quis c-ri ad virtutem ardentius, quis a vitiis acrius revocare possit?; ad pacem; ad studium laudis; vereor, ne id majorem vim ad deterrendum habuerit, quam ad c-dum, C.; c., ut, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhortātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppmaning -stal:</text:span></text:span> judicum ad alqd; c. suscipitur; commovet alqm; concitari c-e, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕhortor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Afråda:</text:span></text:span> me, ne darem, Ter.; res ipsa me aut d-bitur aut invitabit; d. ab aliqua re, C.; scribere, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhortor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppfordra, uppmuntra, hetsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt:</text:span> sese in arma, Vg.; milites ad ultionem, Pn.; cives in hostem; taurum in alqm, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhortātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: C.; Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exhortātīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. innehåller en uppmaning, uppfordrande:</text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hortualis, Hortul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hortus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hortus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Trädgård, hage</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för blommor, kökswäxter, fruktträd m. m.), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">blomstergård</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">köksträdgård:</text:span></text:span> non segetibus solum et pratis et vineis et arbustis res rusticæ lætæ sunt, sed etiam h-is et pomariis -; h-um agricolæ succidiam alteram appellant, C.; floribus halantes h-i, Vg.; cultissimus, Ov.; irriguus, Varr., Hor.; pomaria conserere, h-os rigare, T.; h-um morus et ficus frequens vestit; - subjacet h. alius pinguis et rusticus, Pn. ep. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton. = trädgårds-, kökswäxter,</text:span> Cato, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span> horti, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Park</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med boningshus), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">villa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">landtställe:</text:span></text:span> in h-os D. Bruti venerunt augures commentandi causa; emit (h-os) instructos; Epicuri h-i, C.; habere prædia h-osque, N.; in h-os Lucullianos (profugit Messalina); h-i Sallustiani; Cæsaris h-i ad Tiberim, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortensis</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortensius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till trädgård hörande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Trädgårds-:</text:span></text:span> Col., Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortensia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl. n.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Trädgårdswäxter:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortuālis</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortŭlānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Trädgårds-:</text:span></text:span> Ap., Apic.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortŭlānus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Trädgårdsmästare:</text:span></text:span> Ap., Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hortŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Liten hage, trädgård:</text:span></text:span> Juv.; casula in h-o, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Park;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">villa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">landtställe:</text:span></text:span> h-os emere voluit, quo invitare amicos et ubi se oblectare - posset <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om samma sak:</text:span> hac villa carere non possunt piscatores), C. - inde h-os suos irrigavit Epicurus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = sitt system, hwilkets anhängare samlades kring honom</text:span> in ejus h-is, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hospes,</text:span> ĭtis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gästwän</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. står till ngn i ständigt gästwänskapsförhållande):</text:span> <text:soft-page-break/>deverti ad h-em; h. et amicus meus M. Pacuvius; Blossius h. familiæ vestræ, C.; non h. ab h-e tutus, Ov.: veterem vetus h. amicum accepit, Hor.; Jupiter - h-bus nam te dare jura loquuntur, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för tillfället) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gäst:</text:span></text:span> h. h-i dextram porrexit; clarus homo, in cujus domum multi h-tes recipiendi sunt; caupo homo multorum h-um; Dejotarus Cæsarem eodem tempore et hostem et h-em vidit; h-em accipere; h-em domi habere, domum deducere, C.; vespertinus; quo me cunque rapit tempestas, deferor h., Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wärd:</text:span></text:span> vicimus perfidos h-tes (Romanos Sabini), L., succinctus cursitat h.; sedulus h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(krogwärd),</text:span> Hor.; h. Acestes (Aeneæ), Vg.; h. Aurora colit Io, St.; qui modo h. fuerat, monstrator hospitii et comes, T.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Främling, gäst:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> nos in nostra urbe peregrinantes errantesque tanquam h-tes, C.; curia (senatus) h. in externis tectis, Luc.; hoc, quodcunque vides, h., qua maxima Roma est, ante Phrygem Aenean collis et herba fuit, Ppt.; h., quod dico, paulum est: asta ac perlege, Inscr. sepulcr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">främling = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Obewandrad i, obekant med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bortkommen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngt:</text:span> adeone h. es hujus urbis?; h. in consuetudine civitatis, in moribus civium, in agendo, C.; mene h-em lites sequi!, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hospĭta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gäst, wärdinna; främling:</text:span></text:span> h-a alicujus, Ter., C.; ego sum hic h-a, C.; h-a (Latona) terris, (Delos) undis errabat, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hospĭta</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f. sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">neutr. pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(poet.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gästwänlig; främmande:</text:span></text:span> domus, Sil.; h-a terra, æquora, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhospĭta</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">nom. sing. f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">plur. n. A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ogästwänlig; obeboelig, wild; otjenlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för -:</text:span> tecta, Ov.; tesqua, Hor.; saxa, Vg.; terra Baccho, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hospĭtālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gästwänlig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gästwäns, gästwänskaps-, wärds, gästs:</text:span></text:span> tessera, Pt.; Juppiter h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. wakar öfwer gästwänskapens helgd);</text:span> domus; mensa, C.; deversorium; cubiculum, L.; coena, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gästfri, gästwänlig, frikostig:</text:span></text:span> homo h-simus; domus maxime h.; sedes h., C.; clementia, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hospĭtālĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gästfrihet:</text:span></text:span> recte a Theophrasto laudata est, C.<text:line-break/>b. = hospitium: Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hospĭtālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gästfritt:</text:span></text:span> invitari, L.; excipi, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhospĭtālis</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ogästwänlig, obeboelig:</text:span></text:span> feritas, Pn.; Caucasus, Hor.; litus, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhospĭtālĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ogästwänlighet:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hospĭtium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gästwänskap</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (enskild l. allmän):</text:span> vetus mihi est cum eo; uti, conjungi h-o; facere h. cum aliquo; renovare vetus h.; renuntiare alicui h., C.; pop. Romani h., Cs.; jus, jura h-i, N.; multa h-a habent, amicitias nullas, Sen.; jungimus h-o dextras, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gästande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (att gästa); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">herbergerande, öfwad gästfrihet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gästabud):</text:span> mittit Mercurium Juppiter, ut terræ pateant Trojanis h-o; h-o prohibemur arenæ; Junonia, Vg.; convictibus et h-is nulla gens effusius indulget, T.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gästhem, herberge,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (qvarter, logis):</text:span> ex vita discedo tanquam ex h-o, non tanquam ex domo; h. liberale; h-o invitare, accipere, C.; dividi in h-a, L.; pecus it in longa deserta sine ullis h-is; Thracia antiquum Trojæ h.; linquere pollutum h., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hospĭtor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gästa; wistas ss. främling:</text:span></text:span> animus in corpore, Sen.; arbor nescit h-ri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trifwas i annan jord),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hostia,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Offerdjur, slagtoffer:</text:span></text:span> placare deos cæsis h-is; ad sacrificium præbere h-as; immolare deo h-is majoribus lactentibus, C.; immolare h-as, N.; mactare h-am, Vg., Hor. - humanæ h-æ, C., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hostio</text:span>, 1. = placare: Serv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hostiātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">försedd med offerdjur:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hostio</text:span>, 4. = ferire: Fs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hosticus, Hostilis, -litas, -liter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hostis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ostīlius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hostīlius, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: curia, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hostimentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Hostus.<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> II. Hostio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hostia.<text:line-break/>III. Hostio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Hostus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hostis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sällan</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Främling, utländing:</text:span></text:span> h. apud majores nostros is dicebatur, quem nos peregrinum dicimus. Indicant XII tabulæ, ut ”status dies cum hoste”, C.; si status condictus cum h-e intercedit dies, Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Landsfiende, fiende:</text:span></text:span> h-em qui feriet, mihi erit Carthaginiensis, quisquis erit, Enn.; h. est, qui arma contra fert; is sæpius cum h-e conflixit, quam quisquam cum inimico concertavit; ne h-is quidem et potentis et bellum ultra inferentis interitum cum scelere approbavit; h. ferus, immanis, capitalis; in h-em impetum facere; h-es adoriri, aggredi, fundere, C.; h-es adsunt; Tarquiniensis, novus h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fiende = fiender),</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hostĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillhör främling, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Främlings-:</text:span></text:span> h-um hoc mihi domicilium est, domus Athenis, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillhör fiende, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fiende-:</text:span></text:span> ager, L.; manus, Pt.; ensis, Hor.; incursio, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hostĭcum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fiendeland:</text:span></text:span> errare in h-o, L.; rapi ex h-o, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hostīlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Främmande, utländsk:</text:span></text:span> Petr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillhör fiende, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fiende-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fiendens, -dernes); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">fiendtlig:</text:span></text:span> terra; expugnatio, C.; arma, Vg.; acies; exercitus, T.; h. animus in alqm; h-e odium; h-em in modum necari, C.; omnia sunt h-ia; h-ia audere, pati, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hostīlĭtas</text:span>, ātis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fiendtlighet:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hostīlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På fiendtligt wis, fiendtligt:</text:span></text:span> facere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ostius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hostorium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Hostus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Hostus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwad man får igen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utbyte, inkomst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af oliv):</text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hostio</text:span>, 4. = æquare: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Swara med lika mot lika:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hostīmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wedergällning:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hostorium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Strykträd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (det, hwarmed man jemnar ngt):</text:span> Prisc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕdhostio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gifwa i utbyte:</text:span></text:span> Acc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ostus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. förnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Huc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hui,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Interj.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Åh!, hå!:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hujusmŏdi (hujus modi) = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af detta mått (sätt), art = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sådan,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> se</text:span> Modus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Human . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Homo.<text:line-break/>Humatio, -mator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Humo, Humus.<text:line-break/>Humect . . ., Humefactus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Humeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hūmeo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(ūmeo), ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wara fuktig, wåt:</text:span></text:span> genæ lacrimis; aquā locus, Ov. - h-ens terra, Col.; oculus; noctis umbra, Ov.; cælum, Fl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fuktig, wåt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som håller l. rymmer fuktighet:</text:span> locus, Varr.; nubes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(regntung),</text:span> Ap.; corpus h-simum, Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmecto</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fukta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wattna), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wäta:</text:span></text:span> flumen flaventia culta; largo h-at flumine (lacrimarum) vultum, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fuktas:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmĕfactus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fuktad:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmesco</text:span>, ĕre, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fuktas, bli wåt:</text:span></text:span> oculi h-entes, Pn.; poculis h-re, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fuktig, wåt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (flytande, regn-, wattenrik):</text:span> ligna, C.; ager h-ior, Pn.; nubes; nox; mella; vina; h-ida solstitia atque hiemes optate serenas, Vg.; dies, Ov.; ventus h-simus, Vitr.; regio, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmĭdŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Något fuktig:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bringar fuktighet; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wåt:</text:span></text:span> C. poēt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fuktande:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmĭfĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fukta:</text:span></text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wätska, det wåta; fuktigt, flytande ämne:</text:span></text:span> h. ita mollis est, ut facile comprimi possit; frigoribus durescit h.; h. et calor, qui est fusus in corpore; sidera marinis terrenisque h-bus aluntur, C.; paludis; dulcis musti; tellus bibit h-em, Vg.; h. subit radices; est causa fertilitatis; hausto h-e gravis, Ct.; crassus, Ps. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wätska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">lifssaft, -kraft:</text:span></text:span> nondum exarui -: amoris aliquantum et h-is habeo in corpore, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hūmōrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Full af fuktighet:</text:span></text:span> locus, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hŭmĕrus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwer-arm; skuldra:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> exserit hæc h-um (ut parata sit ad ministrandum), Ov.; in h-os extollere alqd; sustinere bovem h-is; boum h-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bogar),</text:span> C.; demissis <text:soft-page-break/>h-is esse, Ter.; fortes; lati; os h-osque deo similis; illa pharetram fert h-o; hunc turba suspicit exstantem altis h-is, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttr.:</text:span> rempublicam sustinere h-is, C.; (vos, qui scribitis,) versate diu, quid ferre recusent, quid valeant h-i, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rygg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ett föremål:</text:span> jugorum; arborum, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŭmĕrāle</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">axeltäcke:</text:span> Ulp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Humesco, Humid . . ., Humif . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Humeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hŭmĭlis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: (-ilior, -illimus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> humus?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Låg:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Låg, lågwäxt, grund:</text:span></text:span> vitis, C.; turris, Cs.; myricæ: casa; fossa, Vg.; statura, N.; vir, Ct.; bos, Col.: radix; luna, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till samhällsställning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Låg, ringa:</text:span></text:span> natus parentibus h-bus; h-i loco, fortuna; omnes non improbi h-es, C.; h-ores principibus pares, Ct.; ex h-i potens, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Låg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">simpel, obetydlig:</text:span></text:span> ars; hæc sunt h-ora quam ea, quæ a vobis exspectari puto, C.; nos h-em feriemus agnam, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om stil och framställning i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Låg, simpel:</text:span></text:span> oratio abjecta et h.; sermo demissus et h., C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i moralisk men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Låg, simpel, usel, lågsint:</text:span></text:span> in rem h-em et contemptam (voluptatem) omnes cogitationes abjicere; nihil abjectum, nihil h-e cogitare; h. ortus amicitiæ; mens angusta et h., C.; mulier non h., Hor.<text:line-break/>e. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Klenmodig, nedslagen, feg, försagd; ödmjuk:</text:span></text:span> ut res sese dant, ita h-es et magni sumus, Ter.; animus h. et imbecillus; h. homo et infirmus, C.; pavor, Vg.; prece h-i et supplici uti, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŭmĭlitas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Låghet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> siderum, C.; navium, Cs.; arborum, Sa. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ringhet:</text:span></text:span> propter h-em in ignoratione hominum versari; h. contendit cum dignitate, C.; generis, Sa.; h-em objicere alicui, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">låghet = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uselhet, ynklighet, swaghet, förnedring</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i tänkesätt och beteende:</text:span> metus habet h-em; h. et obsecratio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(krypande böner),</text:span> C.; senatus, Pn. ep. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŭmĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lågt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. och oeg. men.:</text:span> deprimi, Pn.; h. et demisse sentire, C.; servire, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Humo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Humus.<text:line-break/>Humor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Humeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hŭmus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jord</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. ämne), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">mull:</text:span></text:span> h. subacta ac pura; humati dicuntur, quos h. injecta contegit, C.; corpus mandare h-o, Vg.; h-um ligonibus exhaurire, Hor.; ea, quæ h-o finguntur (= fictilia), T.; arenosa; limosa; pinguis; arens, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jorden</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = jordbrynet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">marken</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gruset, stoftet), isynnerhet i casus obl., i eg. och oeg. uttryck:</text:span> humi = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på marken, o. s. w.:</text:span> h-i jacere; h-i stratum esse, C.; h-i procumbit bos; fundere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kullslå)</text:span> alqm h-i; tentanda via est, qua me quoque possim tollere h-o, Vg.; repere per h-um; quatere h-um candido pede; deducit ad h-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trycker ned till)</text:span> gravi mærore; dum vitat h-um, nubes et inania captat; h-o affligi, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Land:</text:span></text:span> natalis; Punica, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŭmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">betäcka med jord:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> taleas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sättqwistar),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.: = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jorda, begrafwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lik):</text:span> corpora h-ri i. e. humo tegi, C.; socios, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŭmātio</text:span>, ōnis. <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Begrafning, jordande:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hŭmātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnhŭmātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ej jordad; obegrafwen:</text:span></text:span> Diogenes jussit se projici i-um, C.; cadat ante diem mediaque i-us arena, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆ăcinthus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hy̆ăcinthos), i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mars-blomma, hyacinth:</text:span></text:span> mollis, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personn.:</text:span> Ov. Met. 10. 162. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hy̆ăcinthĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hyacinth-:</text:span></text:span> flos, Catl. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hyacinthfärgad:</text:span> Ps. <text:line-break/>Hy̆ăcinthĭa, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fest hos Lacedæmonierne:</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆æna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hyäna:</text:span></text:span> Luc. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hy̆ænĭus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆ălus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Glas; glasgrön färg:</text:span></text:span> Vg., Aus.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hy̆ălĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: Fulg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆ampŏlis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Phocis.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆antes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gammal folkstam i Boeotien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hy̆antēus, <text:line-break/>Hy̆antĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆as, ădis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆ădes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sjustjernorna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eg. de regnbringande):</text:span> C., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆as, antis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hybern . . . = Hibern . . ., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hiems.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ȳbla, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg på Sicilien, berömdt för sin rikedom på blommor och bin.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hȳblæus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span><text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Sicilien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hȳblenses, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inw. der.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hybrida <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hibrida.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆daspes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">indisk flod.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hy̆daspēus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hydra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wattenorm,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> fabeldjur med 50 hufwud:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydrăgōgĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wattenledning:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydrargy̆rus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Qwicksilfwer:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydraula</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">s</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om spelar wattenorgel:</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydraulus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wattenorgel:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydraulĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydrĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wattenkruka, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ämbar:</text:span></text:span> argenteæ; grandes, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydrŏcēlē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wattenbråck:</text:span></text:span> Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydrŏchŏus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wattumannen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stjernbild):</text:span> Catl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydrŏmĕli</text:span>, ĭtis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mjöd:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydrops</text:span>, ōpis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wattensot:</text:span></text:span> dirus, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydrōpĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wattensigtig:</text:span></text:span> si noles sanus, curres h., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hydrus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wattenorm:</text:span> Ov., Luc., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ydrus, untis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Calabrien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hyems = Hiems.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆gēa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hy̆gīa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">helsans gudinna.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ȳlæus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en centaur.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆las, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr myth. personnamn:</text:span> Ppt. I. 20.; frustra quæsitus H. urnamque secutus, Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>yllus. i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ȳmēn, ĕnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bröllopets, äktenskapets gud:</text:span> H. o Hymenæe, Hymen ades o Hymenæe, Catl. LXII. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: = bröllopssång, bröllop:</text:span> Ov., Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hy̆mĕnæus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. = Hymen: Catl. LXII., Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bröllopssång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (anropande af H.):</text:span> Ov.; aures pepulit h-us meas, Sen. Med.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bröllop; äktenskap</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span>): hic h. erit; Pergama petiit Helena inconcessosque h-os, Vg.; Ov.; mactata soceri concidit thalamis gener victima, tuis ne fieret h-is potens, Sen. Oct. 145.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆mettus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Attica.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hy̆mettĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: marmor; mel, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hymnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lofsång, hymn:</text:span></text:span> Lucil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆oscy̆ămus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bolmört:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆pæpa, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Lydien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hy̆pæpēni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inw. i H.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pæthrus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är under öppen himmel, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öppen:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pallăge,</text:span> es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gramm. utbyte, wexling:</text:span> h. est, quum quasi summutantur verba: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆pănis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Sarmatien (Bug).</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"><text:line-break/>H</text:span>y̆păsis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">indisk flod.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"><text:line-break/>H</text:span>y̆păta, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Thessalien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hy̆pătæus, <text:line-break/>Hy̆pătensis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pēnĕmĭus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: ovum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">windägg:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆perbăton,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omställning af ord, förändring af deras naturliga ordningsföljd:</text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆perbŏlē,</text:span> es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerdrift</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i uttryck:</text:span> C., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆perbŏlus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆perbŏrĕus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(belägen l. boende ofwan nordanwinden), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nordlig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> nordbo:</text:span> Vg., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆percătălectus,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hy̆percătălectĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: versus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har en stafwelse l. fot utöfwer måttet,</text:span> Gramm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆pĕrīdes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆pĕrīon, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">solguden, solen:</text:span> C., Ov. <text:line-break/>Hy̆pĕrīŏnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dotter af H.</text:span> (Aurora): Ov. <text:line-break/>Hy̆pĕrīŏnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆permnestra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en af Danaiderna.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pherthy̆rum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfre dörrträd:</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Hyphasis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hypasis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆phen,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">ind. n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">twå ords uttal ss. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ett:</text:span></text:span> Gramm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pŏcausis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eldning under ett rum:</text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hy̆pŏcaustum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rum, s. uppeldas genom apparat under golfwet:</text:span> Pn. ep., Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pŏcŏrisma,</text:span> ătis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smekord) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Deminutivum:</text:span></text:span> Gramm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pŏcrĭsis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">föreställande af en person:</text:span> Gramm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hy̆pŏcrĭtes</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hy̆pŏcrĭta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skådespelare:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pŏdĭdascălus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Underlärare:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pŏgēum</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Hy̆pŏgæum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Källare; grafrum:</text:span></text:span> Vitr., Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hypomnēma,</text:span> ătis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förklaring, not:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pŏmochlĭon,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">underlag under </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">häfstång:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pŏtēnūsa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sida, s. står emot den räte winkeln, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hypotenusa:</text:span></text:span> Hyg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pŏthēca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hypothek, pant:</text:span></text:span> C., Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hy̆pŏtrăchēlĭum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stycke af en colonn (under capitelet):</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ypsĭcrătes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ypsĭpy̆lē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn. </text:span><text:s/><text:line-break/>Hypsĭpy̆læus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>yrcānus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Hyrcāni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Hyrcānĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Hyrcānĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk och land wid Caspiska hafwet.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆rĭē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad och sjö i Boeotien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>y̆rieus, ĕi, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnam.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hy̆rĭēus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>yrtăcĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">son af</text:span> Hyrtacus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hyssōpus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hyssōpum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Isop:</text:span></text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hyssōpītes</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Isopwin:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">H</text:span>ystaspes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">persiskt personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hystĕrĭcus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hysterisk:</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hystrix,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Piggswin:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>acchus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på Bacchus. - meton. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Win:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jăceo,</text:span> ui, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ligga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: om personer och saker:</text:span> j. humi; ad pedes alicujus stratum; in lecto, C.; j-et ingens litore truncus; sub arbore j., Vg.; ante pedes, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ligga sjuk, slagen, död:</text:span></text:span> cura, ut valeas, ne te j-ente bona tua comedim, C.; graviter, Pn. ep.; veste spoliare j-entem, N.: is j-et inultus, L.; Hector j-et telo Aeacidæ, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om orter: = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wara belägen; sträcka, utbreda sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (isynn. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">part.</text:span>): pars Asiæ inter hunc et illum locum; gens super Ciliciam, N.; j-et insula ponto; planities ignota j-et, Vg.; mare j-et, Luc.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = befinna sig i tillstånd af underlägsenhet, betryck, obemärkthet:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">relat. l. med bestämning för tillståndet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ligga, ligga försänkt, begrafwen:</text:span></text:span> in eodem silentio multa alia oratorum officia j-uerunt; in oblivione j.; in gravi mærore; in lacrimis et sordibus, C.; res in occulto, Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol. (om personer och saker) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ligga under, ligga slagen; wara modlös, tillintetgjord; wara fallen, sjunken, kraftlös; ligga nere</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= ej kunna komma sig upp, ej idkas l. aktas):</text:span> cum id, quod utile videtur, cum eo, quod honestum est, comparatur, j-eat utilitatis species, valeat honestas; dominetur in contionibus, j-at in judiciis invidia; j-et justitia vel vacillat potius; Pompejus totus j-et; ita doleo, ut non j-am; j-et omnis ratio Peripateticorum, C.; pauper ubique j-et, Ov.; j-ent pretia prædiorum; ista j-nt propter numorum caritatem; hic omnia j-nt; pecunia j-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ligger ofruktbar);</text:span> j-ent ea (studia), quæ apud quosque improbantur; Marius septimum annum post præturam j-bat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hade ej wunnit befordran);</text:span> maluit in pace j-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lefwa obemärkt),</text:span> quam in bello vigere; philosophia j-uit usque ad hanc ætatem - - quæ excitanda nobis est, C.; animi militum, L.; oratio, Qu. - <text:span text:style-name="T3">part.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jăcens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om orter) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Belägen nedanför ngn; lågt belägen; lågländt:</text:span></text:span> Juppiter despiciens mare velivolum terrasque j-es; Thapsus, Vg.; despicit Phaĕthon terras penitus penitusque j-es, Ov.; loca, T., Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">s. ligger</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hänger lös:</text:span></text:span> ut sensere equi lora j-ia tergis; crines collo, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sänkt, fallen; sjunken</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i eg. o. oeg. men.):</text:span> oculi, Ov.; animus amici, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Adjăceo</text:span>, ui, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ligga, wara belägen inwid, gränsa intill</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">dat.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">acc.</text:span>): Romani passim a-bant vallo, T.; gentes illæ a-ent mare, N.; ager Tuscus Romano; fines Romani Etruriam, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Adjăcens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Angränsande, grann-;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl. n.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omgifningar:</text:span> T., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Circumjăceo</text:span>, ui, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ligga omkring, omgifwa:</text:span></text:span> populi c-entes, T.; regiones Europæ, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interjăceo</text:span>, ui, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ligga, wara belägen emellan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">acc.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">dat.</text:span>): planities Capuam Tifataque i-et; itineris finem sperent campum i-entem Tiberi ac moenibus Romanis, L.; regio duas Syrtes, Pn.; spatium sulcis i-et, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Objăceo</text:span>, ui, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ligga för, midtför, i wägen för:</text:span></text:span> saxa o-entia pedibus, L.; insula o-et, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præjăceo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ligga framför:</text:span></text:span> campus castra, T.; mare Asiæ, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subjăceo</text:span>, ui, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ligga, bo under, nedanför:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> fenestris s-et vestibulum villæ et hortus; Tusci Apennino, saluberrimo montium, s-ent, Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Höra under, inunder, till; wara underkastad:</text:span></text:span> causæ lites; utilitati defensio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hänföres till),</text:span> Qu.; vita multis casibus, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭperjăceo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ligga öfwer, på:</text:span></text:span> cataplasma, Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">J</text:span>acetāni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i Hispanien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jăcio,</text:span> jēci, jactum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, slunga (strö):</text:span></text:span> lapides; saxa; fulmen Jupiter in medium mare; scyphum de manu in alqm; se in profundum; talos, venerem j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det bästa kastet i tärningsspel),</text:span> C.; tela ex vallo; faces de muro in aggerem, Cs.; ancora de prora j-itur; flores; semen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(strö),</text:span> Vg.; alqd in sublime, Pn.; odorem de corpore <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sprida),</text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: om grundwal, fästningswerk, hamnbyggnader o. s. w.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lägga, uppkasta, bygga, uppföra:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> fundamenta; ab utroque portus cornu moles jecimus, C.; aggerem, Cs., L.; muros, Vg.; hic urbi fundamenta jeci, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildliga uttryck:</text:span> f-a pacis et salutis j.; quasi gradum quendam atque aditum ad cetera (i. e. reliquam orationem) j-tum intelligitis, C.; omnis regio j-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(grundar, bygger)</text:span> salutem in hac arte, Vg. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framkasta, slunga, fälla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> infall, beskyllning mot ngn, ett yttrande, ett förslag; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">antyda, låta förstå:</text:span></text:span> crimen, contumeliam, suspicionem in alqm; adulteria; querelas; j. ridiculum; per ambages j. alqd; obscure alqd, C.; minas alicui; sermones, L.; Hiempsal inter alia j-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framkastar det förslaget),</text:span> regis acta rescindi oportere, Sa.; unde petitum hoc in me j-is?, Hor; quædam de habitu cultuque Tiberii j-rat Augustus, quæ velut exprobrando excusaret, T.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inkasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i en ställning, i förhållanden:</text:span> casus caput meum in mediam contentionem civilem, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jacto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, slunga (ideligen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">häftigt); swänga, slänga hit och dit, wräka:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om lefwande subject:</text:span> diu j-ato brachio scutum manu emittere præoptabant, Cs.; cæstus j-re; hastas; talos; cerviculam; faces in tecta, C.; brachia alterna; bidentes (agricolæ); crura alta (equus), Vg.; se e muro, Ct.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om döda subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, sprida;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om hafwet) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wräka, kringkasta;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> deraf i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wräkas, kastas, kasta sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hit och dit:</text:span> lucem de corpore; suave mari magno j-antibus æquora ventis e terra magnam alterius spectare ruinam, Lucr.; nec, si te validus j-verit auster in alto, idcirco navem vendas; navem j-antibus austris, Hor.; in turba, adversa tempestate in alto j-ri; j-ri æstu febrique, C.; maritimis fluctibus j-ari, N.; terrā j-atus et alto, Vg.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framkasta, yttra; föreslå; omtala, omorda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (discutera):</text:span> minas; voces; res in contionibus, in senatu j-ta est, C.; jocosa dicta; probra in alqm; j-tum est in condiciones (pacis), ut - - L.; pluribus præsentibus eam rem j-ri noluit, Cs.; j-amus te omnes jam pridem Roma beatum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omtala dig ss.),</text:span> Hor.; ausus quin etiam voces j-re per umbram; talia j-anti stridens aquilone procella velum adversa ferit, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framhålla, skryta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt;</text:span> j. se = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hålla, tränga sig fram, göra sig bemärkt; pråla, slå sig ut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lefwa stort); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">göra sig stor, wigtig, hofwera</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> j-as et genus et nomen inutile; se ultorem j-at, Hor.; virtutem, Ov.; ingenium, Qu.; miseros illudi nolunt, nisi se forte j-ant; sancit, ne quis hujus supplicio levando se j-re et in perniciem reip. popularis esse possit; in bonis Roscii se j.; se magnifice, intolerantius in aliqua re; se in causis centumviralibus; in hoc vestra oratio se j. potest, C.; illā se j-et in aula Aeolus; vulnere Aeneæ se j., Vg.<text:line-break/>3. (<text:span text:style-name="T3">syn.</text:span> versare) = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerwäga, behandla;</text:span></text:span> se j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> jactari = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ifrigt sysselsätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig med, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">öfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig i ngt:</text:span> tales pectore curas, Vg.; (formulæ jureconsultorum) - pervulgatæ atque in manibus j-tæ; in republica tu non valde te j-as; in opere declamatorio j-tus (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slängd),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>4. se j-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> j-ri = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kastas, wagga, wackla hit och dit; wara ombytlig, owiß:</text:span></text:span> opiniones se j-ant: j-batur numus sic, ut nemo posset scire, quid haberet, C.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Oroa, anfäkta, anfalla:</text:span></text:span> multis injuriis; clamore et conviciis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jactans</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skrytsam, storordig, fåfäng:</text:span></text:span> sui; gestus, Qu.; epistola, Pn.; j-ior hic est - postulat, ut concinnus amicis videatur, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jactābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som häfwes, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Orolig:</text:span></text:span> mare Gell.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som skryter med l. förhäfwer sig öfwer ngt:</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jactanter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skrytsamt; tillgjordt, med affectation:</text:span></text:span> epistolam composuit j-ius; mærere alqm, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jactantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skrytsamhet, skryt:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jactātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kastande, slängning, skakning:</text:span></text:span> modica corporis; magna (maris, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">krängning),</text:span> C.; ubi (vulnera) j-em (vehiculi) ferre poterant -, L.; cervicum; vulnerum, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skryt, flärd;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bemödande l. förmåga att hålla sig fram, behaga; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">lismeri:</text:span></text:span> populari j-e se tueri; eloquentia habuit j-em in populo (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uppträdde med flärd och ståt);</text:span> ferre hominum insolentiam et j-em, C.; eruditionis, Qu.; virtutis et operæ, Ct.; cultūs nulla j., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jactātor</text:span>, ōris <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. skryter, prålar, koketterar med ngt:</text:span> Qu., Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jactātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Swängning, skakning:</text:span></text:span> pennarum, Ov.; maris, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jactĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Pläga kasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">slunga:</text:span></text:span> juventus inter se ridicula, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jactūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utkastning:</text:span></text:span> si in mari j. facienda sit, equine pretiosi potius j-am faciat (sapiens), an servuli vilis?, C.; fit de oneribus navis, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppoffring, uppoffrande;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt af penningar, medel: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">utgift, omkostnad;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">förlust:</text:span></text:span> gloriæ, juris, rei familiaris j-am facere; Mælius annona levanda j-isque rei familiaris in suspicionem regni appetendi incidit; immanes j-æ infinitique sumptus fiunt ad multitudinem deleniendam, C.; parva j-a accepta Vejentem, hostem sexies victum, pertimescitis, L.; facilis j. sepulcri, Vg.; generis humani; decoris, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jactus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kast,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skott, slungande, störtande):</text:span> fulminum, C.; teli, Ct.; sagittæ; pulveris; teli; j-u se dedit in æquor, Vg.; talorum, Ov.; tesserarum, L.; j-um emere a piscatoribus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ett notwarp);</text:span> j. vocis, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jăcŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. kastas l. kastar sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kast-:</text:span></text:span> rete, Pt.; anguis, Luc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jăcŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kastspjut:</text:span></text:span> j-o trajicere alqd; solem non videre præ multitudine sagittarum et j-orum, C.; ferrea seges j-is increvit acutis, Vg.; j-a ingerere, mittere, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kastnät, not:</text:span></text:span> pisces capiuntur j-o, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jăcŭlor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, slunga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. kastspjut:</text:span> laudem consequebare j-ando, equitando, omni militari labore tolerando, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ipsa Jovis rapidum j-ta e nubibus ignem (Pallas), Vg.; silicem in alqm; fulmina, Ov.; se in confertissima hostium tela, Fl.; j. lucem, umbram, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> probris j-ri in alqm, L.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta efter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">beskjuta, träffa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> cervos; Jupiter rubenti dextera jaculatus arces, Hor.; igne lucos, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sigta efter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (trå efter):</text:span> quid brevi fortes j-amur ævo multa?, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jăcŭlābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är till att slunga l. kasta: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kast-, slung-:</text:span></text:span> telum, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jăcŭlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Spjutkastning; slungande, kastande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. och oeg. men.:</text:span> equestris, Pn.; saxi, Ap.; verborum, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jăcŭlātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. slungar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lansförare, spjutslungare:</text:span></text:span> L., Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jăcŭlātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: Diana, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ējăcŭlor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Ējăcŭllo, Gell.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, skjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (spruta) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ut, upp:</text:span></text:span> arcus cælestis species et colores in parietes, Pn.; fistula aquas; sanguis se in altum, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Abjĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta bort:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta ifrån sig; kasta bort, ned;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ofta med bibet.: likgiltigt, handlöst bortkasta; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wräka, slunga bort:</text:span></text:span> scutum; insigne regium de suo capite; anulum in mare; arma a., non deponere; cadaver Clodii in publicum; natura ceteras animantes ad pastum a-ecit (= pronas finxit), solum hominem erexit, C.; arma, Cs.; <text:span text:style-name="T3">refl.</text:span>: a. se in mare, e muro; se in herba; se ad pedes alicui, ad alicujus pedes; se supplicem pro aliquo; a-tus ad pedes alicujus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: bortkasta = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppgifwa; låta fara, falla; förlora:</text:span></text:span> spem; voluntatem discendi; memoriam doloris; consilium; curam; amorem; a-ta omni cunctatione rempublicam capessere; vitam, C.; a-tis nugis sapere utile est, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med wårdslöshet </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, wräka bort, spilla bort;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. = sälja för underpris:</text:span> omnes cogitationes in rem humilem et contemptam; se ipsum; versum a-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(negligerar, framsäger utan eftertryck; mots.</text:span> agere eo gestu, quo potest); ambitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(period)</text:span> ponendus est, non a-dus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(man bör lägga, ej handlöst släppa den ned),</text:span> C.; ædes, Pt.; agros, Phdr.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedslå; nedsätta, förringa:</text:span></text:span> viribus adversarii a-ci; intercessorem magna contentione; senatus auctoritatem; res augere et a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i rhetorisk men.),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Abjectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Låg, föraktlig, simpel:</text:span></text:span> homo a. et contemptus; causa; senarii; verba; oratio, C.; negotium, Val.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Klenmodig, försagd, alltför ödmjuk, krypande:</text:span></text:span> sæpe in quibusdam animus a-ior est et spes amplificandæ fortunæ fractior; privatum oportet - neque summissum et a-um vivere, neque se efferentem, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedslagen, förkrossad:</text:span></text:span> excitare senatum a-um; recitatis literis debilitatus et a.; a-a metu filia, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Abjecte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Klenmodigt, omanligt:</text:span></text:span> ferre casum; facere alqd a. et timide, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Abjectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: animi, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">modlöshet, förtwiflan,</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Adjĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta (lägga, wända) till:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta till, i; lägga i; foga till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> voces a-tæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som nått, träffat)</text:span> auribus, C.; telum potest a-i ex iis locis in litus, Cs.; vulnera corpori <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genom kast tillfoga),</text:span> T.; album calculum errori (ɔ: assentiri), Pn.; sal in alqd, sorba in urceolos, Col.; aggerem ad munitiones; aggeri loricam, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, rigta, wända</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ögon l. sinne till ngt):</text:span> animum ad virginem, Ter.; ad bona alicujus oculos cupiditatis; oculum hereditati, C.; animum ad consilium, consilio, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ingifwa, skänka, gifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt:</text:span> alicui vires, L.; animos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mod)</text:span> alicui, Ov.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tillägga</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öka med ngt); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ytterligare gifwa, ingifwa; tillfoga:</text:span></text:span> ad (belli laudem) doctrinæ et ingenii gloriam a-ecit, C.; muneri <text:soft-page-break/>aliquantum agri; fessis terrorem, L.; a-ēre bonæ paulo plus artis Athenæ; Britannos imperio; quis scit, an a-ant hodiernæ tempora summæ crastina di superi?, Hor.; a-ecit Tiberius, non id tempus censuræ esse, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Adjectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tilläggning, tillökning, tillfogande:</text:span></text:span> Romana res a-e populi Albani aucta; illiberalis a. (pretii = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stegring, öfwerbud),</text:span> L.; caloris, Sen.; verborum, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Adjectīvum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gramm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tilläggsord, adjectiv:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Adjectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: res a-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genom</text:span> a<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tt komma till)</text:span> tangit nares, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏadjĭcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lägga med till:</text:span> sal in urnas, Col. (d. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭpĕradjĭcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ytterligare tillfoga:</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Circumjĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> uppkasta, uppföra, ställa, lägga </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">omkring:</text:span></text:span> hastas in hostem; vallum, L.; ædificia muris c-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(belägna omkring),</text:span> L.; multitudo moenibus c-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. stod omkring),</text:span> Cs.; campi c-ti, Ct.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Omgifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> alqd aliqua re, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Circumjectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kastande omkring; omslutning, omkrets:</text:span></text:span> (vestis, quæ est) c-ui, Varr.; Oceanus terram tenero c-u amplectitur, C.; parietum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conjĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta tillsammans, i hop; kasta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sinl. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta i hop:</text:span></text:span> sortes in hydriam, C.; sarcinas in medium, in unum locum; tela undique in hostem, L.; igni spolia, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, slunga, rigta:</text:span></text:span> in plaustrum alqm; telum, C.; tela, pila, lapides in hostes; tela intra vallum, Cs.; telum imbelle, Vg.; petitiones, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kasta = med hast l. wåld bringa någorstädes hän, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Drifwa;</text:span></text:span> se c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">störta, skyndsamt begifwa sig; undansticka sig:</text:span></text:span> alqm in vincula, in carcerem, in custodiam, in equuleum, C., Cs.; in catenas, Cs.; in fugam, C., Cs.; in portum navem, C.; in angustias alqm, Ct.; domum alqm, C.; se in pedes, Ter.; se in fugam, in ultimam provinciam, in latebras, in noctem, in scalas tabernæ, C.; in templum se, N. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(combinera) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Draga slutsats, gissa; tyda:</text:span></text:span> bene, belle, male; Brutus de matre suavianda acute arguteque; c., e morbo evasurum ægrotum; de se, C.; de futuris callidissime, N.; somnium alicui, P<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">t.;</text:span> ea non sunt tam mirabilia, quam c-ta belle; male c-ta et interpretata, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Afhandla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (discutera), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">behandla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en sak:</text:span> causam, XII. Tab., C.; de re, Afr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> confero).<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, bringa, drifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn i, till en ställning:</text:span> rem publicam in perturbationes; alqm in apertum latrocinium, C.; in malum; in lætitiam, Ter.; alqm in metum, L.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inkasta, införa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i en skrift:</text:span> prooemium in librum; verba in interdictum, C. <text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta ut, anwända</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på -:</text:span> tantam pecuniam in præclara illa propylæa, C.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tal </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framkasta, rigta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">anwända</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">kasta, skjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> skuld på ngn:</text:span> vocem in disputando; maledicta in vitam alicujus; vanam <text:soft-page-break/>orationem in clarissimos viros; omen in alqm, C.; crimen, causam, in alqm, C., L.; culpam in alqm, C.<text:line-break/>g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rigta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ögon, sinne, sig på ngt:</text:span> oculos in alqm, C.; quum se c-rat in versum, verba sequebantur; C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conjectānea</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Blandad samling:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conjectārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. beror på förmodan l. gißning:</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conjectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kastande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ett</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> föremål):</text:span> telorum, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jemförelse:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uttydning:</text:span></text:span> somniorum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conjecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ihop), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">sammanskjuta:</text:span></text:span> in carcerem hostium duces; ad coenulam alqd, Gell.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sluta, gissa sig till:</text:span></text:span> nescio, quid c-em, Ter.; iter; alqd eventu, L.; offensionem vultu alicujus; alqd ex re, de <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om)</text:span> aliqua re; c-bat, Fabium profectum esse ab urbe, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conjectātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sannolik slutsats l. beräkning:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conjector</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conjectrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Drömtydare, -erska:</text:span></text:span> Pt., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conjectūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sannolik) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Slutsats, gißning, förmodan; uttydning, drömtydning:</text:span></text:span> c-ā nihil incertius; bona, vera, C.; c. me ducit aliquo<text:span text:style-name="T3">;</text:span> c-ā duci ad credendum, ut credat; c-ā quærere, assequi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(leda sig till -);</text:span> c-ā consequi, augurari, prospicere, providere alqd; c-ā aberrare; c-am capere, trahere, facere ex <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> de aliqua re, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. i rhet.: slutsats angående en beskyllnings sannolikhet:</text:span> omnis c. ex causa, ex persona, ex facto ipso capietur, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conjectūrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som beror på sannolikhetsbeslut:</text:span> causa, genus causæ, constitutio, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">der frågan gäller ett factum,</text:span> ubi quæritur, factumne sit, non quale sit, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conjectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kastande i massa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ett</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ställe l. mål; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">kastande, kast</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm., i eg. och oeg. bet.:</text:span> lapidum c-u fracta domus, C.; c-u terræ explere alqd, L.; telorum c-u confodi, N.; ad teli c-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inom skotthåll)</text:span> venire, L.; oculorum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kast = uppkastad hög:</text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Slutsats, gißning:</text:span></text:span> Aur. Vict.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dējĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedkasta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedkasta, nedslå, -störta, kullslå, fälla:</text:span></text:span> de ponte alqm; præcipitem in forum; propugnaculum, C.; equo d-i; in locum inferiorem d-i; antennas d.; naves ad inferiorem partem insulæ d-untur (ab alto; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> deduco, defero), Cs.; se e superiore parte ædium; se in mare, N.; moenia, Ov.; castella, Hor.; feras, Ct.; securim in caput alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låta falla),</text:span> L.; - alvum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(purgera),</text:span> Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rubba, stöta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ifrån hans ställning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bringa att wika; fördrifwa, förjaga:</text:span></text:span> de gradu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ur fotfästet)</text:span> alqm, C.; loco hostes, præsidium equitum, C.; præsidio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> alqm de præsidio, Cs.; præsidium regale loco, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personliga obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stöta ned, undan, bort</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">(beröfwa)</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en ställning; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">rubba</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från en mening:</text:span> senatum a gubernaculis; de honore, prætura, ædilitate d. alqm (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">göra, att han ej winner -);</text:span> de possessione alqm; de sententia, C.; Helvetii hac spe d-ti (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gäckade i);</text:span> d-i principatu, Cs.; quis te casus d-tam conjuge tanto excipit?, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sakliga obj.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedslå, fälla:</text:span></text:span> oculos, C.; Dido vultum d-a profatur, Vg.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nedkasta = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Borttaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en tyngd:</text:span> vide, quantum mali de humana condicione d-eris, quantum de doloris terrore d-ris; jugum servile de cervicibus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dējectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Låg:</text:span></text:span> loca, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förkrossad, modlös:</text:span></text:span> quamvis vis (vulneris) tardat, haud d. equum duci jubet, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dējectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedstötande; fördrifwande; nedslagenhet:</text:span></text:span> alvi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(purgering),</text:span> Sen.; facere, C.; animi, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dējecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedstörta:</text:span></text:span> Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dējectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedkastande, fällande; sluttning:</text:span></text:span> arborum, L.; collis habet d-um, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indējectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ej störtad:</text:span></text:span> domus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Disjĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta åtskils, hit och dit:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. (skingra, försprida, upplösa, kringströ, splittra):</text:span> res vage d-tæ; saxa d-ta, C.; age diversos et d-ce corpora ponto; moles d-tæ avulsaque saxis saxa; classem, Vg.; nubes; comæ d-tæ; vulnere d-ci, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om härmassor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Spränga, upprifwa:</text:span></text:span> manum, C.; phalangem; nostros, Cs.; copias, N.; catervam, T.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förstöra:</text:span></text:span> antennas, Cs.; munitiones; arcem; domum a fundamentis, N.; veterem aram, T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med abstracta obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Upplösa, göra om intet:</text:span></text:span> globum consensionis, N.; rem; pacem; consilia, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Disjecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta hit och dit, förströ, spränga:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Disjectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förströende, kringkastande:</text:span></text:span> materiai, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ējĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utkasta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utkasta, -sträcka, utdrifwa, utstöta;</text:span></text:span> se c.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">störta ut, bort:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> domo, Pt.; foras, Ter.; Gallus e-tā linguā, buccis fluentibus; stirpes e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utrota);</text:span> alqm in exsilium, e senatu, de collegio; se e navi in terram, ex oppido, C.; alqm urbe; ex republica, N.; partu e-o, Pn.; se ex castris, in agros, Cs.; se foras, L.; armos equus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kraftigt utsträcker),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Föra i land;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om hafwet) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">uppkasta, wräka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på land;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">stranda, lida skeppsbrott:</text:span></text:span> navem in terram; e-i in litore, Cs.; ita e-untur, ut ne ad saxa quidem mortui conquiescant; cadaver e-tum, C.; litore e-i; e-tum errare silvis, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uthwißla:</text:span></text:span> cantores; explodi et e-i, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bortdrifwa, aflägsna:</text:span></text:span> mollitiem animi, Ter.; ex animo amorem insitum, C.; ex animis memoriam, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förkasta:</text:span></text:span> Cynicorum ratio tota est e-da, C.<text:line-break/>c. se e. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utbreda sig (utweckla sin kraft):</text:span></text:span> voluptates se profundunt et e-unt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ējectīcius</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. utkastas, utfaller:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ējectio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Landsförwisning:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ējecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ut-, uppkasta:</text:span></text:span> ore crassum cruorem, Vg.; arenas, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ējectāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwad s. uppkastas, uppwräkes:</text:span> diu jacuit sucinum inter cetera e-a maris, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ējectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utkastande, -stötande:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Injĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta in i, på:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg., i allm.: (kasta, i lägga på):</text:span> in flammam alqd; i. stercus supra; catenas, pallium alicui i., C.; tela in alqm; terram, vincula alicui, Vg.; milites (in naves), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">föra ombord,</text:span> Cs.; pellem alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hölja på -),</text:span> N.; frena alicui, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt.</text:span> manus alicui (Cic.), in alqm (Sen.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lägga hand på, dels = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wåldföra:</text:span></text:span> male incontinentes manus dispari i., Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dels = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">tillegna sig, göra laga anspråk på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> injecere manum Parcæ, Vg.; Sen.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dels = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">tillbakahålla:</text:span></text:span> ipsa veritas mihi manum i-it et consistere cogit, C.<text:line-break/>3. se i. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Störta in på, i:</text:span></text:span> in medios hostes, C.; se in ignem, Ter.; se morti, Vg.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Injaga, ingifwa, wäcka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos någon; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">förorsaka:</text:span></text:span> alicui terrorem, mortis formidinem, spem, suspicionem, admirationem, cupiditatem, scrupulum, religionem, periculum; plagam rei, C.; cunctationem; certamen, L.; iras, Vg.<text:line-break/>5. se i. in rem = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Rigta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sina tankar </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">på:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framkasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ett yttrande), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wäcka tal</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">låta förstå:</text:span></text:span> mentionem rei; is mihi in sermone i-ecit se velle, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Injectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: manus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">besittningstagande, egendomsanspråk:</text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Injecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>: manum rei <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillgripa),</text:span> Sil.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Injectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Påkastande, inkastande:</text:span></text:span> Lucr., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Circŭminjĭcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Påkasta omkring:</text:span></text:span> L. (XXV. 36. 5. d. l.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Madv. läser</text:span> circumjicere; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Kühnast</text:span> p. 41.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭbinjĭcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lätt) på:</text:span> manum, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭpĕrinjĭcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, lägga ofwanpå:</text:span></text:span> frondes alveariis, Vg.; terram; togam, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interjăcio</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interjĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sätta, ställa, skjuta </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">emellan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i eg. o. oeg. bet.), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">in ibland; inblanda, inströ</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ord;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">part. pass.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interjectus</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mellanliggande, förfluten emellan, stående emellan -:</text:span> sagittarios inter equites; rubos (inter arbores), Cs.; librum (ɔ: libri scriptionem), C.; moram; pleraque Latino sermone, T. - ea quasi <text:soft-page-break/>longo intervallo i-to videmus; i-ti inter philosophos et eos, qui rem publicam administrant, C.; tempore, die i-to <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efter en tids, dags förlopp),</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interjectio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inskjutande emellan:</text:span></text:span> verborum, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gramm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">interjection;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> parenthes:</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interjectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mellankomst:</text:span></text:span> luna i-u terræ deficit, C.; paucorum dierum, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Objĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta för, åt, emot:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kasta (sätta, skjuta, hålla) för, åt:</text:span> feris alqm, C.; offam Cerbero, Vg.; argentum alicui, Ter.; florem naribus, Pt.; manum ad os, C.; cibum cani, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="T3">part.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Objectus</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">belägen midt emot, framför:</text:span> Cs., L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sätta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ställa, skjuta i wägen för, till motwärn; blottställa:</text:span> propugnaculum hostibus; se telis hostium, C.; carros pro vallo o-rant, Cs.; brachium, vallum, L.; se hosti; milites hosti, N.; clipeos ad tela hostium, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förete, wisa;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynn. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">te sig, wisa sig:</text:span></text:span> homo ignorabilis oculis meis, Pt.; o-ta res terribilis; quum aliqua species utilitatis o-ta est, commoveri animos necesse est, C.; hic aliud majus miseris o-itur, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Injaga, -gifwa, förorsaka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">möta, wederfaras, träffa:</text:span></text:span> alicui lætitiam, Ter.; errorem judicibus; animo metum et dolorem, C.; spem; furorem; terrorem hosti, L.; malum alicui o-itur, Ter.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sätta emot, till bålwerk emot; utsätta, blottställa, wåga:</text:span></text:span> hoc omne tempus post consulatum objecimus iis fluctibus, qui -, C.; facinorosorum armis cives meos o-re nolui; se o. in dimicationem, ad omnes casus periculorum; fortunæ o-tus, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Anföra emot, förekasta, -hålla, tillwita:</text:span></text:span> pleraque, quæ o-bantur, confitebar; adversario alqd; probra; furta; alicui de peculatu, de morte Cæsaris; in loco criminis id o-ecit Fulvio, quod in provinciam poētas duxisset; o-it mihi, me ad Bajas fuisse, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Objecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta fram emot:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> caput fretis volucres, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Blottställa, utsätta:</text:span></text:span> periculis alqm, Sa., Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förekasta, tillwita:</text:span></text:span> crimen alicui, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Objectācŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Dam:</text:span></text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Objectāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Objectātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förebråelse, beskyllning:</text:span></text:span> Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Objectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framskjutande, -hållande, emot,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt:</text:span> insula portum efficit o-u laterum, Vg.; molis, T.; vestis, Col. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Företeelse:</text:span></text:span> hoc repentino o-u viso, N. (Hann. 5. 2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">troligtwis oriktig läsart i st. f.</text:span> o-to visu).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Porrĭcio</text:span>, rēci, rectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framkasta, -bära offer, offra:</text:span></text:span> exta in mare, in fluctus, L., Vg.; inter exta cæsa et p-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mellan slagtandet och offrandet),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præjăcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uppkasta framför:</text:span> moles, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōjĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, skjuta, drifwa fram:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, wräka fram, framstupa, hän, ut:</text:span></text:span> se ad pedes alicujus; Diogenes se p-i jussit inhumatum, C.; flentes se ad Cæsaris pedes; arma p., Cs.; evomere forasque p., C.; p. galeam ante pedes; p-ce tela manu, sanguis meus; se super amicum, Vg.; aurum in deserto Libyæ p-i jussit, Hor.; puerum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utsätta),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skjuta, sträcka fram;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">skjuta fram, ut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i intr. bet.):</text:span> brachium, C.; hastam, N.; clipeum, L.; tectum p-itur, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Drifwa hän,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> stöta bort, ut;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">refl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">störta fram, ut:</text:span> alqm in exsilium, C.; Agrippam insulam Planasiam, T.; se ex urbe, C.; se in forum; L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nedslå, slå till marken, störta:</text:span></text:span> oculi p-ti, T.; nondum desertam esse rempublicam neque p-tum consulare imperium, L.; in miserias p., Sa. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bortkasta, öfwergifwa, gifwa till spillo:</text:span></text:span> libertatem cives, C.; animam, Vg.; ampullas, Hor.; pudorem, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utsätta, blottställa:</text:span></text:span> monere aliquem, ne se p-at, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">framskjuta = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppskjuta:</text:span></text:span> T.<text:line-break/>e. se p. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">tränga sig fram, framstörta; hängifwa sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt -:</text:span> in hoc judicium; libido se proripiet et p-et, C.; in fletus muliebres, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōjectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framskjutande; som skjuter ut, fram:</text:span></text:span> urbs in altum, C. venter p-ior, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framstående, ytterlig:</text:span></text:span> audacia; cupiditas, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Böjd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt:</text:span> ad audendum, C.; ad libidinem p-simus, T.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Krypande:</text:span></text:span> p-a servientium patientia, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōjectīcius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utsatt:</text:span></text:span> puella, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōjectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framkastande, utsträckande:</text:span></text:span> brachii, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōjecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kasta, störta:</text:span> in pericula, Amm. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förebrå:</text:span> Enn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōjectūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utsprång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en byggnad:</text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōjectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framskjutande:</text:span></text:span> corporis, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rējĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta tillbaka:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, drifwa tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> vento tempestate r-i, aliquo; hostem Antiochiā; hostes in oppidum, C.; capellas a flumine, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta bakåt, kasta, ställa bakom</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sig); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">kasta baklänges:</text:span></text:span> manibus ad tergum r-tis; scutum r.; fugere scuto non modo abjecto, sed ne r-to quidem; pænulam; sagulam, C.; amictum ex humeris; parmam, Vg.; in postremam aciem aliquos, L. - se in alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i ngns armar)</text:span> puella, Ter.; membra rejecit, Ct.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åter bortkasta, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bortwända:</text:span></text:span> librum, Ov.; oculos Rutulorum arvis, Vg.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, skjuta igen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till swar):</text:span> telum in hostem, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T4">uppkasta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">-kräka:</text:span></text:span> sanguinem ore, Pn.; vinum, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tillbakaslå, -drifwa, afslå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (anfall); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">aflägsna:</text:span></text:span> minas Hannibalis, Hor.; ferrum atque audaciam alicujus; a suspicionibus, C.; alqm a studio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afskräcka),</text:span> Ter.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta bort, förwisa, afwisa; rata, förkasta;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">jäfwa:</text:span></text:span> ex honestorum grege iu hunc gregem, C.; consolationem, Pn.; Ennii Medeam; divinationem; bona, C.; r-tæ patet janua Lydiæ, Hor.; judices, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta ifrån sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wisa, skjuta, ifrån sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hänskjuta, förwisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt till ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hänwisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till -:</text:span> invidiam consules ad senatum; senatus rem ad populum, ad novos magistratus, L.; Romam causam r-as; consultores ad Furium r.; ad epistolam alqm, C.<text:line-break/>d. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppskjuta:</text:span></text:span> alqd in aliud tempus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rējectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förkastlig:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rējĭciendus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förkastlig:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rējectāneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är att rata, ej wälja:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rējectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppkastande:</text:span></text:span> sanguinis, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bortskjutande; afwisande, försmående, förkastande:</text:span></text:span> culpæ, Qu. -, civitatis; judicum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rējecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Återkasta:</text:span></text:span> montes voces, Lucr.; caseum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppkasta),</text:span> Sp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rējĭcŭlus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(reĭculus), <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är att förkasta, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Dålig; förspilld:</text:span></text:span> ovis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. ej är wärd att lägga på),</text:span> Varr.; dies, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subjĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta under; kasta upp intill:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kasta, lägga, skjuta under, hänunder, inunder:</text:span> ignem, faces rei; cervices securi, C.; epistolam sub pulvinum, N.; ova gallinis, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, skjuta upp under; skjuta upp, uppkasta;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">refl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skjuta upp</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">intr.</text:span>): inter carros rotasque mataras et tragulas s-bant, Cs.; in equum alqm; alnus se, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skjuta, föra, uppföra intill; räcka, lemna:</text:span></text:span> aciem tumulis; ædes colli, L.; libellum alicui, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Underkasta, underlägga;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (logiskt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">underordna:</text:span></text:span> se alterius imperio et potestati; tutelæ alqm; sub dominationem alicujus alqm; virtus sub varios casus s-ta, C.; se legibus, Pn.; apes sub regem, Col.; pars s-ta generi; sub genus partes, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utsätta för, gifwa till pris åt:</text:span></text:span> scelus nocentis odio civium, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Underställa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">göra till föremål</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">framställa för; tilldela:</text:span></text:span> res sensibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> sub sensus s-tæ; huic virtuti veritas s-ta est est tanquam materia, quam tractet, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Underlägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett ord en betydelse, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">inlägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> betyd. i ordet;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ligga under, i:</text:span></text:span> voci, sub voce s-ta sententia; verborum sonitus inanis nullā s-tā sententiā, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Underskjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">sätta i stället för:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">falskligen understicka; förfalska:</text:span></text:span> verbum pro verbo; testamenta, C.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tal </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tillfoga:</text:span></text:span> rationem, cur sic opinetur; causam; exemplum, C.<text:line-break/>g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Erinra, ingifwa; yttra till swar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (förmaning, tröst):</text:span> cupio mihi ab <text:soft-page-break/>illo s-i, si quid prætereo; spem s. alicui, C.; ea, quæ muliebris dolor s-it querentibus, L.; carmina amor mihi, Ppt.; vix pauca furenti s., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subjectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Underliggande; belägen under;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> belägen intill, inwid:</text:span> campus viæ, urbi, L., T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Underlydande, -ordnad; underdånig, ödmjuk; utsatt för:</text:span></text:span> nulli, C.; parcere subjectis et debellare superbos, Vg.; s-ior invidiæ, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subjecte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Underdånigt, ödmjukt:</text:span></text:span> s-sime, C s.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subjectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">underställande = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Framställande:</text:span></text:span> rei sub adspectum paene s., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">understickande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förfalskning:</text:span></text:span> testamentorum, L. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tillbifogande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af swar, förklaring):</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subjecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, sticka, föra under,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> inunder:</text:span> stimulos alicui, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta uppåt:</text:span></text:span> saxa Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subjector</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förfalskare:</text:span></text:span> testamentorum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subjectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Underläggning, -lag:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭperjăcio</text:span>, jēci, jactum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> jectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta ofwanpå, öfwer:</text:span></text:span> folia, Col.; æquor s-tum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. flödat öfwer),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerhölja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerskrida, -stiga:</text:span></text:span> fidem augendo, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭperjacto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta upp:</text:span></text:span> Val. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hopa öfwer:</text:span> mugiles navigia s-ant, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭperjectio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerdrift), hyperbol;</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭperjectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">betäckning:</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Transjĭcio</text:span> (Cs.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oftare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trājĭcio</text:span>, jēci, jectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta öfwer, till andra sidan, till annat ställe:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: så wäl </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta ngt öfwer,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">kasta öfwer ngt med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> vexillum trans vallum hostium, L.; murum jaculo, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Föra öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (en flod l. dyl.);</text:span> se t-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. blott</text:span> t-re: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sätta, fara, gå öfwer:</text:span> exercitum ex Asia in Europam, N.; milites trans flumen; legiones in Siciliam, L.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> 2 <text:span text:style-name="T3">acc.</text:span>: exercitum Rhodanum, C. ep.; copias Hellespontum, N.; se Alpes, C.; amnem vado t., L.; mari in terram, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">öfwerflytta;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwergå:</text:span></text:span> alqd in alia vasa, Varr.; Athenas magnam partem fortunarum, N.; alqd de navi in navem, L.; ad nos illud incendium t-et, L.; dolore capitis in cor t-to, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Flytta, skjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">omflytta:</text:span></text:span> invidiam in alqm; verba, C. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kasta, borra igenom; genomborra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med något:</text:span> columbam suspendit in fune t-to <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genom masten draget),</text:span> Vg.; alqm; femur tragulā; t-tus pilis, Cs.; ferro pectora; t-tus lora per pedes, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trājectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwergång, -fart; förflyttning:</text:span></text:span> Acherontis; stellæ; verborum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hyperbol:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trājectūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwerskjutande:</text:span> mutulorum, Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trājectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerfart:</text:span></text:span> commodissimus in Britanniam, Cs.; t. Albulæ, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwergångsställe, färjstad:</text:span></text:span> Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Jact . . ., Jacul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jacio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jam</text:span> <text:line-break/>(ĭam, Com.), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ren tidspartikel (om hwilken tid som helst i förhållande till en föregående eller efterföljande): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Redan (allt, allaredan,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i mots. till något följande); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nu, då, numera;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (efter negation) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">mera</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till något föregående):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om något närwarande: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Redan, nu, numera, mera;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ej sällan</text:span> j. nunc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(redan nu);</text:span> nunc j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nu),</text:span> Com.: scio j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(redan);</text:span> hoc agite, sultis, spectatores, nunc ĭam, Pt.; defunctus j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nu)</text:span> sum: nil est, quod dicat mihi; me ejus spero fratrem propemodum j. reperisse, Ter.; j. nunc timeo; deflexit j. de spatio consuetudo majorum; parietes modo urbis stant, iique ipsi j. extrema scelera metuentes; eo j. nobis frui non licet, C.; non j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(icke mer)</text:span> lactens, Varr.; non j. mortem, tantummodo cruciatus deprecor, Sa.; ohe, j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nu)</text:span> satis est!; redeunt j. gramina campis; j. non prata rigent, Hor.; adeunt Cephisidas undas, ut nondum liquidas, sic j. vada nota secantes, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om något tillkommande: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nu straxt; på stunden; sedan:</text:span></text:span> j. hic ero, Ter.; illud j. videbimus, nunc hoc agamus, C.; jamque aderit Pyrrhus multa de cæde Politæ, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om något förflutet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Redan; då; numera</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (efter negation):</text:span> summam spem de eo j. puero habuerant; sensim j. antea hanc consuetudinem minuebamus, post vero Sullæ victoriam penitus amisimus; quum j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(när sedan)</text:span> ætas et auctoritas gravius quiddam requireret, idem erat, neque decebat idem, C.; j. se sustinere non poterant; j. defendebat nemo, Cs.; jamque rubescebat stellis Aurora remotis, , Vg.; j. tum in Palatino monte Lupercal hoc fuit; j. filii prope ætatem puberem erant; j. non feras tantum subsistere, sed in latrones impetum facere; j. inde ab initio Faustulo spes fuerat, regiam stirpem apud se educari; j. induciæ exierant, L.; non j. imperator erat, T.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fördubbladt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Än- än:</text:span></text:span> Hor. Od. IV. 9.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">consecutiv partikel l. utmärkande följd: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Då; nu:</text:span></text:span> mane j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wänta då),</text:span> Pt.; accede ad ignem hunc, j. calesces plus satis, Ter.; jam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nu)</text:span> illa non longam disputationem desiderant; adde numeros et ipsa verba compone: j. neminem antepones Catoni, C.; quod si non aliam venturo fata Neroni invenere viam, j. nihil, o Superi, querimur, Luc.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwergångspartikel: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nu, widare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (oftare i förening med</text:span> porro, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eller med</text:span> vero, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">när det följande skall framhållas ss. det wigtigare):</text:span> j. ad illa summa veniamus; j. vituperandi præcepta ex contrariis vitiis sumenda esse perspicuum est; j. illa, quæ naturā, non literis assecuti sunt, neque cum Græcia neque ulla cum gente sunt conferenda (Tusc. I. §. 2.); jam Antonii caput in Rostris positum est; j. vero videtis, nihil esse morti tam simile, quam somnum; j. v. virtuti Cn. Pompeji quæ par oratio inveniri potest?, C.; ac j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(och se’n, och slutligen),</text:span> ut (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ock)</text:span> omnia contra opinionem acciderent, tamen patere refugium, Cs. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> 4.).<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>4. = etiam: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Till och med; ännu</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wid comparativa uttryck); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ock:</text:span></text:span> Campans genus multo Surorum j. antidit patientiam, Pt. Trin. 545; Cato cognomen j. habebat in senectute sapientis, C. (de Am. §. 6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Seyffert);</text:span> neque enim prædone marito filia digna tua est, si j. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ock)</text:span> mea filia digna est, Ov. (Met. V. 523).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jamdiu</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Redan länge; redan längesedan:</text:span></text:span> j. desiit fieri; j. flagitat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bedt och beder ännu),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jamdūdum</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Redan en stund</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">någon tid; redan för en stund</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">tid sedan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> dudum), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så wäl med</text:span> tempora <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för fulländad som med</text:span> tempora <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för ofulländad handling om något fortfarande; i sw. öfwersättes</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">præs.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">impf.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">perf.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">plusqpf.</text:span>: j. animus est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(warit)</text:span> in patinis, Ter., dixi j. d., Pt.; j. te hortor, C.; j. erumpere nubem ardebant, Vg.; pressa tuis balanus capillus j. apud me est, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i uppmaningar (med otålighet) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På stunden, ofördröjligen:</text:span></text:span> j. sumite poenas, Vg.; ardua j. demittite cornua, rector clamat; utere j. generoso sanguine, dixit, nulla mora est, Ov. (Met. XIII. 458).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jamjam</text:span> <text:line-break/>(jam jam) <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nu, nu) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nu</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med stark betoning), alltren, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">numera:</text:span></text:span> j. intelligo, quid dicas; Appius senatum j. inclinatum a Pyrrhi pace revocavit, C.; j. nulla mora est, sequor et, qua ducitis, adsum; j. nec maxima Juno nec pater omnipotens oculis hæc aspicit æquis, Vg.; j. efficaci do manus scientiæ, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Genast, i nästa ögonblick:</text:span></text:span> silex j. casura imminet, Vg.; ego j. illum convenam investigabo, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jam</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">jamque</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Just nu</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">då; i nästa ögonblick:</text:span></text:span> j. adero; quæ potest in vita esse jucunditas, quum dies et noctes cogitandum sit, jam jamque esse moriendum?, C.; j. manu tenet et premit hasta, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jamprīdem</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> pridem):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Redan längesedan:</text:span></text:span> j. conticuerunt literæ tuæ, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Redan länge:</text:span></text:span> sic j. cupio, C.; jactamus te omnis j. Roma beatum, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭambus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">versfoten </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jamb:</text:span></text:span> syllaba longa brevi subjecta (⏑—) vocatur i., pes citus, Hor.; i-um frequentem ab oratore segregat (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utdömer ur den oratoriske stilen)</text:span> Aristoteles, C.; i. est ex brevi et longa, Qu. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> IX. cap. 4.). <text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jambisk vers,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> enkannerligen med afs. på innehållet = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">smädedikt:</text:span></text:span> Archilochum proprio rabies armavit i-o; quem criminosis cunque voles modum, pones i-bis, Hor.; scriptores i-orum, Qu. X. 1. 9. 59. 96. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭambēus</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jambisk vers:</text:span></text:span> iambus - trimetris accrescere jussit nomen i-is, senos quum redderet ictus (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gaf de sexfotade iamberne namn af trimetri),</text:span> Hor. AP. 251 ff.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭambĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jambisk:</text:span></text:span> Gramm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>ămĭdæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">siareslägt i Elis.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">J</text:span>āna = Diana, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Janalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Janus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">J</text:span>ānĭcŭlum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kulle i Rom på westra sidan om Tibern.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Janigena <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Janus.<text:line-break/>Janitor, -trix <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Janua.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭanthis,</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Viol.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭanthĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Violblå:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jānua,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Dörr:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttryck:</text:span> pultare, Pt.; patefacere, claudere, effringere, evellere, C.; pulsare, pandere; j. adaperta, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. uttryck:</text:span> eā j-ā, qua nolui, in causam ingressus sum, C.; patet isti j. leto, Vg.; desine, Paule, meum lacrimis urgere sepulcrum: panditur ad nullas j. nigra preces, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jānĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Dörrwaktare:</text:span></text:span> carceris, C.; infernæ j. aulæ, Ppt.; cæli, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jānĭtrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Dörrwakterska:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Janualis, -arius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Janus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jānus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl. Ciceros gißning</text:span> ab eundo):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Porthwalf, genomgångsbåge:</text:span></text:span> transitiones perviæ j-i appellantur, C.; dexter j. portæ Carmentalis, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt wid</text:span> forum Romanum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">woro</text:span> jani <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med twå l. fyra hwalf på </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">en</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> gång genomgångar och ett slags bodar l. bazarer för wexlare (en sådan står ännu qwar nära kyrkan S. Giorgio in Velabro emellan </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">forum</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och Tibern):</text:span> boni viri ad j-um medium sedentes (ɔ: argentarii), C.; o cives, cives, quærenda pecunia primum est, virtus post numos, hæc j. summus ab imo prodocet, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. Janus Quirinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> Quirini, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en byggnad</text:span> (fornix bifrons) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af det slag, som ofwan (1) beskrifwits, hwilken stod öppen i krig, men war tillsluten under fredstid; denna byggnad stod öster om</text:span> forum Romanum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">der detta gränsade intill</text:span> forum Cæsaris, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och inneslöt, åtminstone i sednare tid, en bild</text:span> a<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">f den personificerade</text:span> Janus (3): quum tot sint j-i, cur stas sacratus in uno, hic ubi juncta foris templa duobus habes?; ut populo reditus pateant ad bella profecto, tota patet dempta janua nostra sera. Pace fores obdo, ne quā discedere possit, Ov. (Fast. I. 257—281); Numa j-um ad infimum Argiletum indicem pacis bellique fecit, apertus ut in armis esse civitatem, clausus pacatos circa omnes esse populos significaret, L. I. 19.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="T5">J</text:span>ānus i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">dörrarnes</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och i widsträcktare mening </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ingångens, begynnelsens</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> gud, åt hwilken morgonen, årets första dag, det första offret och öfwerhufwud hwarje företags begynnelse war helgad: Ianus föreställdes med twå, åt motsatta håll wända ansigten (enl.</text:span> Ov. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">emedan hwarje dörr har</text:span> geminas frontes): principem in sacrificando J-um esse voluerunt, C.; Matutine pater seu J-e libentius audis, unde homines primos operum vitæque labores instituunt, Hor.; J-e biceps, anni tacite labentis origo, solus de superis qui tua terga vides; J. biformis; sacer ancipiti mirandus imagine J. bina repens oculis obtulit ora meis; præsideo foribus cæli cum mitibus Horis: it, redit officio Juppiter ipse meo. Inde vocor Janus, Ov. (Fast. I. 1—281); Ps. I. 58. ff.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">J</text:span>ānālis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till Ianus hörande.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">J</text:span>ānĭgĕna, ae, c.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">son l. dotter af Ianus.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Jānuālis, <text:line-break/>Jānuārius, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: Jani, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som tillhör Ianus</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">årets begynnelsemånad:</text:span> mensis, kalendæ j-æ, C. - <text:span text:style-name="T3">Subst.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Jānuārius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">månaden Ianuari.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>ăpĕtus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en Titan:</text:span> I-i genus (= Prometheus), Hor. <text:line-break/>Īăpĕtĭdes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īăpĕtīŏnĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronym.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>āpy̆des, um, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">illyriskt folk.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>āpys, y̆dis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">japydisk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īăpy̆dĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Iapydien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>āpyx, y̆gis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nordwest-wind:</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>Īăpy̆gĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sydöstre delen af Italien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>arba <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭarbas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Ĭabīta, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mauritanska namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>ardănis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dotter af Iardanus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>ăsĭus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īăsĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Īăsis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronym.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>āson, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn (Argonauternes anförare).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭāsŏnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭaspis,</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grön ädelsten, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Iaspis:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>assus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Carien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭassĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭassenses, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inw. i I.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭātrăliptes,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭātrălipta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(läkare) s. insmörjer ngn för kroppsöfningar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sjukgymnastiker:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭātrăliptĭcē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sjnkgymnastik:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭātrŏnīces</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Läkares besegrare:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>azy̆ges, um, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sarmatiskt folk i nuw. Ungern.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭazyx, y̆gis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>bēres, um, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Iberer, folkslag</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Spanien.</text:span><text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Asien, mellan Swarta och Caspiska hafwet (äfwen</text:span> Iberi). <text:line-break/>Ĭbēria, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Iberien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭbērus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">iberisk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭbērĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>bērus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Spanien (Ebro).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ibex,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stenbock:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ibi, Ibidem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Is.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ībis,</text:span> is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> -ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ibis,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos Aegyptierne helig fågel:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>by̆cus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>cărus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mythiskt personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īcărĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: mare I-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utmed mindre Asiens sydwestra kust).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Iccirco = Idcirco, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Is.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span>cēni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">britanniskt folkslag.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ichneumon,</text:span> ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags råtta:</text:span> C. N. D. I. §. 101.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span>chnŏbătes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(spårgångare): hundnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ichnŏgrăphĭa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Grundritning:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ichthy̆ŏcolla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fiskkitt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Husbloß,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwensom den fisk, hwaraf det fås:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span>chthy̆ŏphăgi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fiskätare) ett folkslag:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Īco,</text:span> īci, ictum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stöta, hugga, slå, träffa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> femur alicujus, Pt.; lapide ictus, C.; ici fulmine, sagittā, Ct.; sonat icta securibus ilex, Vg.; catapulta aut ballista icit alqm, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. foedus icere cum aliquo, inter aliquos = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sluta fördrag:</text:span></text:span> icisse, icerat, C.; L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om slag, som träffa sinnet, om dynamisk inwerkan på sinnena o. s. w.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Slå, träffa:</text:span></text:span> orbitatis metu icta pubes Romana (morte Romuli), L.; patria desideriis icta fidelibus, Hor.; nidore (culinæ) ictus (Claudius), Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ictus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stöt, slag, hugg,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kast, skott, bett):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> i. comminus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.:</text:span> conjectio telorum); gladiatoris; i-u fulminis Phaĕthon deflagravit, C.; scuta uno i-u pilorum transfixa et colligata; i-um defendere et repellere, Cs.; ferire alquid certo i-u; telorum levis et vanus i., Ct.; cædere arborem cæcis i-bus, Pn.; i. cornuum, cæstus, gladii, cuspidis; validi incudibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på städen)</text:span> i-us, Vg.; baculi; serpentis, Ov.; saxi, T.; fervidi solis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stygn),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prægnant: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fart:</text:span></text:span> telum imbelle sine i-u (misit senex), Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Taktslag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i musik l. metrik:</text:span> (senarius) tres reddit i-us, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. l. i bildl. uttryck: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Slag, hugg:</text:span></text:span> i. novæ calamitatis; status hic non dolendi non habet ullum i-um, quo pellat animum, C.; sub i-u, extra i-um esse, Sen., sub i-um dari, T. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under, utom hugget</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i, utom fara); -</text:span> singulis i-bus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ett</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> slag)</text:span> transigere bella, T.; i. temporis, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Īcon,</text:span> ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bild, porträtt:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īcŏnĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: simulacrum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(porträttbild),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īcuncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>cŏnĭum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. stadsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ictĕrĭcus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gulsiktig:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ictis,</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Weßla:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Ictus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ico.<text:line-break/>Icuncula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Icon.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>da, ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īdē, es; <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg wid Troja och på Creta.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īdæus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>dălĭum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Cypern, med berömdt Venus-tempel.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īdălĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: Venus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>das, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. mansnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Idcirco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Is.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭdĕa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hos C. skrifwet med grek. bokstäfwer,</text:span> Tusc. I. §. 58: ἰδέαν nos dicimus speciem): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Idée</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lat.</text:span> species, forma): eorum, quæ natura fiunt, æternum exemplar, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Idem Identidem, Ideo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Is.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭdĭŏgrăphus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.:</text:span> v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egenhändigt skrifwen:</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭdĭōta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Okunnig, olärd, obildad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> menniska:</text:span> C., Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭdĭōtismus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">från hwardagsspråket hemtad wändning:</text:span> Sen. Rhet. III. præf.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span>distavisus campus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid Weser:</text:span> T. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span>dmon, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Idmŏnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Īdōlon,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īdōlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Spöke, skenbild</text:span></text:span>:Pn. ep. VII. 27.; Lucil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>dŏmĕneus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fyrstafwigt,</text:span> Vg.), ĕi, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T3">acc.</text:span> -ēa, Vg.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">konung på Creta.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭdōneus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tjenlig, lämplig, egnad; i stånd till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">duglig; wärdig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">relat.: tjenlig o. s. w. till</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">ad rem</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T3">alicui rei</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">qui</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">conj.</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet. med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">inf.</text:span>): tempus ad agendum; mens sapientis ad jubendum et ad deterrendnm; i. rei; res i-a, de qua quæratur; is i. est, quem imitere, C.; locus ad aciem instruendam, Cs.; ad ponenda castra, N.; i. bello, vitæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nyttig);</text:span> arti, pugnæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. har anlag, är duglig till),</text:span> Hor.; in nullam rem, Sen.; fons rivo dare nomen i., Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tjenlig; wärdig; gill, giltig:</text:span></text:span> loca i-a castellis communiit; tempus, causa i., N.; minus i-um hominem præmio afficere; hominibus indigentibus et i-is ex re familiari impertire; testis; auctor, C.; debitor i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i stånd att betala),</text:span> Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭdōnee</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrĭdōneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mycket tjenlig, duglig:</text:span></text:span> locus castris, Cs.; præceptor, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Īdos,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: forma rei naturalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> idea), Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>dŏthĕa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Idulis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Idus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>dūmæa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭdūmē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landskap i Palæstina.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭdūmæus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">judisk:</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Iduo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Idus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Īdus,</text:span> uum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> di-vido?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mellerste dagen (13 l. 15:de) i en månad: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Idus:</text:span></text:span> hæc i-bus scripsi, C.; ad i-us Apriles reverterentur, Cs.; omnem redegit i-bus pecuniam (fenerator), Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īdūlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: ovis, (quæ omnibus idibus Jovi mactabatur), Fs., Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īduo</text:span>, 1. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dela,</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>dȳia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Īdyllĭum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poetiskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Småstycke,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> smärre dikt:</text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jĕcur</text:span> <text:line-break/>(jocur, L. d. l.), cŏris, jŏcĭnŏris (-nĕris; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Neue),</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lefwer:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. känslans, begärens säte (hjerta):</text:span> ulcerare, torrere j. alicujus, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jĕcŏrosus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lefwersjuk:</text:span> Sil.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jĕcuscŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jējūnus</text:span>, -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fastande; tom, hungrig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> biduum ita j. fui, ut ne aquam quidem gustarem, C.; corpora, L.; stomachus; dentes, Hor.; plebecula misera ac j-a, C.; os; aviditas, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i materiel mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Torr, ofruktbar:</text:span></text:span> agri, C.; glarea, Vg.; terra, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på andligt innehåll, lif, kraft) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tom, andelös, torr:</text:span></text:span> j-a concertatio verborum; cognitio j-a et solivaga sit, si nulla actio rerum consequatur; res j-æ, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om framställningen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mager, torr, nykter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> ubertas): oratio j-a; orator j-ior, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tänkesätt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Småaktig, torftig, simpel:</text:span></text:span> animo est j-o et angusto, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tom, saknande:</text:span></text:span> nox visu j-a, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jējūne</text:span>, -ius. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T6">f</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ramställningen) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Torrt, magert; torftigt, knappt:</text:span></text:span> disputare j. et exiliter; hæc dicuntur j-ius: nam iis ubertas orationis adhiberi non potest, C.; quid j-ius (de meis laudibus) dixit inimicus?, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jējūnĭtas</text:span>, atis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i materiel men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Torrhet:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tomhet, okunnighet:</text:span></text:span> bonarum artium, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Magerhet, torrhet; nykterhet, enkelhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i framställn.:</text:span> cavenda est oratori j. et inopia, C.; alii sunt in eadem j-e concinniores et leviter ornati, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jējūnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fastetid, fasta, fastande, hunger:</text:span></text:span> Jupiter indicit j-a, Hor.; Cereri instituere, L.; solvere edendo, Ov.; undæ, Luc.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Magerhet; ofruktbarhet:</text:span></text:span> pecoris, Vg.; terra laborat j-o, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jējūniōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Förhungrad:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jento,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Spisa frukost:</text:span></text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jentācŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Frukost:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span>gilium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö wid kusten af Etrurien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭgĭtur,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">partikel (wanligast postpositiv):</text:span> <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T3">conclusiv</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Alltså;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i frågor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">då:</text:span></text:span> verum autem primum: verum i. extremum; quum ita sit, certe nec secerni nec distrahi potest animus, ne interire quidem i.; A. ego vero mortuos nusquam esse puto. - M. i. ne esse quidem; nulla est i. excusatio peccati, si amici causā peccaveris; hæc i. prima lex in amicitia sanciatur; quæ est i. aut ubi versatur divinatio?; in quo i. loco est animus?, C.; quisnam i. liber? - sapiens, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T3">consecutiv</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Då; nu; i sådant fall; således, sålunda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i imperativsatser:</text:span> expone i. primum, animos remanere post mortem, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i frågor:</text:span> quid i. faciam?, Ter.; quis i. vocaris?, Pt.; Themistocles omnium civium perceperat nomina. Num i. censetis, eum, qui esset Lysimachus, Aristiden salutare solitum?, C.; Iliacas i. classes atque ultima Teucrum jussa sequar?, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hos de historiske författarne, serskildt</text:span> Sa. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> T.) = itaque: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Derför ock, sålunda, under sådana förhållanden:</text:span></text:span> nulla i. blandimenta a senatu data, L.; ubi periculum aderat, invidia atque superbia post fuere. I. consul declaratur M. Tullius, Sa.; i. verso civitatis statu nihil usquam prisci et integri moris, T. (Aun. I. 4.); ergo i., Ap.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eftersatser: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Då:</text:span></text:span> ubi rex ero, i. instruam agrum et ædes, Pt.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">der man efter en inledning eller ämnets uppställning öfwergår till sjelfwa berättelsen l. utwecklingen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Alltså, då:</text:span></text:span> nunc ad reliquam partem divisionis institutæ revertamur. Panætius i. - (de Off. III. 3.); A. Tu, ut videtur: nos ad audiendum parati sumus. - M. mors i. ipsa quid sit, primum est videndum; nunc juris principia videamus. I. doctissimis viris placuit proficisci a lege, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sammanfattande och återknytande en afbruten tankeföljd:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inuti en period: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Säger jag, alltså, således:</text:span></text:span> ut, quum videmus speciem primum candoremque cæli - - hæc i. et alia innumerabilia quum cernimus -, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inledande en ny period:</text:span> quibus rationibus hanc facultatem assequi possimus -, dicemus - -: sed pauca ante dicenda sunt. Hoc i. cognito -, Cic. Off. II. 20.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ignarus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gnarus.<text:line-break/>Ignav . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Navus.<text:line-break/>Igne . . ., Igni . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ignis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ignis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eld:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> <text:line-break/>1.; eg.:</text:span> i. elicitur conflictu et tritu lapidum, corripit alqd; materia concipit i-em; i-em subjicere tectis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sätta eld på -),</text:span> C.; i-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> i-es facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppgöra);</text:span> i-em inferre operibus; i-i cremare, necare, interficere alqm; ignibus significatio - nem facere, Cs.; æstuat in fornace, Vg.; i-em ab æde abstinere, L. - i-es = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eldswådor,</text:span> T.; = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lusteldar,</text:span> St.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om stjernorna:</text:span> illi sempiterni i-es, quæ sidera vocantur, C.; vos, <text:soft-page-break/>æterni i-es, testor, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eldglans, blixtrande glans:</text:span></text:span> oculorum, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om begärens, serskildt kärlekens eld:</text:span> exarsere i-es animo, subit ira -; cæco carpitur i-e regina, Vg.; lentis penitus maceror ignibus, Hor.; mersus visceribus i., Sen. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton. = den älskade:</text:span> meus i. Amyntas, Vg. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">farans, förderfwets </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eld, brand:</text:span></text:span> senatui i-em subjicere, C.; parvus hic i. incendium ingens suscitabit, L.<text:line-break/>e. sacer i., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en sjukdom (ros):</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Taga eld; an-, upptändas:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> mundus, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> ira, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Igneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af eld, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eld-; brännande, glödhet:</text:span></text:span> humidum, flabile, i-um; i-a natura animi; sive animus animalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af luft)</text:span> est sive i., - C.; sol, Hor., Vg.; fervor Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Blixtrande, strålande:</text:span></text:span> astra, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Brännande:</text:span></text:span> sitis, Vg. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eldig, häftig, blixtsnabb:</text:span></text:span> virtus, Luc.; virgo - pernicibus i-a plantis transit equum cursu, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Igniārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fnöske, tunder:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignĭcŏmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eld-, guld-hårig, -lockig:</text:span></text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Liten eld, gnista:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Juv., Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eldglans:</text:span></text:span> carbunculi, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">låga = smärta:</text:span> desiderii, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gnista = anlag:</text:span> natura nobis dedit parvos i-os virtutum; is jacit viriles i-os, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eldbringande, -förande:</text:span></text:span> axis (solis), Ov.; lampas, Lucr.; hortatus, Sil. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignĭfluus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. strömmar af eld:</text:span> Cd. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignĭgĕna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">född i eld (Bacchus):</text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignĭgĕnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. wållar eldswåda:</text:span> Ap. (al.: <text:line-break/>igninus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: asinus i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. går i elden),</text:span> Ap. (alii: <text:line-break/>ignigenus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignĭpes</text:span>, ĕdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Eldfotad:</text:span></text:span> equus, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignĭpŏtens</text:span>, tis. <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som råder öfwer elden:</text:span> deus (Vulcanus), Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignispĭcium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spådom af eld:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Glödande, hetsig:</text:span></text:span> æther, Ap.; vinum, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ignītābŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: ”ignis receptaculum”, Fs., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">glödpanna: - bildl.:</text:span> vinum fomes et i. ingenii virtutisque, Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ignobil . . ., Ignomin . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Nosco. <text:line-break/>Ignor . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gnarus.<text:line-break/>Ignosc . . ., Ignotus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Nosco.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>gŭvium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Umbrien (Eugubio, Gubbio).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īgŭvīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īgŭvīnātes, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inwånare i Iguvium.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>lerda, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Spanien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭlĕus,</text:span> ei, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tarmref, kolik:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Īlex,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Jernek, stenek:</text:span></text:span> cavis imposita saxis; i. multa fruge pecus, multa dominum juvat umbrā, Hor.; arguta, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īlĭcētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skog af</text:span> ilex: Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īlĭceus</text:span> (St.),<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īligneus</text:span> (Cato),<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īlignus</text:span> (Ter., Vg.) <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Stenek-.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Īlia,</text:span> ium, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Buk, weka lifwet;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hos djur) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">slaksidor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till de omgifwande hårde delarne); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">innanmäte:</text:span></text:span> inter latus et i. figere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genomborra)</text:span> alqm; per uterum et i. venit arundo; i. singultu tendere, Vg.; solve senescentem - equum, ne peccet ad extremum - et i. ducat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(flämta; hafwa qwickdrag);</text:span> i. rhombi edere; o dura messorum i., Hor.; i. trahere, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īliōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har tarmref:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>lia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Romuli moder (Rhea Silvia).</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>liădes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ilias son:</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Iliacus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ilium.<text:line-break/>Iliades <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ilia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Ilium.<text:line-break/>Ilias <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ilium.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Īlĭcet</text:span> = i, licet:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå, det är tillåtet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> scilicet, videlicet):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i uttryck, som brukades wid upplösningen af en senats- l. folkförsamling l. af en församling wid likbegängelse:</text:span> Donat. ad Ter. Heaut. V. 2. 20.; Serv. ad Vg. Aen. II. 424. VI. 216. 231. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nu är tid att gå; nu kan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">måste du</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">nu kunna wi gå:</text:span></text:span> i.: quid hic conterimus operam frustra?, Ter.; i. parasiticæ arti maxumam in malam crucem, Pt.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(farwäl mitt hopp), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Allt är slut; allt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hopp) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">är ute; wälan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (uttryck för förtwiflan l. resignation):</text:span> i., mandata heri perierunt, Pt.; actum est, i., peristi, Ter. <text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Straxt, utan dröjsmål:</text:span></text:span> i. obruimur numero, Vg.; acer Amor, tractas utinam tua tela sagittas i. exstinctas aspiciamque faces, Tib.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ilicetum, Iliceus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ilex.<text:line-break/>Ilico <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Illico.<text:line-break/>Ilign . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ilex.<text:line-break/>Ilion <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ilium.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>lĭŏnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>lĭŏneus (4<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-stafwigt),</text:span> ei, (<text:span text:style-name="T3">acc.</text:span> -ēa), <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Iliosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Ilia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>līsus <text:line-break/>(Ilissus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod wid Athen.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>līthȳia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">barnsbördens gudinna (Diana).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>lĭum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>lĭon, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Troja.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>lĭus, <text:line-break/>Īlĭăcus, <text:line-break/>Īlĭensis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>lĭădes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Trojan.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>lĭas, ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dotter af Ilion, ilisk qwinna.</text:span><text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sången om Ilion, Iliaden.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Illā, Illac (af Illic) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ille. <text:line-break/>Illacessitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lacesso, Lacio.<text:line-break/>Illæsus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lædo. <text:line-break/>Illatabilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lātus.<text:line-break/>Illatenus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ille. <text:line-break/>Illautus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lavo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ille,</text:span> illa, illud (illut; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.</text:span> ollus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se detta;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">gen.</text:span> illīus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o.</text:span> illĭus), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Pron. personale</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">demonstr.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Han, hon, det; den, det:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med eftertryck och stark betoning, i motsats till mig eller dig eller den, som för tillfället är talets föremål</text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den andre):</text:span> quid enim? Africanus indigens mei? Minime, ac ne ego quidem illius; natura hominis beluis antecedit: i-æ enim nihil sentiunt præter voluptatem, C.; regique hæc dicite vestro, non i-i imperium pelagi sævumque tridentem, sed mihi sorte datum; sic oculos, sic i. manus, sic ora ferebat, Vg.; reliqui, qui domi manserunt, se atque i-os alunt; quum fratri auxilium ferret, i-um ex periculo eripuit, ipse equo dejectus est, Cs.; i., - ego contra (Epam. VI. 6.); nostris moribus sunt honesta multa, quæ apud i-os turpia putantur, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utan eftertryck, ett enkelt personale:</text:span> quam Juno fertur terris magis omnibus unam posthabita coluisse Samo, hic illius arma, hic currus fuit, Vg.; N. Ag. VII. 2.; quoties aliquos parat edere questus, sibilat: hanc i-i vocem natura reliquit, Ov. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Met. IV. 497. 507. 586. 590. 596.); beatulus - in portam rigidos calces extendit, at i-um hesterni capite induto subiere Quirites, Ps.; plurimus hic æger moritur vigilando, sed i-um languorem (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sömnlösheten)</text:span> peperit cibus imperfectus et hærens ardenti stomacho, Juv.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">demonstrativum i mots. till</text:span> hic: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Den; den der,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> stundom i sw. att öfwersätta med en demonstrativ partikel: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">der</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">då:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mots. till det i rummet närwarande l. närmare:</text:span> ad i-ud divinum animorum concilium ex hac turba et colluvione discedam; ex his tenebris in i-am lucem, C.; i-i (Persæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mots. till</text:span> Græci), N.; Ausoniæ pars i-a procul, quam pandit Apollo, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som tillhör annan tid, föregående l. efterföljande: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Den; den förre:</text:span></text:span> hinc i-æ lacrimæ, Ter., Hor.; i-um diem Scipio clarissimum vidit; ea laus non est hominis, sed temporum i-orum; in i-a dictatura scriba, in hac prætor urbanus; horribilem i-um diem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om dödsdagen)</text:span> nobis faustum putemus; quam jucundum i-ud esse debet, quo confecto <text:soft-page-break/>nulla cura reliqua futura sit!; utinam ad i-a tempora me fortuna reservasset, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Den förre, den förstnämnde, den andre</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> hic = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">denne, den sednare, den ene):</text:span> i-ud semel profuit, hoc semper proderit civitati; i-ud animi, hoc etiam ingenii magni est, C.; hunc (juvat), si mobilium turba Quiritium certat tergeminis tollere honoribus: i-um, si proprio condidit horreo, quidquid de Libycis verritur areis, Hor.; modo hi, modo i-i erant in summo fastigio aut periculo, N.; hos, rursus i-os clamore et plausu fovebant, T.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Den bekante, den omtalade</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (den berömde):</text:span> Terentianus i. Chremes; Aristoteles i.; dux i. Græciæ; hæc est i-a pernicies; i-ud Platonis, C.; hoc est i-ud <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det sökta l. omtalade)</text:span> in rerum cognitione frugiferum, omnis te exempli documenta in illustri monumento posita intueri, L.; Ulyssis longus i. et fabulosus error, T.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">antydande ngt följande, som uttryckes i en oberoende l. beroende sats: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Den; den der:</text:span></text:span> i-ud maxime rarum genus est eorum, qui suum quoddam vitæ institutum sequuntur; i-ud odiosum est, quod in magnitudine animi facillime innascitur cupiditas principatus, C.; i-ud in his rebus vereor, ne forte rearis, impia te rationis inire elementa viamque indugredi sceleris, Lucr.; i-a seges demum votis respondet avari agricolæ, bis quæ solem, bis frigora sensit, Vg.; i-ud vereor, ne quos privata Jugurthæ amicitia transvorsos agat, Sa.; N. Thras. I. 1. 5. II. 3.; i-ud ex libertate vitium, quod non conveniunt jussi, T.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jemte ett</text:span> quidem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i concessiva uttryck (i sw. icke öfwersatt, jfr</text:span> quidem): tollenda est malitia, quæ vult i-a q. videri prudentia, sed ab ea abest plurumum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illā</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På den wägen, i den rigtningen:</text:span></text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illātĕnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Så till wida:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Postillā</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sedan deß; sedan den tiden:</text:span></text:span> p. eum nunquam vidi, Pt.; p. te intumum habeo, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illīc</text:span>, illæc, illuc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> illoc, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Pron. demonstr.</text:span> = ille <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> ce <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> hic = hi-ce): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Han</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">den der borta:</text:span></text:span> quis est illæc mulier?; jamjam convenam illunc investigabo; illuc ætatis homo, Pt.; illicine <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= månne den</text:span>)?, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illāc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På den wägen, i den rigtningen:</text:span></text:span> hac an i. eam, nescio, Pt.; hac i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på båda sidor)</text:span> perfluo, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illī</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illīc</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> domi, hic), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Der borta; der</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till</text:span> hic): ut vos hic, ita illi apud vos servatur filius meus; et hic et i. erit mulier; fenus i., fenus hic! nescit quidem nisi fenus fabularier, Pt.; i. (ɔ: in Italia) res lætæ regnumque et regia conjux parta tibi: lacrimas dilectæ pelle Creūsæ, Vg.; nemo i. vitia ridet, neque corrumpere et corrumpi seculum vocatur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illim</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illinc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Derifrån; från</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> eller </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">på andra sidan:</text:span></text:span> i. Gnæum profectum puto, C.; i. beneficium est, Cs.; hinc a porta Collina, i. a Nævia clamor oriebatur, L.; hinc movet Euphrates, i. Germania <text:soft-page-break/>bellum, Vg.; hinc i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från båda sidor)</text:span> mutabile, ut res poscit, remigium, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illō</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illoc</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illuc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Dit, dithän, ditbort, till det andra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">till det förra stället, sidan, ämnet:</text:span></text:span> age tu i-uc procede; ubi i-o adveni, inveni amicam heri, Pt.; nemo i-o adit; hoc i-o pertinet, Cs. b. G. VII. 43.; i-uc (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till ämnet)</text:span> revertor; quum i-o venisset, in vincula est conjectus, N.; huc atque i-uc intuens, C.; i-uc usque tantum natura; diversitas supplicii i. respicit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(syftar derpå),</text:span> tanquam abscondi flagitia, dum puniantur, oporteat; unus supererat Tiberius: i. cuncta vergere, T.; i., heu miseri, traducimur!, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Illecebr . . ., Illectamentum, -lectatio, -lecto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Illicio, Lacio.<text:line-break/>Illectus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lacio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Lĕgo.<text:line-break/>Illex <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Illicio, Lacio.<text:line-break/>Illi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(adv.) se</text:span> Ille.<text:line-break/>Illibatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Libo.<text:line-break/>Illic <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pron. och adv.) se</text:span> Ille.<text:line-break/>Illicet = Ilicet. <text:line-break/>Illicio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lacio.<text:line-break/>Illicitator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Liceo. <text:line-break/>Illicite, -citus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Licet.<text:line-break/>Illicium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Illicio, Lacio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Illĭco,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īlĭco</text:span>, (in loco?), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På stället; der:</text:span></text:span> i. manere, Enn.; sta i.: noli advorsari, neque te occultassis mihi, Pt.; i. consiste, Ter.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Straxt, på stunden:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. temporal mening:</text:span> simul atque increpuit suspicio tumultus, artes nostræ i. conticescunt, C.; Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i slutsats:</text:span> non sequitur i., causas esse immutabiles, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Illido <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lædo.<text:line-break/>Illim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ille. <text:line-break/>Illimatus, -limis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Limus.<text:line-break/>Illinc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ille. <text:line-break/>Illisus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Illido, Lædo.<text:line-break/>Illitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Illino, Lino.<text:line-break/>Illo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Illoc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(adv.) se</text:span> Ille. <text:line-break/>Illotus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lavo.<text:line-break/>Illuc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ille. <text:line-break/>Illumin . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lumen, Luceo.<text:line-break/>Illunis, -lunius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luna.<text:line-break/>Illusio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Illudo, Ludo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Illustris,</text:span> (illuster i <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: Val. Max.), <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> collustro, prælustris, sublustris): p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ljus, klar, lysande, upplyst:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> bona et i-a domicilia; via lata et i. (ɔ: via lactea); stella; sol i-ior, C.; caput, Ov.; die jam i-i procedere, Ct.; nox sideribus i., T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för förståndet) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Klar, tydlig, allmänt begriplig; utredd, utrönt, bekant:</text:span></text:span> nulla sententia i. esse potest sine luce verborum; hæc notiora et i-ora (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">populär, om poesi, i mots. till</text:span> recondita, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om wetenskaper);</text:span> a rebus i-bus et certis cohibere assensum; factum i-e et vetus; res i. et testata, C.; i. ad cognoscendum, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Märkwärdig, märklig:</text:span></text:span> res major et i-or, Cs.; maxime id fuit i-e, quum -, N. (Ep. VlI. 3).<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Lysande, berömd:</text:span></text:span> Themistoclis nomen est, quam Solonis, i-us, C.; famā, Vg.; proelium; legatio, N.; hoc est illud in rerum cognitione frugiferum, omnis te exempli documenta in i-i monumento posita intueri, L.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ansedd, förnäm:</text:span></text:span> homo i. honore et nomine; C.; i-i loco natus, C., Cs.; quanto quis i-or, tanto magis falsi et festinantes, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illustre</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illustrissĭmum</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Berömd bragd:</text:span></text:span> hujus i-mum est proelium apud Platæas, N. -<text:line-break/>(<text:span text:style-name="T1">Illustre</text:span>), <text:line-break/>Illustrius, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tydligare:</text:span></text:span> C.; i-sime, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illustro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Upplysa, bestråla:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> sol cuncta sua luce i-at; templum fulgore auri, C.; maximĕ principum, quā sol habitabiles i-at oras, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bringa i ljuset</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">i dagen; förklara, framställa:</text:span></text:span> omnia Catilinæ consilia per me i-ta, patefacta, comperta sunt; dubia perspicuis i-re; philosophiam literis Latinis, C.; nec me animi fallit Grajorum obscura reperta difficile i-re Latinis versibus esse, Lucr.; quid prius i-em Musa pedestri?, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Pryda, försköna:</text:span></text:span> verba translata orationem i-ant, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Göra berömd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">namnkunnig:</text:span></text:span> injuriæ hominum tuam amplitudinem i-ant, C.; brevi tempore i-tus est (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fick ett namn),</text:span> N.; Musa alqm, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illustrāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Försköningsmedel:</text:span></text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Illustrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Åskådlig framställning:</text:span></text:span> C. ap. Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrillustris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ganska tydlig:</text:span></text:span> N. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mycket berömd:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Illutilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luo.<text:line-break/>Illutus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> Illotus, Lavo.<text:line-break/>Illuvies <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span>lly̆rĭi <text:line-break/>(Illurii, <text:line-break/>Hilurii, Pt.), ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkstam kring Adriatiska hafwet.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Illy̆rĭus, <text:line-break/>Illy̆rĭcus, <text:line-break/>Illy̆ris, ĭdis (<text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Illy̆rĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Illy̆ris, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Illyrien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ilotæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Helotes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span>lva, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö wester om Etrurien (Elba).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>lus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">trojanskt personnamn, (se</text:span> Ilium).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Im <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.</text:span> = eum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span>machăra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Sicilien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Imachărensis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭmāgo,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> imitor): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bild:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sinlig men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bild, afbild, beläte</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt, ware sig naturens werk l. konstens:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> i. Narcissi (in fonte), Ov.; viri picta; ficta; ex ære; muta, C.; Astyanactis i. (Ascanius); Jani bifrontis, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span> (i atrium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uppställd) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Waxbild</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af berömde förfäder, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">anbild,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (anor, namn):</text:span> majorum i-es intueri; homo veteris prosapiæ et multarum i-um, Sa.; jus i-is ad memoriam posteritatemque prodendæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. medföljde curuliskt embete),</text:span> C.; Ancus unā i-e Numæ nobilis fuit; dii te penates - et patris i. - creat vocatque regem; vir honoratissimæ i-is futurus ad posteros, L.; volgus stupet titulis et i-bus, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl. Epicuri system: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bild</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af tinget ss. orsak till förnimmelsen och föreställningen derom:</text:span> i-es (εἴδωλα), quarum incursione non videmus solum, sed etiam cogitamus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skepnad, wålnad, skugga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af en afliden); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">syn:</text:span></text:span> mortuorum, poēt. ap. C.; ipsa in somnis inhumati venit i. conjugis (ad Dido); ter frustra comprensa manus effugit i., Vg.; quietis, T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Genljud, echo:</text:span></text:span> vocis resultat i., Vg.; cujus recinet jocosa nomen i.?, Hor.; laus virtuti resonat tanquam i., C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skapnad, gestalt, form, (sätt):</text:span></text:span> sic, modo quæ fuerat rudis et sine i-e tellus, induit hominum figuras (fingente Prometheo), Ov.; plurima mortis i., Vg.; varia pereuntium forma et omnis i. mortium, T.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildliga uttryck l. i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blott) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bild, skuggbild, skugga, sken</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till werkligheten):</text:span> somnus i. mortis; justitiæ solidam effigiem non habemus: umbris et i-bus utimur; nullam reipublicæ i-em relinquere; judiciorum i. non est in civitate; sive ars est, sive artis i. (rhetorica), non est repudianda, C.; amicitiæ, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bild</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för föreställningen l. minnet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">afbild; inbillning, föreställning:</text:span></text:span> in alienis personis expressam suæ vitæ i-em videre; meorum temporum i-em video in rebus tuis, C.; i-em vitæ Epaminondæ exprimere, N.; i-em cladis furculas Caudinas memorabant, L.; i. periculi oberrat oculis; Ct.; horret animus i-e rei, T.; concipere rei i-em; repræsentare sceleris i-em, Qu.; ulcisci statuit poenæque in i-e tota est, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bild</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">liknelse, jemförelse:</text:span></text:span> i. est formæ cum forma collatio. - - Sic: ibat in proelium corpore tauri, impetu leonis similis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmāgĭnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skenbar, ej werklig; ej äkta; falsk:</text:span></text:span> omnia, quæ sensibus serviunt, i-a sunt; i. paupertas, honor, Sen.; i-is fascibus (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">usurperade och dermed betydelselösa)</text:span> non cedemus, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bär (kejsarens) bild (ss. fälttecken),</text:span> Veg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmāgĭnĭfer</text:span> = imaginarius 2., Veg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmāgĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Afbilda, återgifwa bilden af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> speculum, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmāgĭnor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Föreställa, tänka sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">se i drömmen, drömma:</text:span></text:span> i-are Cæsarem liberti imperio obtemperantem!, Pn. ep.; aliquid per somnia, Pn.; Calpurnia i-ta est, maritum in gremio suo confodi, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmāgĭnābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. föreställer sig, tycker sig se:</text:span> carnificem i-us, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmāgĭnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Föreställning, tanke, phantasi:</text:span></text:span> secretæ, T.; libidinum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmāguncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Liten bild:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭ</text:span>māus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Asien:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Imbēcillus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Imbēcillis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Swag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till kropp l. själ); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">kraft-, makt-, modlös:</text:span></text:span> homo et valetudine et natura i-ior; homo i-us a valentissima bestia laniatur; egentes abundant, i-i valent, mortui vivunt; natura i-a est ad mortem contemnendam; mulier i-i consilii; superstitio i-i animi et anilis; animo et fortunā i., C.; regnum i-um, Sa.; ætas, Hor.; is est i-i ingenio, Pn.; vox i-a, Qu.; <text:span text:style-name="T3">superl.</text:span>: -illimus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och -</text:span> illissimus, Sen. -(-cille), <text:line-break/>Imbēcillius, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: horrere et reformidare alqd; assentiri alicui i-ius, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Imbēcillĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Swaghet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så wäl kroppslig sjuklighet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bräcklighet, wanmakt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som brist på förmögenhet, makt, och moralisk l. intellectuel </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">swaghet:</text:span></text:span> virium; valetudinis; Tulliæ meæ; rerum humanarum; propter i-em desiderata est amicitia; ineunte ætate maxima est i. consilii; susceptum onus propter i-em animi deponere, C.; materiæ; murorum; animi, Cs.; i-is damnare, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrimbēcillus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mycket swag:</text:span></text:span> Varr., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Imbellis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Duellum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Imber,</text:span> bris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Regnskur; stöp-, ös-, hällregn:</text:span></text:span> maximo i-i Capuam veni; magnos i-es habebamus; sæpe lapidum, sanguinis nonnumquam, quondam etiam lactis i. defluxit, C.; largus, Vg., i-e lutoque aspersus; i-es nivesque deducunt Jovem, Hor.; te, janua, verberet i., Tib.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Regnwatten, watten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span> collectos bibere i-es, Hor.; cisternæ servandis i-bus, T.; calidi, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skur, ström,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: nedstörtande massa:</text:span> grandinis, Lucr.; tempestas telorum et ferreus i., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Imbrĭcĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: (cieo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Regnframdrifware</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (-skockare):</text:span> spiritus Austri i., Enn.; Jupiter, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Imbrĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Regnig, regnbringande:</text:span></text:span> Auster, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Imbrĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> = imbricus: ver, Vg.; Auster, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Imberbis, -berbus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Barba.<text:line-break/>Imbito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Beto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span>mbrăsus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. nom. propr.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Imbrăsĭdes. ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronymicum.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Imbrex,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.,</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">m.,</text:span> Pn.):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Takpanna, hwälfd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hålkad) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">taksten,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. betäckte de platte stenarnes</text:span> (tegularum) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fogningar (enl.</text:span> Isid. ”quod accipiant imbres”): tempestas confregit tegulas i-esque, Pt.; servari inter duos i-es, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ränna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af takpannor:</text:span> Col., Cato.<text:line-break/>c. i. porci <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ett serskildt stycke på swinet):</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/>d. plausus genus: Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Imbrĭcātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hålkad, hwälfd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som en takpanna:</text:span> vertebra; unguis, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Imbrĭcātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Imbricitor, -bricus, -brifer <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Imber.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span>mbros, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö i Aegeiska hafwet.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Imbrĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Imbuo,</text:span> ui, ūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beslägtadt med</text:span> bibo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Indoppa (inbyra); wäta, fukta, bestänka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (-sudla):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> lanam coloribus, Col.; gladios, viam sanguine alicujus, C.; sanguis arma i-it, Vg.; quo semel est i-ta recens, servabit odorem testa diu, Hor.; tela veneno i-ta; vestem sanguine i., Ov.; manus sanguine i-re, Vell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inwiga, införa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (indränka) i; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wänja wid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">underwisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= gifwa den första underwisningen), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hemmastadd i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">förtrogen med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> an tu dialecticis ne i-tus quidem es?; ad hanc legem non instituti, sed i-ti sumus; tinctus literis, aliquo i-tus usu, C.; illa (navis) rudem cursu primum i-it Amphitriten, Catl.; literulis Græcis i-tus, Hor.: certaminibus plebejis jam a juventa i-tus, L.; literis saltem i-tus, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(moraliskt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppfylla; genomtränga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om känslor, intryck o. s. w.); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">smitta:</text:span></text:span> superstitione; bonis opinionibus; parentum præceptis; nulla gens est, cujus mentem non i-erit aliqua deorum opinio, C.; animus i-tus malis artibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det onda),</text:span> Sa.; pectora pietate; animum errore, L.; aures alicujus honestis sermonibus, T.; gladium scelere, C.; legiones favore Othonis, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭmĭtor,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dep.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Ĭmĭto, 1.: Liv. Andr., Varr.):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Söka att likna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">efterlikna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i yttre l. inre men.), så wäl (göra efter) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">härma,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">följa, efterfölja, bilda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig efter ngn:</text:span> amictum, statum, motum alicujus; verbis et sono aliquem; chirographum alicujus; alquem sibi proponere ad i-dum; i-di sunt majores; etiam vitia alcujus; i. et exprimere aliquem; i-da consuetudo medicorum est; hoc faciendum i-dumque est omnibus, C.; celeritatem alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ngn i -),</text:span> Cs.; gestum alicujus, Lucr.; sonum, mores alicujus, Ct.; vulpes leonem, Hor.; turdus sermonem, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om konstnärer och konstwerk: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fram-, föreställa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eftergöra), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bilda;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i prægn. mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">fullkomligt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (adæquat) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">framställa, träffa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ett original), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">upphinna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ett ideal):</text:span> qui actor i-dā, quam orator suscipiendā veritate jucundior?; heroum casus fictosque luctus i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">scenen),</text:span> C.; ære capillos; argillā alqd, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="T3">part. pass.</text:span>: simulacra i-ata, C.; Canăchi signa rigidiora sunt, quam ut i-entur veritatem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wara natursanna);</text:span> summum illum luctum penicillo non poterat i-ri; oris pulcritudo reliqui corporis i-di spem auferebat, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: om sakliga subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Härma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">likna, wara lik:</text:span></text:span> casus i-atur veritatem, C.; flammas i-atur pyropus, Ov.; terra ita pura et splendens, ut picturam i-etur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmĭtābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Efterliknelig; lätt att efterlikna; som kan efterliknas:</text:span></text:span> subtilitas oratoris, C.; Jovis non i-e fulmen, Vg.; decipit exemplar vitiis i-e, Hor.; smaragdus, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmĭtāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmĭtāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Försök att efterlikna,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">föreställa; efterliknande:</text:span></text:span> peractis tristitiæ i-tis, T.; æra Corybantes movent, prisci i-na facti; somnia veras æquant i-ne formas, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Bemödande att likna; efterliknande, -följande; härmande:</text:span></text:span> virtus i-e digna; consequi alqd i-e; factorum meorum i. ad te pertinet; prodere alicui periculosam exempli i-em; similitudinem alicujus i-e assequi; depravata i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(karrikering),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmĭtātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Efterliknare, -följare; efterapare; härmare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. har förmåga att härma andres tal, sätt o. s. w.):</text:span> moris majorum; studiorum meorum, C.; Atticorum, Qu.; o i-es, servum pecus, Hor.; natura - creat i-es et narratores facetos, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭmĭtātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Efterliknerska, -aperska; härmerska:</text:span></text:span> gloriæ se vult i-em esse fama popularis, C.; psittacus Eois i. ales ab Indis, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnĭmĭtābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Oefterliknelig:</text:span></text:span> opus, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Imitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Infer.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Immānis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ofantlig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s.öfwergår wanligt, menskligt mått) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">understor, wäldig, jättestor, bålstor:</text:span></text:span> pecunia; jactura; quæstus; ambitus; præda, C.; corporum i. magnitudo, Cs.; cæli templa i-ia, Lucr.; avaritia, Sa.; moles; saxa; templa; antrum; hydrus, Vg.; i-ia Cæsaris facta celebrare, Ov.; res i-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(storwerk),</text:span> Vell.; vitium; i-e quantum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> mirum quantum) discrepat, Hor.; i-e dictu, Sa.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wild, barbarisk; gräslig:</text:span></text:span> pace parta conservandi sunt, qui in bello non i-es fuerunt; belua; hostis; natio fera et i.; natura i. et inhumana; i-simus quisque, C.; animo i-is, Ov.; ora; i-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wild)</text:span> in antro bacchatur vates; monstrum; scelere ante alios i-ior omnes, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Immāne</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Immānĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ofantligt; gräsligt;</text:span></text:span> Vg., Gell., Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Immānĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ofantlighet:</text:span></text:span> pretii, Pn.; frigoris, Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wildhet, råhet, grymhet, omensklighet:</text:span></text:span> eorum i. detestabilis, qui omni scelere lacerarunt patriam; ista in figura hominis feritas et i. beluæ; naturæ; barbara vitiorum; facinŏris, C.; sceleris, Sa.; ferarum, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Immens . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Metior.<text:line-break/>Immersabilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Immergo, Mergo.<text:line-break/>Immetatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Metor, Metior.<text:line-break/>Immiss . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Immitto, Mitto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Immo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(īmo), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i inkast eller i swar på egna l. andres frågor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fastmer, twärtom</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ja eller nej); ofta tillsammans med</text:span> vero, certe, etiam:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nej; (nej) twärtom; nej fastmer; nej, utan:</text:span></text:span> esse ergo eos dicis? - i. quia non sunt, eo miseros esse; quid opus fuit <text:span text:style-name="T3">de</text:span>? i. vero, quid opus fuit <text:span text:style-name="T3">te</text:span>?; num Romæ fuit? i. longe abfuit; silebitne filius? i. vero obsecrabit patrem, ne id faciat; vicit ergo utilitas honestatem? i. vero honestatem consecuta est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blef en följd af -)</text:span> utilitas; i. vero rogemus Antonium, C.; quid tibi hic negotist? i. quid tibi?; fatetur etiam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ännu)?</text:span> i. pernegat, Pt.; quod optimum esse dicunt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwad beträffar deras påstående att),</text:span> nihil interponi vos bello, nihil i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(twärtom)</text:span> tam alienum vestris rebus est, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i swar på en fråga, s. utsäges med förwåning, l. på en negativ sats: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Io; ja; jo wisserligen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (men):</text:span> hoc quid ad me? - i. ad te pertinet, Pt.; non igitur patria præstat omnibus officiis? i. vero, sed ipsi patriæ conducit cives habere pios in parentes; non bona est igitur causa? i. optima; hic tamen etiam vivit. - Vivit? i. vero etiam in senatum venit, C.; nullane habes vitia? i. alia et fortasse minora, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(der ett uttryck rättas såsom för swagt, sål. genom att sätta ett starkare i stället): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Nej; ja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till och med; (hos sednare förff. tillsammans med</text:span> quin): omnium rerum libertatem, i. licentiam desiderant; simulacra deûm, i. dii ipsi; vide, ne in æquo hostes sint - ac nos -, i. ne meliore jure sint, L.; sermo Græcus, i. Atticus, Pn. ep.; pigrum quin i. et iners videtur sudore acquirere, quod possis sanguine parare, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Immoenis = Immunis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Munia. <text:line-break/>Immolatio, -lator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Immolo, Molo. <text:line-break/>Immolitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Molior, Moles.<text:line-break/>Immorsus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mordeo.<text:line-break/>Immunis, -nĭtas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Munia. <text:line-break/>Immunītus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Moenia.<text:line-break/>Imo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Immo. <text:line-break/>Impactio, -pages <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Impingo, Pango <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under</text:span> Pago.<text:line-break/>Imparilis, -parilitas, -pariter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Impar, Par.<text:line-break/>Impastus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pasco.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Impĕdio,</text:span> 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af samma stam s.</text:span> (compes?), expedio, præpedio): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inweckla, omweckla, -linda; insnärja:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> sese in plagas, Pt.; ingentem clipeum informant - septenosque orbibus orbes i-unt, Vg.; cornua sertis, Ov.; caput viridi myrto, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">In-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">omweckla:</text:span></text:span> curæ me i-unt; se nuptiis impedire, Ter.; me quotidie aliud ex alio i-it, sed si me expedivero, ibo; causam interrogationibus; ipsum suā stultitiā, sua defensione i-ri, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hindra, förhindra:</text:span></text:span> nihil i-o; iter alicujus; discendi studio i-ti eos deserunt, quos tueri debent; i-ri fletu, pudore, curis, morbo, occupationibus; ab omni delectatione i-imur negotiis; a republica bene gerenda i-ri; pudor me i-it exquirere; nihil i-it, quominus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> quin facias; casus i-vit, ne id facerem, Cs.; Euryalum tenebræ prædaque i-unt, Vg.; navigatio, prospectus i-itur; alqm in jure suo, ad capiendam fugam i-re, Cs.; celeritatem alicujus; non i., quominus, N.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ställen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Göra swårtillgänglig:</text:span></text:span> palus locum, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕdītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer och deras lemmar, sinnen, tankar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Upptagen, sysselsatt, ej ledig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (spec. = ej stridsfärdig):</text:span> omnium animis i-is, Cs.; i-os itinere hostes aggredi, Cs.; agmen, L.; malis domesticis i.; ad iter faciendum i-simus, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker (spec. om ställen): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Swår, brydsam, beswärlig, obeqwäm, swårtillgänglig:</text:span></text:span> silva, palus i-a; locus i-ior, Cs.; tempora i-a reipublicæ; magnus et i. et muliebris comitatus; nomina <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skulder),</text:span> C.; quid horum non i-simum?, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕdīmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hinder:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> esse alicui i-o; inferre alicui i.; naturæ i-a diligentiā superare, C.; Gallis magno ad pugnam fuit i-o, quod - - non poterant, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Troß</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lastdjur och troßknektar inberäknade):</text:span> obviam ei fit Clodius in equo, nulla rheda, nullis i-is, C.; ad i-a se conferre; i-a abdere, diripere, amittere, recipere; i-is potiri, Cs.; magna pars i-orum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lastdjur)</text:span> ceciderant, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕdītio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hindrande, hinder:</text:span></text:span> liber ab omni i-e curarum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕdĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hindra:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pĕrimpĕdītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mycket swårtillgänglig:</text:span></text:span> locus, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Impedo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pes.<text:line-break/>Impendio, -diosus, -dium, Impens . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Impendo, Pendo. <text:line-break/>Imperat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Impero.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Imperceptus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: (percipio, capio): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Oupptäckt:</text:span></text:span> fraus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Imperco</text:span>, ĕre: (parco): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Skona, spara:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Imperialis, -periose, -periosus, -perĭto, -perium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Impero.<text:line-break/>Imperīte, -rītia, -rītus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Perior.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Impĕro,</text:span> 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Befalla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. husbonde, makt- l. befälhafwande) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ålägga, beordra; gifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någon </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ordres, befallning; tillsäga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någon om ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">alicui aliquid</text:span>):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> i-a, si quid vis, Pt.; puerperæ alqd; i., quid opus sit facto, Ter.; domi nihil i-aram; coenam famulo i-re, C.; i-tum, i-ta facere, Cs.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">inf.</text:span>: i-vi mihimet omnia assentari, Ter.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">acc. cum inf.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pass.</text:span>): tabulas describi - et pervulgari i-vi, C.; legiones - proficisci i-at, Cs.; hæc ego procurare i-or, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">conj.</text:span>-<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sats:</text:span> legatis i-at, ut naves ædificandas curarent; Cæsar suis i-vit, ne quod omnino telum in hostes rejicerent; huic i-at - adeat civitates, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.:</text:span> i. (<text:span text:style-name="T3">alicui</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="T3">aliquid</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Befalla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn att </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">utgöra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (en afgift) l. att </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ställa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (manskap); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ålägga, fordra:</text:span></text:span> prætor remiges, pecuniam in remiges; frumentum sibi in cellam, C.; civitatibus arma, naves, equites, obsides; equites Galliæ i-ti, Cs.; Jugurthæ argentum, Sa.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> sola terræ seges i-atur, T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om jord l. andra afkastning lemnande föremål: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Suga, pressa, fresta:</text:span></text:span> agris, Vg.; vitibus, Col.; fertilibus agris non est i-dum, Sen.; <text:soft-page-break/>voci, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Herrska, wara herre:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> i-at aut servit collecta pecunia cuique, Hor.; liberis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(frie),</text:span> Ter.; cupiditatibus, quibus ceteri serviunt, i-bat; sibi ipsi, C.; animo i-re nequivi, quin -, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i civil l. militär mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Herrska, regera; föra befälet:</text:span></text:span> qui bene i-et, prius pareat necesse est; omnibus gentibus terrā ac mari i-re, C.; Ariovistus superbe et crudeliter; sic se complures annos illo i-ante meruisse, ut -, Cs.; crudeliter, N. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i serskildaste mening, om Roms imperatorer (kejsare): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wara sjelfherrskare; regera:</text:span></text:span> Galba - omnium consensu capax imperii, nisi i-asset; ea est condicio i-di, ut non aliter ratio constet, quam si uni reddatur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕrātīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Befalld, föreskrifwen:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Som utmärker befallning:</text:span></text:span> modus, Gramm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕrātor</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(arch.</text:span> induperator, endoperator), ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har att befalla:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Herre, herrskare:</text:span></text:span> Jupiter, qui est i. divom atque hominum; i. familiæ, Pt.; tria signa Jovis I-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ss. tillnamn);</text:span> populus Romanus victor atque i. omnium gentium, C.; dux et i. vitæ mortalium animus est, Sa.; vitæ, et necis i., Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwerbefälhafware, fältherre:</text:span></text:span> i. est administrator belli gerendi; (Regulus victus est) duce Xanthippo, i-e autem Hamilcare; quis est, qui - non anteponat oratori i-em?; bonus et fortis; callidus et sapiens; iidem labores non æque graves sunt i-i et militi, C.; magnus, summus i.; alqm sibi i-em sumere, N.; i. (Scipio) omnes fere res asperas per Jugurtham agebat; novo i-i plus ex moribus militum sollicitudinis, quam ex copia - spei bonæ accedebat, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hederstitel för en segrande fältherre (segerherre):</text:span> eo proelio Pompejus i. est appellatus; universi exercitus conclamatione i. appellatur, Cs.; M. Tull. Cicero I., C.; i. est, qui - oppressit hostes, Varr.; (ab Augusto) nomen i-is semel et vicies partum, T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Imperator</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = romerska rikets sjelfherrskare, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">kejsare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sättes då före namnet):</text:span> Janus clausus est ab i-e Cæsare Augusto, pace terra marique parta, L.; leviore flagitio legatum (Cæsaris) interficietis, quam ab i-e desciscitis; tres et viginti speculatores Othonem consalutant i-em; Valens cum equitibus - - i-em Vitellium consalutavit; Vitellius tribuno insultanti se tamen i-em ejus fuisse respondit, T.<text:line-break/>d. = rex Romæ: omnibu’ cura viris, uter esset induperator, Enn. Ann. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕrātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillhör l. anstår fältherre, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fältherre-:</text:span></text:span> nomen; jus; laus, C.; forma, N.; artes, L.; navis, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillhör kejsare, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kejserlig:</text:span></text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕrātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Herrskarinna:</text:span></text:span> Italia (gentium), Pn.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">befälhafwerska:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på spe),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕrĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T3">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Befalla; herrska, beherrska; föra befäl, regering:</text:span></text:span> æquam rem i-o, Hor.; - plerāque Africā Carthaginienses i-bant; naturam ceteris i-antem vincere, Sa.; Albæ Cluilius; decem i-<text:soft-page-break/>bant, unus cum insignibus imperii erat; victis superbe i-re, L.; magnis legionibus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Befallning, bud, maktspråk, (commando, ordres):</text:span></text:span> heri i. exsequi, Pt.; i-o parere, obtemperare; i. negligere, Cs.; accipere, L.; exspectare, detrectare i-a, Ct.; i-o Jovis huc venio, Vg.; i. observare, signa sequi milites decet, Sa. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Makt, wälde, styrelse:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> is errat, qui credit i. stabilius esse, quod vi fit, quam quod amicitiā injungitur, Ter.; facile est i. in bonos, Pt.; habere, tenere i. in alqm, Ter., C.; esse sub i-o matris, Ter.; i. domesticum (in servulos), C.; regum timendorum in proprios greges, reges in ipsos i. est Jovis, Hor.; nostra omnis vis in animo et corpore sita est: animi i-o, corporis servitio magis utimur, Sa.; <text:span text:style-name="T3">plur.</text:span>: (Jupiter) qui res hominum atque deorum æternis regis i-is, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk. i civil l. militär men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Regering</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i och för sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">styrelse, makten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i samhället; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">styrelseform:</text:span></text:span> i. semper ad optimum quemque a minus bono transfertur, Sa.; i-a legum potentiora, quam regum, L.; expertem esse i-i, consilii publici, judicii, C.; in terris nomen i-i id (regium) primum fuit, Sa.; i. singulare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enwälde),</text:span> C.; regium i., Sa.; i-um regit Dido, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Herrskare-, regeringsmakt, högsta makten, regering</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. utöfwad af en person, i monarchi l. fristat:</text:span> perpetua urbium i-a; i. perpetuo obtinebat (Chersonesi Miltiades), N.; Tullus Hostilius de i-o suo - populum consuluit curiatim; contra consulare i-um tribuni plebis constituti; de i-o legem curiatam tulit; aliquo honore aut i-o affectum esse; Hortensius tum consul erit cum summo i-o et potestate; in urbibus Græciæ cum summo i-o et potestate versari <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ss. proconsul),</text:span> C. - summum imperium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillkom i strängaste mening blott konungar och dictatorer, en consul blott utom staden och ss.</text:span> i. militare.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Befäl, högsta befälet, commando-post</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid arméen (i motsats till</text:span> honores <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> potestas): - secundæ res, honores, i-a, victoriæ fortuita sunt; nec vero i-a expetenda, sed potius aut non accipienda, aut deponenda nonnunquam, C.; i. committere, abrogare alicui; summa i-i traditur alicui, est penes aliquem; præesse summæ i-i; versari in i-is, N.; Tiberius egregius vitā famāque, quoad privatus vel in i-is sub Augusto fuit, T.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">concr.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Befälsperson:</text:span></text:span> Cs.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Imperators-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">kejsaremakten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (thronen):</text:span> etiam tu (Galba) i. degustabis; (Augusto) idem dies accepti i-i princeps et vitæ supremus; Nero i. per scelus adeptus est, T.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett folks l. en furstes </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Öfwer-, herrawälde</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (öfwerhöghet), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wälde</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer andra folk l. furstar (äfwen i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span>): cum Pyrrho de i-o dimicatum, decertatum est; ei bello i-i gloria proposita fuit; i. populi Romani beneficiis, non injuriis tenebatur; i-o omnium gentium constituto; sub i-um populi Romani cadere, C.; sub alicujus dicione et i-o esse; i-o potiri, Cs.; Roma domicilium orbis terrarum i-i; Corcyram sub i-um Atheniensium Timotheus redegit, N.; gentes humanæ æquo animo i. (Romanum) patiuntur; cupido i-i duos cognatos - populos ad arma stimulat, L.; inimici i. deprecor; i-a ejus <text:soft-page-break/>injusta, superba, crudelia barbari pati nequiverunt, Sa.; præstat - Gallorum quam Romanorum i-a perferre; non posse se Ariovisti) i-a diutius sustinere; novis i-is (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förändring i)</text:span> studere, Cs.<text:line-break/>g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett öfwer andra folk herrskande folks </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Egowälde, rike, besittningar:</text:span></text:span> Pausaniæ rebus gestis i. Lacedæmonis dilatatum putatur; rempublicam augere i-o, agris, vectigalibus; duæ urbes huic i-o inimicissimæ; hujus urbis et i-i interitus, C.; eum locum finem i-i habuere Carthaginienses; maximam gloriam in maximo i-o putare, Sa.; populus Atheniensis postquam majus i. adeptus est - -, N.; nascetur Cæsar - -, i-um Oceano, famam qui terminet astris, Vg.; mari Oceano aut longinquis amnibus sæptum i. (Romanum); Batavi pars i-i Romani; si immensum i-i corpus stare ac librari sine rectore posset, dignus eram, a quo res publica inciperet, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕriālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Kejserlig:</text:span></text:span> majestas; ornamenta: Cap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Impĕriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har stor makt l. stort wälde, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Mäktig:</text:span></text:span> i-i populi et reges illustres, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sträng, myndig, despotisk, tyrannisk:</text:span></text:span> consul, domina; i-i philosophi est vetare meminisse, C.; dictatura; familia i-sissima, L.; quisnam igitur liber? - sibi qui i-us; me trahit i-a Proserpina; i-ius æquor, Hor.; inedia, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Imperiōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Myndigt; tyranniskt:</text:span></text:span> præcipere, Gell.; interimere, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Impertio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pars.<text:line-break/>Impervius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Via. <text:line-break/>Impes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Peto.<text:line-break/>Impetibilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Patior.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Impĕtīgo,</text:span> ĭnis <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ref-orm, utslag:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Impetr . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Patro.<text:line-break/>Impetus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Peto. <text:line-break/>Impexus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pecto.<text:line-break/>Impico <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pix. <text:line-break/>Impigre, -pigritas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Impiger, Piget. <text:line-break/>Impilia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pileus.<text:line-break/>Impingo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pango, Pago <text:line-break/>Implexus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Implecto, II. Plecto. <text:line-break/>Implic . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Plico.<text:line-break/>Implumis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pluma. <text:line-break/>Impluviatus, -pluvium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pluo. <text:line-break/>Impollutus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Polluo, Luo.<text:line-break/>Importun . . ., Importuosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Portus.<text:line-break/>Impos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Potis. <text:line-break/>Imposit . . ., Impost . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Impono, Pono.<text:line-break/>Impræsentiarum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Præsens, Sum. <text:line-break/>Impransus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Prandeo.<text:line-break/>Impressio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Imprimo, Premo.<text:line-break/>lmprimis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Primus 5. C.<text:line-break/>Improfessus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Profiteor, Fateor. <text:line-break/>Impromptus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Promo, Emo.<text:line-break/>Improvide, -vidus, -visus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Provideo, Video. <text:line-break/>Impuls . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Impello, Pello.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Impun . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Poena.<text:line-break/>Imulus, Imus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Infer.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭn,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Præp.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(arch.:</text:span> indu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> endo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen i sammansättningar, såsom</text:span> indugredi, Lucr., endoperator, Enn., Juv.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I; på; till:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>A. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">abl.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om rummet:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I, på, (ibland, inom):</text:span></text:span> est in urbe, Ter.; in hac civitate; in scena; in capite, C.; in oppido; in statione; in Sequanis, in Treveris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i deras land);</text:span> in milibus passuum tribus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inom, på en omkrets af),</text:span> Cs.; pontem fecit in Hellesponto, N.; stans celsa in puppi, Vg.; stans pede in uno, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hit hör ock:</text:span> est in conspectu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inom synhåll)</text:span> Tenedos, Vg.; in oculis duo navigia submersa sunt, Ct.;<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Wid:</text:span></text:span> Edonis fessa choreis qualis in herboso concidit Apidano, Ppt. I. 3. 5. 6.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. wid verba, som egentl. utmärka en rörelse l. werksamhet i rummet, brukade i oegentlig bet.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I; på:</text:span></text:span> versari in republica; curam, diligentiam, spem ponere in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nedlägga, bygga på)</text:span> re; habere alqd in animo; hærere in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla sig wid)</text:span> causa; multitudo in omni genere causarum; hæc jura civilia - jam pridem in nostra familia versantur (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillhöra; idkas inom),</text:span> C.; spem positam habere in aliquo, N. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I, wid, på, under</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wanl. om en tidpunkt, under en tidrymd); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">om</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wid</text:span> adverbia numeralia): Cato habebat in senectute cognomen sapientis; in hoc tempore; mortem contemnendam esse in tam longa ætate non vidit; in hoc anno; nihil in vita Antonii simile fecit; in præsenti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för närwarande);</text:span> in tempore <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på rätt tid),</text:span> C.; in hora ducentos versus faciebat, Hor.; bis in die; ter in anno, C.; in quo facto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(härunder)</text:span> revocatur), N.; in itinere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under tåget),</text:span> Cs.; in brevi spatio, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ibland</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett antal, en klaß:</text:span> tu es in principibus; mors in malis est; in his (fuerunt) et nobilissimi philosophi - et principes in civitate viri, C.; omnibus fere vulneratis, in his P. Sextio, Cs.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Hos, i,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på, med; om egenskaper, känslor, omständigheter o. s. w. hos en person l. sak):</text:span> probitatem in hoste etiam diligimus; in aliis facilius, quam in nobismetipsis, cernimus, si quid delinquitur; erat in Crasso multus lepos; ut nihil boni est in morte, sic certe nihil mali; tantum est in excellente oratore ornamenti civitati, C.; in amore sunt hæc: pax, bellum rursus etc., Ter.; tanta erat in iis firmitudo, Cs. - tu nihil in magno reprendis Homero?; est in juvencis, est in equis vigor paternus, Hor. <text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I, under, wid, i och med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett tillstånd l. en handling, händelse:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. in omnium rerum abundantia vivere; in rebus prosperis, secundissimis; in amplissimis fortunis mori; in utraque fortuna gravem se in amicitia præstitit; in silenti o jacere; in cursu, in studio, in vitio, in imperio esse; in liberis populis et in juris æquabilitate exercenda est altitudo animi; in hac reipublicæ pernicie; in morte finis miseriæ; in morte evolat animus ex vinculis corporis; solebat doctoribus ea ponere in percontando, C.; in mea in juria vos despecti estis, Sa.; in consulatu; rem esse in angusto vidit; etiam in extremis suis rebus operam navare cupiebant, Cs.; in convivio; in summo timore, N.; res est in dubio; spes erat in cursu, nunc lare pulsa suo est, Ov.; in pace; in funere<text:span text:style-name="T3">;</text:span> fecundi calices quem non fecere <text:soft-page-break/>disertum, contracta quem non in paupertate solutum?; res est in ambiguo, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med causal l. concessiv bibetydelse:</text:span> in maxima discentium multitudine; maximis in malis hoc boni assecuti esse videmur; ne id quidem effecerunt, quod in tanto otio assequi potuerunt, C.; in tanta rerum iniquitate - eventus varii sequebantur; singulari militum studio in summa inopia, Cs.; meo sum pauper in ære <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fattig, dock utan skuld),</text:span> Hor.; quidam, ut in licentia vetustatis, plures deo ortos adfirmant; habitus corporum, quamquam in tanto hominum numero, idem omnibus, T.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> något hänseende; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">i fråga om;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (förfarande) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">med afseende på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mot):</text:span> in dicendo admirabilem exsistere; homo in quærendo diligens, in testimonio religiosus; cupidus in rerum natura cognoscenda; in hoc sumus sapientes, quod -, C.; in verbis etiam tenuis cautusque serendis, Hor.; in minoribus navigiis rudem esse; quidam in parva pecunia perspiciuntur, quam sint leves; qui clamores in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid, öfwer)</text:span> Pacuvii nova fabula!; quid - effecerint in Scipione, sine lacrimis vix queo dicere; hoc in veris et certis patribus multo magis est faciendum; in utroque (homine) eandem fortuna habuit potestatem, usa est in altero; quid opus est in hoc philosophari?, C.; peccare in aliquo; in agris vastandis nocere hostibus, Cs.; foeda facinora in civibus facere, Sa.; peccare in matrona; laborare in (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">brinna för)</text:span> uno, Hor.<text:line-break/>7. ponere, ducere in vitio = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Räkna för:</text:span></text:span> C.; ponere alqd in discrimine ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">anse något för att göra ngt till saken, lägga wigt på,</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>B. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">acc.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fråga om rummet:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Till, in i, i, in på:</text:span></text:span> faces in Capitolium ferre; dux in cælum mors; in carcerem se includere, C.; Ilium in Italiam portans, Vg.; in agrum Noricum transire, Cs.; in flumen conjicere; in agros Romanos incursionem facere, L.; in mare decidit, Ov.; gestit numos in loculos demittere, Hor.; venit in exsequias tota caterva meas, Ppt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utm. en rigtning </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Åt, mot; på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i fråga om dimensioner):</text:span> in forum versus, C.; Belgæ spectant in septentrionem; flumen in utram partem fluat, judicari non potest; in eam partem ire, Cs.; densos ruit in hostes; gemini minantur in cælum scopuli, Vg.; fines Helvetiorum in longitudinem milia passuum CCXL patebant, Cs.; trecentos pedes in agrum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inåt fältet)</text:span> cippus dabat, Hor. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I, på,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om den del l. sida af ett föremål, som träffas af en inwerkan, på hwilken man faller o. s. w.:</text:span> cuspide montem impulit in latus; volvitur in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på)</text:span> caput, Vg.; in cubitum se reponere, Hor.; in dextram, in utramvis aurem dormire, Ter., Pn. - assurgere in clipeum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med lyftad sköld),</text:span> Vg.; in eversum equum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ofwanpå)</text:span> fundere alqm, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fråga om tid:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Till:</text:span></text:span> in posterum diem invitare alqm; earum rerum consolatio est in aliud tempus differenda, C.; in crastinum differo res severas; in diem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till l. att betala på en wiß dag)</text:span> emere aliquid, N.; (librum) nonum premere in annum; nec dulcia differ in annum, Hor. stertere in lucem, Ps.; in lucem lucernas perferre, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">För</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wid bestämningar, som omfatta en wiß tid, l. i distributiva uttryck):</text:span> amicitia bona spe in posterum prælucet; in omne tempus <text:soft-page-break/>reipublicæ suisque consulere; in perpetuum; in præsens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för det närwarande);</text:span> barbarorum est in diem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för dagen)</text:span> vivere: nostra consilia sempiternum tempus spectare debent; in horam vivere, C.; in dies, in horas addiscere alqd, mutari <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för l. med hwarje dag l. timma),</text:span> C., Hor.; in proximum annum consulatum petere, Sa.; monet eum, ut in reliquum tempus omnes suspiciones vitet; hostium numerus in dies augebatur, Cs.; in præsens tempus omittere alqd, Hor.; in præsentia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för närwarande,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">acc. pl. neutr.</text:span>), N. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om andra förhållanden:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Till, i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett tillstånd, ställning, handling, beskaffenhet o. s. w.:</text:span> in matrimonium ducere aliquem; in fidem recipere; in invidiam, odium venire <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ådraga sig);</text:span> in luctus, sermonem incidere; in invidiam vocare alqm, C.; venire in contemptionem, Cs.; in villos abeunt vestes, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">I</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en rigtning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">åt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett håll, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en sida:</text:span> præcepta, quibus usus vitæ in omnes partes conformari potest; disputare in utramque partem; in contrarias partes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för och emot);</text:span> in sententiam aliquam; in bonam partem accipere alqd; multi in hanc partem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i denna rigtning)</text:span> principum facta imitantur; in optimam partem cognoscuntur adolescentes, qui se ad probatos viros contulerunt, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sätt l. wilkor; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">i, till</text:span></text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så att ett sätt följes, ett tillstånd l. en bestämning uppkommer):</text:span> servilem in modum cruciari; villæ in urbium modum ædificatæ; id erit mihi in majorem modum gratum; peto in majorem modum, C.; in has leges data pax, L.; patiens admirandum in modum, N.; in eam sententiam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i den syftningen)</text:span> disputare, Cs.; juremus in hoc; jurare in verba alicujus, Hor.; in orbem consistere; in chori speciem ludere, Ov.; somnia in faciem meam credita, Ppt.; certatum totis concussi viribus orbis in commune nefas, Luc.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fördela) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">På;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (dela) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">i:</text:span></text:span> prædam socios partitur in omnes, Vg.; Gallia est divisa in partes tres, Cs.; omnis oratoris vis ac facultas in quinque partes distribuitur; causas in plura genera secuerunt, C.; pars in frusta secant (carnem), Vg.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Till,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> utmärkande en bestämmelse l. afsigt; (bestämning) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn l. ngt:</text:span> nasci in miseriam sempiternam; pecunia in rem militarem data, C.; in eam rem fidem suam interponere, Cs.; ædificare in spem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för, på</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i hoppet) -,</text:span> L.; in commune consulere; in universum æstimanti plus in pedite roboris, T.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sinnesstämning, handlingssätt, yttrande) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">mot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om):</text:span> in alqm talem esse, qualis ipse ille est; multa commemorare nefaria in socios; pietas in matrem, liberalitas in sorores, bonitas in suos, justitia in omnes, in rempublicam merita; severe inquirere in se ipsum; illud, quod a Platone dictum est in philosophos, C.; odio ferri in alqm, N., Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">In</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sammansättning:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Præp.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">in, i, på, ss.</text:span> induco, incido, impono, induo.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med upphäfwande betydelse liks. det sw. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">O-, miß-.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Præp.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stundom ställd efter sin casus): (af</text:span> in, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som</text:span> subter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> sub): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Imellan, ibland:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg., i rummet:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Imellan:</text:span></text:span> i. manus auferri, C.; ager est i. urbem et Fidenas, L.; <text:soft-page-break/>inter utrumque tene <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(styr!),</text:span> Ov.; terras i. et cælum volare, Vg.; Judæam i. et Syriam, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ibland,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> inne emellan l. ibland:</text:span> i. arma silent leges; i. hostium tela versari; i. homines esse desiit; hi tres libri i. Cratippi commentarios tanquam hospites erunt recipiendi, C.; i. equites proeliari, Cs.; flammam i. et hostes expedior: dant tela locum flammæque recedunt, Vg.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Imellan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om ett förhållande af likhet l. olikhet, strid l. wänskap o. s. w.):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> nuper hæc i. nos notitia est, Ter.; i. hominem et beluam hoc maxime interest; benevolentia maxime elucet i. æquales; beneficiis ii, i. quos sunt, firmā devinciuntur societate; hos i. societas est; i. Africanum et Metellum fuit sine acerbitate dissensio; i. omnes constat, C.; quos i. medius venit furor, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt märkes:</text:span> inter se = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Sinsemellan, inbördes;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i sw. ofta = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hwarandra:</text:span></text:span> i. se amare, diligere, colere, aspicere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(älska etc. hwarandra);</text:span> homines nati sunt, ut i. se alii aliis prodesse possent, C.; obtrectarunt i. se, N. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ibland</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ett antal, en klaß);</text:span> i. hos Galba præstitit eloquentiā; i. primores mox venit, L.; vir i. suos honestissimus), C.; plurimum i. Belgas Bellovaci virtute valent, Cs.; i. quos referendus erit? veteresne poētas an quos et præsens et postera respuit ætas?, Hor.; gens allecta i. Romanas, Su. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid och tillstånd:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Imellan:</text:span></text:span> i. Valerii primum et tertium consulatum XIV interfuerunt anni, C.; i. Lavinium et Albam deductam XXX interfuere anni, L.; spemque metumque i. dubii, Vg.; non mea mutata est ætas, sine crimine tota est: viximus egregie i. utramque facem (ɔ: nuptialem et funebrem), Ppt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Under; ibland:</text:span></text:span> omnia commemorabuntur, quæ i. X annos nefarie facta sunt; hæc dictavi i. coenam; i. viam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under resan)</text:span> agere alqd, C.; bina spolia i. tot annos, tot bella parta sunt; i. hæc equites præmissi erant, qui Albanos Romam traducerent, L.; i. vina fugam Cinaræ plorare protervæ; i. amicitias et amores i. et iras omnem crede diem tibi diluxisse supremum, Hor.; puerorum mores i. ludendum facillime cognoscuntur, Qu.; i. initia, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intrā</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">abl. sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af adj.</text:span> inter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> interus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liks.</text:span> supra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> super):<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Innantill, inuti:</text:span></text:span> vasa i. picata, Col.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Præp.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Innanför, inom,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (äfwen ss. uttr. för en rörelse); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hitom,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på denna sidan om; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">inne i:</text:span></text:span> i. parietes, regiones, C.<text:span text:style-name="T3">;</text:span> i. castra, Cs.; i. oppidum; i. moenia, L.; Iliacos i. muros peccatur et extra, Hor.; Cimbros i. fines suos ingredi prohibuerant, Cs.; i. moenia compellere, N.; i. montem Taurum regnare; nunc nulla i. Oceani ostium hostium navis est, C.; nil i. est oleam, nil extra est in nuce duri, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inom</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i sinnet, i tankarne):</text:span> non tam refert, qualia sint, quæ i. nosmet ipsos composuimus, quam quomodo efferantur, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inom:</text:span></text:span> i. decem annos, C.; i. annum vicesimum, Cs.; i. paucos dies; i. decimum diem, L.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: dels = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inom ett mått</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. en factisk gräns; dels = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ej utöfwer, blott till; under</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mindre, måttligare än):</text:span> tutus et i. spem veniæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inom den gräns, till hwilken man kan hoppas ursäkt)</text:span> cautus, Hor.; i. ea, quæ commentariolis vulgata sunt, consistere; i. verba desipere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blott i ord),</text:span> Qu.; modice faciam aut etiam i. modum; epulamur non modo non contra legem, sed etiam i. legem, C.; i. fortunam mansit, Ov.; scripta Hortensii i. famam sunt, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intrō</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">dat.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> inter, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liks.</text:span> eo, quo, ultro):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">In, inåt:</text:span></text:span> spectare, Pt.; venit i. ad nos; abi i., Ter.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Derinne</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i kroppen):</text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĕrior</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Comparat.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till</text:span> inter): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inre:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> Africa, C.; domus i., Vg.; regni ora i., L.; i-es Germani <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(de s. bo längre inne i landet, ej wid gränsen),</text:span> T.; epistola i-ri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i midten af brefwet),</text:span> C.; medius juvenum (senex) ibat et i., si comes unus erat, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inåt, enl. Schol. = till höger; (jfr</text:span> comes exterior, Hor.), Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Trängre, kortare; mindre:</text:span></text:span> bruma nivalem i-re diem gyro trahit, Hor.; Cynosura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(polstjernan)</text:span> cursu i-re brevi convertitur orbe, C. poēt.; contentionis (oratoriæ) extremum - tamen i-us est, quam acutissimus clamor, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Närmare; innerligare, förtroligare:</text:span></text:span> gradus sunt plures societatis humanæ: i-ius est ejusdem esse civitatis; societas i. est eorum, qui ejusdem gentis sunt, propior eorum, qui ejusdem civitatis, C.; i. periculo; amicitia i., L.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Djupare, grundligare:</text:span></text:span> timor proprius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(personlig)</text:span> est i., C.; cura, Sil.; consilia, N.; literæ i-es et reconditæ, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĕrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Längre inne, inåt:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> oratio nec insistat i-us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förr)</text:span> neque excurrat longius, C.; Sen. - <text:span text:style-name="T3">Superl.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Innerst:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> pars urbis; ædes; sacrarium, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Närmast, förtroligast, trognast, innerligast:</text:span></text:span> tute scis postilla, quam intumum habeam te et mea consilia ut tibi credam omnia, Ter. Enn. 127; tecti ad alienos esse possumus, i-i multa apertiora videant necesse est; i., proximus, familiarissimus quisque; is Catilinæ i. fuit; in i-is meis est, C.; i. alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> alicujus; i-a amicitia, familiaritas, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Innerst, hemligast, djupast, grundligast:</text:span></text:span> i-æ vestræ cogitationes; ad i-a alicujus consilia pervenire; odium i-um; penitus ex i-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(djupet af)</text:span> philosophia haurire alqd; ea ipsa hujus artificii disputatio pæne i-a, C.; nulla Tiberio tam i-a causa fuerat, cur Rhodum abscederet, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĭme</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Innerst; innerligast; förtroligast:</text:span></text:span> regere, Ap.; commendari, C.; uti aliquo, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĭmo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Föra</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tränga) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">längst, långt in:</text:span></text:span> mari, Amm.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tillkännagifwa, underrätta:</text:span></text:span> Amm., Treb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĭmātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĭmātor</text:span>, ōris <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">underrättelse, budbärare:</text:span> Cap., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĕrāneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inre, inwärtes:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĕrāneum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tarm, innanmäte;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inelfwor:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Internus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inre, inwärtes, inwändig:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men. (i kroppen, inne i landet m. m.):</text:span> ignis; motus, Sen.; maria, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inhemsk:</text:span></text:span> discordiæ; bella, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Internas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> = internus: Front.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interne</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĕrŭla</text:span> tunica, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inre, under-;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absol. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">skjorta:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intrinsĕcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Innantill, inwändigt, -wärtes, i det inre:</text:span></text:span> pellem i. adipe perungunt, Varr., fauces i. sudabant sanguine, Lucr.; vasa i. picare, Col.; solum Siciliæ i. stratum sulfure est, Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inträda, intränga i, inom; ingå i; beträda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T3">intr.</text:span>: in urbem; in Capitolium, C.; intra præsidia, aliquo, Cs.; casæ, Sil.; a parte heredum i-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inför rätta),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T3">trans.</text:span>: limen, C.; castra, L., N.; Phaĕthon i-vit dubitati tecta parentis, Ov.; mare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(befares),</text:span> curia i-atur, T.; silva i-ta, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Genomborra:</text:span></text:span> venabulo ursos, Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inträda, intränga, innästla sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ett förhållande:</text:span> in possessionem bonorum; in alicujus familiaritatem, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med framställningen) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Gå in uti</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ett ämne); forskande </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">intränga i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> i-bo etiam magis, C.; i-dum est in rerum naturam et penitus, quid ea postulet, videndum, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om ord, tankar, känslor) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Intränga; uppkomma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">bemäktiga sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngns sinne), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">hänföra:</text:span></text:span> definitio in mentem judicis i. non potest, cupido rei animum i-vit, C.; pudor alqm, T.; vatem deus, St. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intrābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. kan befaras:</text:span> os amnis, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intŭs</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">partikel:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inifrån:</text:span></text:span> dic, me orare, ut aliquis i. prodeat; i. exire, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inne; innantill, inwändigt, i det inre:</text:span></text:span> i. ibidem uxor tua est; nemo exibit: omnes i. conficiunt negotium, Pt.; Nasica sensit, Ennium i. esse; non modo in oculis civium magnus, sed etiam i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i det enskilda)</text:span> domique, C.; i. in cella, in æde Junonis, L.; omne ovum i. bicolor est, Pn.; ad populum phaleras: ego te i. et in cute nov<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">i,</text:span></text:span> Ps.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">In:</text:span></text:span> ex omnibus cibis corpora i. in artus discedunt, C.; i. agere equos, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Præp.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inne i:</text:span></text:span> ædium, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intestīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> tempus, tempestivus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inwärtes, inwändig, inre; inifrån kommande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i kroppen:</text:span> dolor; tremor, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allmännare mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inre, inhemsk;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> inom sig sjelf:</text:span> malum i-um et domesticum bellum, C.; scelus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(familje-);</text:span> i-a corporis seditio, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intestīnum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intestīna</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tarm,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">pl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">innanmäte, inelfwor:</text:span></text:span> medium; i-a se astringunt, relaxant; laborare ex <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i)</text:span> i-is, C.; murmurant i-a alicui, Pt.; capiunt plus i-a poētæ, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>năchus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod och mythisk konung i Argolis.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īnăchĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronym.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īnăchĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īnăchis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A. f.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ĭnānis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tom</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T3">aliqua re, alicujus rei</text:span>):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: tom = obesatt, blottad, öde; fastande m. m.:</text:span> vas; navis; lagena; sella; equus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utan ryttare);</text:span> ager aratoribus, C.; currus, Ov.; domus, Ct.; siccus, i. sperne cibum vilem, Hor.; aures, quid plenum, quid i-e sit, judicant, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">relativt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tom, blottad på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> epistola re utili i.; omnia plena consiliorum, i-ia verborum reperietis, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tomhändt, utblottad, utfattig:</text:span></text:span> egentes i-esque redierunt, C.; homines i-es, Pt. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tom</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">wäsenlös, liflös, innehållslös, meningslös, betydelselös, grundlös; inbillad; wärdelös, gagnlös, fruktlös, fåfäng:</text:span></text:span> animum picturā pascit i-i, Vg.; epistola; vox i.; elocutio i. et puerilis; i. concertatio, sonitus verborum; falsa et i-ia visa somniorum; multis i-bus rebus delectari; crimen; cogitatio; labor, C.; simulatio, Cs.; metus, Lucr.; operam insumere i-em, Hor.; credulitas, T. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tom</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = som intet lärt l. wet:</text:span> Athenis redire i-em, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Fåfäng, inbilsk:</text:span></text:span> homo i. et regiæ superbiæ, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnāne</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Det tomma, tomma rymden</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (tomrum):</text:span> nullum i. nihil esse individuum potest, C.; est in rebus i., Lucr.; nubes et i-ia captare, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tom form</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ceremoni, tomt sken:</text:span></text:span> apud Romanos vis imperii valet, i-ia transmittuntur; ludos et i-ia honoris medio rationis et abundantiæ duxit, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnānia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tomhet:</text:span></text:span> ædes i-is oppletæ atque araneis, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnānĭlŏquus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som talar tomma ord:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnānio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Göra tom, uttömma:</text:span></text:span> alvum, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnānīmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T3">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tomrum:</text:span></text:span> i-is (alvi) explementum quærito, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnānĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tomhet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg., abstract mening:</text:span> arundinis, Pn.; loci, Sen.; oris, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Tomma rymden:</text:span></text:span> individua corpora per i-em feruntur, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inbillning, dårskap:</text:span></text:span> error et i.; versari in summa i-e, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnānĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Utan grund, utan werklig orsak; förgäfwes, fruktlöst:</text:span></text:span> animus i. et effuse exsultat, C.; (poēta) animum (spectatoris) i. angit, Hor.; artes medicas i. exercere, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exĭnānio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uttömma, tömma ut; - utplundra, utarma:</text:span></text:span> naves, C.; ovum; alvum; urinam, Pn.; - reges et gentes; agros; domos, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭbĭnānis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Något fåfäng</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ärekär:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ĭ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">nappărātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: (apparo, paro): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Obereddhet; brist på anstalter:</text:span></text:span> C. Her. II. 4. §. 7.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ĭ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">nărātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: (aro): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Oplöjd:</text:span></text:span> Vg., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Ī</text:span>nărĭmē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T3">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en ö (Ischia).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Inauris, -auritus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Auris.<text:line-break/>Inauro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Aurum.<text:line-break/>Inausus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Audeo.<text:line-break/>Incæduus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cædo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">I</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">ncalfăcio</text:span>, ĕre: (caleo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Uppwärma:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Incend . . ., Incensio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Candeo. <text:line-break/>Incensus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Censeo.<text:line-break/>Incent . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Incino, Cano.<text:line-break/>Incept . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Incipio, Capio. <text:line-break/>Incert . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cerno.<text:line-break/>Incess . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Incedo, Cedo.<text:line-break/>Incest . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Castus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Inchoo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŏho</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Börja, påbörja; göra början</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med l. lägga grunden till -:</text:span> libros i-re et conficere; oratorem i-re et informare; philosophiam multis locis (in saturis meis) i-vi; sapientia hominem non genuit, sed accepit a natura i-tum. C.; villam; opus, Su.; vitæ summa brevis spem nos vetat i. longam, Hor.; dignitatem nostram a Vespasiano i-tam, a Tito auctam non abnuerim, T.; reges plures i-ant apes, ne desint (reges electo flore - fiunt), Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol. = börja tala:</text:span> St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inchoātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T3">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Blott påbörjad, ofulländad; ofullkomlig:</text:span></text:span> multa i-a, non perfecta; i-o operi fastigium imponere; quædam rudia et i-a e nostris commentariis exciderunt; cognitio manca</text:p>
  </office:text>
 </office:body>
</office:document>